\id PSA - Keyagana NT with OT portions [kyg] -Papua New Guinea 2001 (web 2014)
\h Samu
\toc1 SAMU
\toc2 Samu
\toc3 Sam
\mt1 SAMU
\ip Mani mukumo Isaleli vayaꞌmogimo ina kavaꞌmo huꞌa mono yokemo nehaya mukumae. Mago mani mukufiꞌmo haneꞌniya yokemo Yulusalemu kotega Goti mono 3 noꞌafiꞌmo aliꞌa anupa nehaya afinaꞌmo nehaya mono yokemo haneꞌniye. Magoꞌamo ina kavaꞌmo huꞌa mono hisaya afinaꞌmo ve aꞌnemogimo aeꞌa hakalo huꞌa nunumu huge magoke magoke ve aꞌnemogimo apakaiꞌapi kanaꞌapimo haneya afinaꞌmo huge nehae. Ina kavaꞌmo huꞌa asole vayaꞌmogimo mani yokeꞌe nunumu geꞌeꞌmo alu afina alu afinafeꞌmo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnae. Henagaꞌamo mago vayaꞌmogimo aliꞌa magokepi maleꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo magoke mukugana huno haneꞌniye. Mani yokemogiꞌe nunumu gemogiꞌeꞌmo alu aepa alu aepaꞌagi aipa agesagi huno haneꞌniye.
\ip Goti agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hisaya yokemo hanege hosu kavaꞌapieꞌmo aeꞌa hakalo hisageno alino atalesiya nunumu gemo hanege hanageke yaꞌmo alige kana alige hisaya afinaꞌmo hapa maesiya yaꞌmo alisaya nunumu gemo hanege alopa afinaꞌmo saufa kini vekamo lekana paiꞌa atesaya afina yokemo hanege Gotifeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago huꞌnaya kavaꞌapieꞌmo aeꞌa hakalo hisaya yokemo hanege Gotifeꞌmo hao ke hesaya yokemo hanege apaipamoꞌmo kana huge apakesamo afige hisaya kavafeꞌmo aeꞌa hakalo hisaya nunumu gemo hanege Gotifeꞌmo afi gesageno kame vayaꞌapimo apamagisiya nunumu gemo hanege ina kava huno ve aꞌnemogimo akame nehisaya alagepa kavaꞌapimo alino apave lisiya yokemo hanege huno haneꞌniye.
\ip Mani yokemoꞌe nunumu gemoꞌeꞌmo muki afaꞌa maiꞌnona ve aꞌnemogitamo alu kava alu kavapiꞌmo maiꞌnisunagenoꞌaeꞌmo mani yokemoꞌa laha maegaiye. Lagaemo lamogaga aisuna afinatimo hanege laipamoꞌmo kana hisiya afinatimo hanege huno haneꞌniye. Lagaemo neya vayaꞌmo lokiya vayaꞌmo maisuna afinatimo hanege kosuna lesuna afinatimo hanege huno haneꞌniye. Mago afinaꞌmo kaitaꞌmo lahauge mago afinaꞌmo laipamoꞌmo kanale huge nehiye. Yoke mukufiꞌmo haneꞌniya yokemoꞌmo fatago kavaꞌmo huno muki mani agufa afinaꞌmo lagaemo afaꞌa maiꞌnonagenoꞌaeꞌmo alino anupa huno nelateyaꞌmofeꞌmo akeyaꞌvilagatiꞌmo eno hemeniꞌeꞌmo mani yokemoꞌa apakesamo afiꞌa fatago huꞌnaya kavaꞌmo alino lokiya vaino apateteno Goti vayaꞌamo afaꞌa neꞌmaiya kavaꞌapimo alagi ha neꞌmae.
\ip Neviniꞌa asole samu yokemo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌniye. Moseseꞌa samu 90 gemo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌniye. Etaniꞌa samu 89 gemo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌniye. Esafiꞌa samu 73, 74, 75, 76, 77, 78, 79, 80, 81, 82, 83 gemo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌniye. Ina laꞌmo mago samu yokemo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnifi huta oꞌafiꞌnone. Mago samu yokemo Mesaiya vekamo afole aisiya Kalaisi vekaeꞌmo ava gemo haneꞌniye. Mago mani samu gefatiꞌmo saufa kotalake mukufiꞌmo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnae. Samu 2, 8, 16, 19, 21, 22, 23, 24, 40, 45, 69, 72, 89, 102, 110 Kalaisi vekaeꞌmo ava gemae. Magoꞌe samu yokefiꞌmo Kalaisifeꞌmo ava gemo haneꞌnegaiye.
\c 1
\s1 Alagepa vayaꞌe Gotifeꞌmo mono nosaya vayaꞌefeꞌmo apava ge yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Gotifeꞌmo mono nosaya vayaꞌmogimo apakesamo afiteꞌapaeꞌmo, ina kateꞌmo viyo, huꞌa nehaya kateꞌmo umenitata osuge hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo neꞌvaya kateꞌmo uꞌa he tiꞌa oꞌmaige mono katefeꞌmo, afa kane, huꞌa huteꞌa huꞌa faipa huꞌa neꞌataya vayaꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌa itopaleꞌmo oꞌmaige huꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogimo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\v 2 Ani agufa kavaꞌmo nosayaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmo keꞌaepa geꞌalefekeꞌmo amuse huteꞌa apamogaga neꞌaiye. Apakaemo felugaꞌe haniꞌilagaꞌeꞌmo keꞌaepa geꞌaekeꞌmo apakesa afifi huꞌa neꞌmaiye.
\v 3 Apakaemo ani agoꞌnanena folagapiꞌmo fai maleꞌniya yosamoꞌmo alagamo neꞌaeya afinaꞌmo alagamo neꞌaesigenoꞌaeꞌmo haitaꞌamo falu noteya yosagana huꞌa maiꞌnae. Muki aliꞌnaya aliꞌyaꞌapimoꞌmo alagepa huno afole neꞌaiye.
\p 
\v 4 Hosu vayaꞌmo ani kava huꞌa oꞌmaiꞌnae. Apakaemo mago haletiꞌya yakana huꞌa maiꞌnae. Haleti yaꞌamo haleꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo yasimoꞌmo alino halelino neꞌviya haletiꞌya yakana huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 5 Maiꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo Gotifeꞌmo mono nosaya vayaꞌmo agoti huno apatesiya yateꞌmo he tiꞌa oꞌmaiꞌa alagi asagauꞌa aigae. Inagi hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo fatago vayaꞌmo aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maisayapiꞌmo uꞌa oꞌmaigae.
\v 6 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fatago vayaꞌmogimo nehaya kavaꞌapieꞌmo apakeno amuse huno neꞌapateyaꞌmonanafa agaefeꞌmo mono nosaya vayaꞌai aliꞌyaꞌapimo alino hano huno atalesigeꞌa alagi lageso hugae.
\c 2
\s1 Gotiꞌa kini vekamo lekana paino ateꞌniya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Na kavaꞌmo hisayafeꞌmo malaga vayaꞌmogi apavamusa valeteꞌa apano neꞌae. Vayaꞌmogimo, mani kavaꞌmo hugune, huꞌa apakesamo neꞌafiyaꞌmonanafa afaꞌa osugae.
\v 2-3 Ma mopafi kava vayaꞌe kini vayaꞌapimogiꞌeꞌmo Ala kava netegaꞌe lekana paino ateteno uvelimo lakino faleno ateꞌniya vekalegaꞌeꞌmo kame huꞌana anatesayafeꞌmo aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maiꞌneꞌa vegemo huꞌapaeꞌmo, yagaiꞌana latesaꞌagetaeꞌmo anaiyafiꞌmo oꞌmaigune, huꞌa nehae.
\p 
\v 4 Kokuꞌnapiꞌmo fai maiꞌniya vekamoꞌa kigi huno apategaiye. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa, afa gemo nehae, huno nehiye.
\v 5 Aipamo leno apateꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo lokiya gefatiꞌmo nehigeꞌapaeꞌmo atete nehae.
\v 6 Agaemo, ani kavaꞌmo nehayaꞌmonanafa nagaemo Saiyoni kotega naote aveleꞌmo lekana paiꞌna ateꞌnova kini vekamoꞌa yagaino apatesiyafeꞌmo lekana paiꞌna ateꞌnove, huno hapa paiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 7 Kini vekamoꞌa, Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hu maleꞌniya gemo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna lapa paiguve, huno huꞌniye. Agaemo, Hemeni afinaꞌmo mafaꞌneꞌnimo aliꞌna kateꞌnogeka maiꞌnane, huno naha paiꞌniye.
\v 8 Ge huka nafi gegeꞌnao muki alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌmo apavaleꞌna aliꞌna kayapiꞌmo apatesugeno muki ma mopamo kagaika yaꞌmo haneno.
\v 9 Kalipa mopaletiꞌmo alo nehaya samomo kayotetiꞌmo amagiꞌnageno aino atagino aise aise nehiya kava huka aeni kayotetiꞌmo apamagigane, huno naha paiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 10 Ani ge huꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo kini vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, alagepa hutapa afiyo. Ma mopafiꞌmo neꞌyagaiya vayane, huꞌna, ehetapiye.
\v 11 Lapakaemo koli nehutapaekeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌamo aliyo. Atete nehutapaekeꞌmo lapamogaga aiyo.
\v 12 Mafaꞌneꞌamo haetapa neyo. Fiku yanageno aipamo aiseꞌamo leno lapateteno lapamagisigetapa kateꞌmo asagautapa aigayanagi. Agaepiꞌmo eꞌa fala kiꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogimo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\c 3
\s1 Nevini mafaꞌneꞌamo Apasalomiꞌa hafaiꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo Neviniꞌmo nunumu huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Vaehae, kame vayaꞌnimo magoꞌe magoꞌe huꞌa asole vayaꞌmo afole neꞌaiye. Asole vayaꞌmo natale uꞌa kame huꞌa neꞌnatae.
\v 2 Apakaemo nagaefeꞌmo, Gotiꞌa ha oꞌmaegaiye, huꞌa nehae.
\v 3 Nehayaꞌmonanafa Ala kava nene, kagaemo haleguꞌnimo maiꞌnane. Kagaekeꞌmo naha maeꞌnanageꞌna aeꞌna neꞌapakasove. Kagaekeꞌmo alika he tika neꞌnatana vekamo maiꞌnane.
\v 4 Nagaemo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge nehugenoꞌaeꞌmo aote aveleꞌmo mono noꞌafatiꞌmo neꞌafiye.
\v 5 Muki haniꞌilagamo hipaꞌnileꞌmo haiꞌna nauꞌmo nekalogenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa yagaino neꞌnate.
\v 6 Asole kame vayaꞌnimogimo faiꞌa ku aiꞌa neꞌnatayaꞌmonanafa koliꞌapimo nosuve.
\v 7 Ala kava nene, Gotiꞌnimogamo, he tika nagufamo alika katika nato. Kagaemo muki kame vayaꞌnimo kayoꞌmo neꞌapaminagenoꞌaeꞌmo lokiyaꞌapimo alagi hano nehiyanageꞌa oꞌnahaegae.
\v 8 Kagaekeꞌmo lagufamo alika katika nelatane. Vayaꞌamo fiku hapa maeno apamino.
\c 5
\s1 Netepiꞌmo nunumu huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 O, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, geꞌnimo afika alagepa huka afiyo. Naipafiꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna neꞌmauvanagi kaipamo namiyo.
\v 2 Ala kini vekaꞌnimo Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, kagaefekeꞌmo nunumu huguvaꞌmofeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge hisuva geꞌnimo afiyo.
\v 3 Nagaemo muki afinaꞌmo netepiꞌmo ge hisugeka afigane. O, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Netepiꞌmo nunumu hisuva geꞌnimoꞌa kevemo haegekana huꞌna kahaeteꞌna aliꞌna maku huꞌna kagegauve.
\v 4 Kagaemo hosu kavafeꞌmo amuse huka noꞌatana Gotigamo maiꞌnane. Hosu kavaꞌmoꞌa kagae kahaopaleꞌmo alagi lokaeno ohanegaiye.
\v 5 Apakiꞌapileꞌmo aliꞌa asaga nehaya vayaꞌmo kaulagaleꞌmo he tiꞌa oꞌmaigae. Kagaemo muki hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo alagi okahauꞌnigeka kaini huka neꞌapatane.
\v 6 Kagaemo aigofe gemo nehaya vayaꞌaina alika apagoꞌya lagauka apatalegane. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa vayaꞌmo nehapaya vayaꞌe humi neꞌapataya vayaꞌefeꞌmo avenatuꞌna heno atalegekana huno neꞌmaiye.
\p 
\v 7 Ani kava huka maiꞌnanaꞌmonanafa nagaefeꞌmo muki kahau huka neꞌnatana kavakaletiꞌmo nokafiꞌmo faleꞌna haiguve. Kagaefekeꞌmo koli huteꞌnaeꞌmo aote mono nokamo ageteꞌna mono huguve.
\v 8 O, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kame vayaꞌnimo maiꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo fatago kavakafiꞌmo nayateꞌmo alika navalelika uvo. Naulagamo kakaleꞌmo alika api aika nato.
\v 9 Lama gemo apavayafiꞌmo alagi ohaneꞌniye. Apaipafiꞌmo hosu kavaꞌageꞌmo haneꞌniye. Lugoꞌapimo kano kelimo aliꞌa halo neꞌaigeno atu neꞌaiya kano keligana huno haneꞌniye. Apavenafuꞌnaletiꞌmo hapaisiya agufa gemo nehae.
\v 10 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, Vaiꞌmo alika apamiyo. Alika apatalegeꞌapao ani kavaꞌmo hugune, huꞌa apakesamo neꞌafiya kavatetiꞌmo asagauꞌa aiyo. Kagaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa gekamo ago amagiꞌa ataleꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo asole hosu kavaꞌapifiꞌmo maiꞌnagi alika yaga auka apatalo.
\p 
\v 11 Apataleganaꞌmonanafa kagaefekeꞌmo, laha maegaiye, huꞌa apakesamo neꞌafiya vayaꞌmogi muki afinaꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo huteꞌa apamogaga aiyo, kagaemo alagepa huꞌa maisayafeꞌmo aika apati kaeꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmae. Kagikaeꞌmo hapau apayamopafiꞌmo hapauꞌnisiya vayaꞌmogimo kagaepiꞌmo apamogaga aiyo.
\v 12 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kagaemo fatago vayaꞌmo hapa maesanageꞌa alagepa huꞌa maigae. Kagaemo haleguꞌapigana huka faika ku aika apategane.
\c 6
\s1 Haniꞌilagamo havaeꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo nunumu huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, ge neꞌnahaugenoꞌaeꞌmo kaipamo neleneꞌmo ge oꞌnahauvo. Kayoꞌmo neꞌnamisanagenoꞌaeꞌmo kaipamo neleneꞌmo kayoꞌmo oꞌnamiyo.
\v 2 Lokiyaꞌnimo alagi ohaneꞌniyanagi kahau huka nato. Lokiyaꞌnimo alagi ohaneꞌnigeꞌna atete nehuvanagi halate alika alagepa huka nato.
\v 3 Naipamoꞌmo lusi kava huno kana huꞌniyanageka na magi afinaꞌmo maiteka naha maegane.
\v 4 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, aika afe leka nagetekaeꞌmo hatu maeka nato. Falu kaipa vekamo maiꞌneka kahau huka neꞌapatana vekamo falisuva kavategatiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 5 Faliꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo kagaefeꞌmo apakesamo noꞌafiye. Kanolufiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogi kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa nokatae.
\v 6 Yulagefa neꞌaugenoꞌaeꞌmo lusi kava huno alaga neꞌnahae. Muki haniꞌilagamo hipaꞌnileꞌmo havaeꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo naunu aniꞌmoꞌmo hipaꞌnileꞌmo lamiꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo lanitani nehiye.
\v 7 Kame vayaꞌnimo maiꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo naunumo lamiꞌnigeno naulagamo kosiꞌnigeꞌna ageꞌna alagepa huꞌna noꞌagove.
\v 8 Aviꞌya nehugenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa afiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayanagi nataletapa viyo.
\v 9 Nunumu huꞌna aukaya huꞌna ge nehugenoꞌaeꞌmo afiꞌniyanageno afaꞌa naha maegaiye.
\v 10 Naha maesigeꞌapaeꞌmo muki kame vayaꞌnimo apavagage hisigeꞌa atete hugae. Apavagage hisigeꞌa nataleꞌa ugae.
\c 8
\s1 Vemo mafaꞌneꞌaifeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, Ala kava netimogae, huꞌna, ma mopafi muki haopalegatiꞌmo ala kagikamo aliꞌnane. Ha le konali yakamoꞌa kokuꞌnate haneꞌniya yaꞌe vayaꞌeꞌmo ago aeno apakaseꞌniye.
\v 2 Kagaemo muki aise mafaꞌne anagaꞌe nute mafaꞌne anagaꞌeꞌmo lokiya vaika apateꞌnanageꞌapaeꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga nehageꞌapaeꞌmo kamekamogiꞌe gekamo amagiꞌa neꞌatalaya vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo ge osuꞌa afaꞌa maigae.
\p 
\v 3-4 Nagaemo kokuꞌnate yaꞌmo kayatetiꞌmo alo huꞌnana yaꞌmo kaiꞌe muki kanefiꞌeꞌmo alo huka maleꞌnana yafeꞌmo nagesamo neꞌafiꞌnaeꞌmo, ma mopafi vayaꞌmo ina agufa vayanagi na kava higeka apakaefeꞌmo kagesamo neꞌafine. Na kava higeka vemo mafaꞌnemo ha neꞌmane.
\v 5 Kagaemo vemo mafaꞌnemo alika atege enisole vayaꞌmo alika apatege huꞌnanageꞌapaeꞌmo enisole vayaꞌmogimo aise afinaꞌmo aeꞌa agaseꞌa maiꞌnae. Enisole vayaꞌai apaiyafiꞌmo alika ateteka ha le konali yaꞌaꞌe ala agiꞌaꞌeꞌmo alika amiꞌnane.
\v 6 Kagaemo, alo huꞌnova yateꞌmo yagaika apato, huka hapa paiteka muki yaꞌe vayaꞌeꞌmo alika aiyafiꞌmo apateꞌnane.
\v 7-8 Muki sipisipigi pulumakagi afela afugi kokuꞌnate namagi anipi noyamegi solovalapiꞌmo umenitata nehaya yanagi huka alika aiyafiꞌmo apateꞌnane.
\v 9 Ala kava nene, Ala kava netimogae, huꞌna, ma mopafi muki haopalegatiꞌmo ala kagikamo aliꞌnane.
\c 11
\s1 Gotiꞌa alino fako huno neꞌapateya kavafeꞌmo ava gemo huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Nagaemo hakumo alino ataleno yagaino natesiyafeꞌmo Ala kava nepiꞌmo uꞌna fala nekuvaꞌmofeꞌmo na agufa gemo, namagana huka avelegamo halelika kaune ho, hutapa naha paigae.
\v 2 Ago, hosu vayaꞌmogimo alagepa apaipa vayaꞌmo hapaesayafeꞌmo atiꞌapimo yagaiteꞌa kevemo aliꞌa yagailiꞌa haniꞌilagamo neꞌvae.
\v 3 Faino ateꞌniya yaꞌmo aliꞌa halagape vaiꞌa atalesayana alagepa vayaꞌmogimo na kava hugae.
\v 4 Gotiꞌa kokuꞌnapiꞌmo maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo aote mono noꞌafiꞌmo fai maiꞌniye. Gotiꞌa yagaino neꞌapateya siateꞌmo fai maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo ma mopafi muki vayaꞌmo apakeno alagepa huno apakeꞌneno alino fako huno neꞌapate.
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alagepa vayaꞌmo apamalageka nehiyaꞌmonanafa hosu vayanagi vayaꞌmo apamagisayafeꞌmo hapauꞌniya vayaꞌenagi huno aipafatiꞌmo alagi ohauꞌniye.
\v 6 Agaemo apakaetegamo ko aigekana huno aneꞌai nofikana yaꞌmo yaga augiye. Atagi atafiꞌmo kae malefa yafanagi amuko yasimogi huno hetamaꞌapimo haneꞌniye.
\v 7 Na agufa kavafeꞌmo hauꞌniyanagenoꞌaene. Ala kava neꞌmo fatago vekamo maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo fatago kavafekeꞌmo hauꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmae. Alagepa kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo haiꞌa augosafiꞌmo agegae.
\c 12
\s1 Gotiꞌa yagaino latesigeta alagepa huta maigune, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Hemenimo kagaefekeꞌmo mono nehaya vayaꞌmo oꞌmaiꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo laha mao. Ma mopafi vayapatiꞌmo fatago vayaꞌmo ago faliꞌa hano huꞌnae.
\v 2 Muki vayaꞌmogimo afa gegeꞌmo hapa nepaiye. Aigofe geletiꞌmo huꞌa hapaoke nehae.
\p 
\v 3 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa aigofe gemo huteꞌa huꞌa hapaoke nehaya vayaꞌmo kayoꞌmo apamigiye. Ala apakimo alisayafeꞌmo ge nehaya vayaꞌmo alagi alino hano huno apatalegaiye.
\v 4 Apakaemo, getiletiꞌmo afaꞌa huta aeta apakasegaune. Lahauꞌniya gemo afaꞌa hugune. Ina laꞌmo yagaino nelate, huꞌa nehae.
\p 
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hunoꞌaeꞌmo, apakaemo kagemi yaꞌapimo oꞌmaleꞌnaya vayaꞌmo aliꞌa afepi neꞌapatae. Kafu huteꞌa alagepa huꞌa noꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogimo ha ha nehayaꞌmofeꞌmo he tiꞌna hapa maegauve. Afaꞌa maisayafeꞌmo hapauꞌniyanageꞌna hapa maeteꞌna aliꞌna alagepa huꞌna apategauve, huno huꞌniye.
\p 
\v 6 Ala kava neꞌmo geꞌamo alagi lama geꞌageꞌmo haneꞌniye. Vayaꞌmogimo siluva yafaꞌmo aliꞌa atafiꞌmo seveni afinaꞌmo kaete kaete huꞌa kaeꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo muki oꞌaniꞌya faiꞌniya yaꞌamo leno hano huno ataleꞌnigeno siluva yafaꞌageꞌmo alino afole neꞌaiya kava huno Goti geꞌamo alagi lama geꞌageꞌmo haneꞌniye.
\v 7 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, yagaika latesanageta alagepa huta maigune. Muki afinaꞌmo laha maesanageꞌapaeꞌmo hosu vayaꞌmogi olatafaugae.
\p 
\v 8 Alagi hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo ala apakimo neꞌaligeꞌapaeꞌmo hosu vayaꞌmogimo muki haopalegamo umenitata nehae.
\c 15
\s1 Seli mono noꞌafiꞌmo afaꞌa haiꞌa maisaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo apava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, haiya agufa vayaꞌmogimo seli mono nokafiꞌmo afaꞌa haiꞌa maigae. Haiya agufa vayaꞌmogimo kaote aveleꞌmo afaꞌa haiꞌa maigae.
\p 
\v 2 Vaiꞌmo oꞌaliꞌa he tiꞌa umenitata huge fatago kavaꞌmo huge apaipafatiꞌmo lama gemo huge
\v 3 huꞌa faipa huꞌa oꞌapatege apao vayaꞌaitegamo hosu kavaꞌmo osuge hapaopale neꞌmaiya vayaꞌaifenagi alu vayaꞌaifenagi huꞌa hosu faigoko gemo nehaya gemo oꞌafige
\v 4 Gotiꞌa ohauꞌniya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo, laulagaleꞌmo ina agufa vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae, huꞌa huge Gotifeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌai apakiꞌapileꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa apatege Goti agiꞌalefeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo hugune, huꞌa hapa nepaiya gemo akame hisayafeꞌmo kana huꞌnisiyana afaꞌa akame huge
\v 5 akamelegatiꞌmo magoꞌe monimo oꞌalige vaiꞌmo oꞌapamiꞌnaya vayaꞌaitegamo hosu kavaꞌmo hisayafeꞌmo kutulu monimo ohagege huꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogimo haiꞌa maigae.
\p Aliꞌa hapa ofaisageꞌa ani agufa kavaꞌmo nehisaya vayaꞌmogimo muki afinaꞌmo maige maige huꞌa maigae.
\c 16
\s1 Gotiꞌa agae vekaꞌamo alagepa huno ha maesiya gemae
\p 
\v 1 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, nagaemo kagaefekeꞌmo, naha maegaiye, huꞌna nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo yagaika nategeꞌnao afaꞌa maino.
\v 2-3 Nagaemo Ala kava nefeꞌmo, Ala kava neꞌnimo maiꞌnane, huꞌna kaha nepauve. Kaha maesuvafeꞌmo alagepa kavaꞌmo nosufa ma mopafi maiꞌnaya apaote vayaꞌmo hapa maesuvafekeꞌmo alagepa kavaꞌmo nehuve. Apakaemo hogote vayaꞌmo maiꞌnageꞌna apakaefekeꞌmo amuse huꞌna neꞌapatove.
\v 4 Alu gotiꞌapimo akame hisayafeꞌmo apayamukiki nehaya vayaꞌmogimo magoꞌe huꞌa lusi kana yaꞌmo aligae. Nagaemo kola ofaliniꞌapimo aliꞌna lakiꞌna oꞌapamiꞌna apakiꞌapimo oꞌaegauve.
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmo hetamaꞌnimo maiꞌneno aniꞌmo kapufatiꞌmo neꞌnova anikana huno maiꞌniye. Hetamaꞌnileꞌmo alagepa huka yagaika neꞌnatane.
\v 6 Kagaemo alagepa yaꞌageꞌmo alika fako huka namiꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo amuse nehuve. He, alagepa yaꞌmo ago aliꞌnove.
\v 7 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alino api aino neꞌnateyanageꞌna agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna ategauve. Haniꞌilagamo nagupi mafaꞌnemoꞌa alino naya neꞌmale.
\v 8 Nagaemo muki afinaꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo aliꞌna naulagaleꞌmo neꞌatove. Lamaga nahaopaleꞌmo neꞌmaiyaꞌmofeꞌmo alagepa katetiꞌmo navaleliꞌa oꞌvisageꞌna aliꞌyaꞌnimo oꞌatalegauve.
\v 9 Neꞌmaiyaꞌmofeꞌmo naipafiꞌmo namogaga neꞌauve. Navayafatiꞌmo namogaga neꞌauve. Navayagunagu huꞌna agava neꞌmauvanageno nagufaꞌnimo alagepa huno hanesigeꞌna maiꞌna falu huguve.
\v 10 Kagaemo mani kavatefeꞌmo nauneꞌnameꞌnimo kanolufiꞌmo oꞌatalegane. Kagaemo, aote vekaꞌnimo agufaꞌamo atalesugeno okasaligiye, huka huꞌnane.
\v 11 Kagaemo alagepa huꞌna maige maige huꞌna maisuva kaꞌmo alika nave ligane. Kaulagaleꞌmo maisaya vayaꞌai apaipafiꞌmo apamogaga aisaya kavaꞌmoꞌa havai tegaiye. Lamaga kahaopaleꞌmo maisaya vayaꞌmogimo muki afinaꞌmo lusi kava huꞌa apavai apavai huge huge huli uꞌa maigae.
\c 17
\s1 Naha mao, huno nunumuꞌmo huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Alagepa kavaꞌnieꞌmo ge hisugekaeꞌmo geꞌnimo afiyo. Kamalageka hisuvafeꞌmo nunumu osuꞌnogi kaipamo namiyo.
\v 2 Kaulagaleꞌmo maiꞌnisugekaeꞌmo alika fako huka natetekaeꞌmo, alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌnane, huka huvo. Kagaemo alagepa kavaꞌnimo ago.
\p 
\v 3 Naipaeꞌmo amalageka huꞌnane. Kagaemo haniꞌilagamo eka nagetekaeꞌmo namalageka huꞌnanaꞌmonanafa hosu nagesa neꞌafuva kavaꞌnimo oꞌageꞌnane. Hosu gemo osuguve, huꞌna nagoꞌyamo ataleꞌna ge huꞌnove.
\v 4 Ma mopafi vayaꞌai kavaꞌapieꞌmo oꞌnahauꞌnigeꞌna nagesa noꞌafuve. Gekamo afiteꞌnaeꞌmo vayaꞌmo nehapaeya vekamo kaꞌaleꞌmo oꞌuꞌnove.
\v 5 Nagaemo kakaleꞌmo neꞌuꞌnaeꞌmo aeꞌna halu oꞌvalesuvafeꞌmo natafauvo.
\p 
\v 6 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, Geꞌnimo afaꞌa afiganaꞌmofeꞌmo kagaefekeꞌmo ge huꞌnove. Kagetafo huꞌneka geꞌnimo afiyo.
\v 7 Lamaga kayatetiꞌmo naha maeteka kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauꞌniya kavakamo ageꞌna nahau aisuva kavakamo alika nave liyo. O Gotiyo, huꞌna, kame hapaesayafeꞌmo huꞌnaya vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo apakufamo alika katika neꞌapatana Gotigae, huꞌna, Naha mao.
\v 8 Vayaꞌmogimo apaulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa neꞌyagaiya kava huka yagaika nato. Kahakumo ulunapiꞌmo alika fala kika nato.
\v 9 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo kana yaꞌmo aliꞌa neꞌnamiye. Kame vayaꞌnimogimo nahaesayafeꞌmo yagaiꞌa ku aiꞌa nateꞌnayanagi naha mao.
\p 
\v 10 Apaipaguꞌe vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae. Ala apakimo alisayafekeꞌmo gemo nehae.
\v 11 Apakaemo faiꞌa ku aiꞌa lateꞌnae. Laiyakamo ageteꞌa mopafiꞌmo aliꞌa yaga auꞌa latalesayafeꞌmo nehae.
\v 12 Hapaesayafeꞌmo yagaiꞌa maiꞌnaya laiyonigana huꞌa maige fala kino maiꞌniya aikeli laiyonigana huꞌa maige huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\p 
\v 13 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, he tika eka apakaeꞌeꞌmo fotu nehukaeꞌmo mopafiꞌmo alika yaga auka apatalo. Kagaemo naipekaletiꞌmo hosu vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 14 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kayatetiꞌmo ma mopafi vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato. Ma mopafikeꞌmo hetamaꞌapimo haneꞌniye. Kagaemo fala kino haneꞌniya alagepa yakamo alika neꞌapaminagenoꞌaeꞌmo apakupafiꞌmo havai teꞌniye. Mafaꞌneꞌapimo neꞌyaꞌmoꞌa apamu paeꞌniye. Apakaemo kagemi yaꞌapimo neꞌatalageꞌapaeꞌmo nute mafaꞌneꞌapimogi neꞌaliye.
\p 
\v 15 Kagemi yaꞌapimo neꞌaliyaꞌmonanafa nagaemo fatago kavakamo aliꞌnovanageꞌna kaugosafiꞌmo kagegauve. Nagaemo naupatiꞌmo he tiꞌna kagaekana huꞌna maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo magoꞌe kavafeꞌmo nahaꞌye osugiye.
\c 19
\s1 Gotiꞌa alo huꞌniya yaꞌmoꞌmo ala agiꞌamo neꞌamiya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Kokuꞌnateꞌmo haneꞌniya yaꞌmoꞌa Goti ha le konali yaꞌaeꞌmo aeno hakalo huno hapa nepaiye. Kokuꞌnaꞌmoꞌa Goti alagepa aliꞌyaꞌamo alino apave neliye.
\v 2 Felugaꞌe felugaꞌeꞌmo ge nehunoꞌaeꞌmo haniꞌilagaꞌe haniꞌilagaꞌeꞌmo huꞌa ageteꞌa afisayafeꞌmo alino apave neliye.
\v 3 Muki ma mopafiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa alu apake alu apakemo neꞌaiya vayaꞌmogimo kokuꞌnate haneꞌniya yaꞌmo ava gemo neꞌafiye. Ava gemo oꞌafiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo mago oꞌmaiꞌnae.
\v 4 Kokuꞌnate haneꞌniya yaꞌmo ava gemo muki haopalega mopamo loleꞌe loleꞌe atupalegamo aino atagu faelino uneno hulino uꞌniye. Gotiꞌa yegemo noꞌamo kokuꞌnapiꞌmo ki maleꞌniye.
\v 5 Aꞌmo aligefeꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogi noꞌapimo ataleꞌa apamogaga aime aime neꞌvaya kava huno yegemoꞌmo haineno nelamiye. Apayamufa vayaꞌmogimo uꞌa aeꞌa apakasesayafeꞌmo nagu nagu huꞌa neꞌvaya kava huno yegemoꞌmo haineno nelamiye.
\v 6 Yegemoꞌa kokuꞌnaꞌmo aepalegatiꞌmo haineno atupalegamo nelamiye. Yegemo nelegenoꞌaeꞌmo mago amuko nosiya aupilagamo ohaneꞌnifa muki aupilagaꞌamo alagi leno amuko huno neꞌate.
\p 
\v 7 Ala kava neꞌmo keꞌaepa geꞌamo kanale alagepa gemo haneꞌneno apakupi mafaꞌnemo alino alagepa huno neꞌate. Ala kava neꞌmo faigoko geꞌamoꞌmo aino ataginovano nosifa alagepa huno haneꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo oꞌageꞌnaya vayaꞌmo alino apaya maleꞌnigeꞌa apakesamo neꞌafiye.
\v 8 Keꞌaepa gemo api gemo haneꞌnigeꞌa neꞌafiya vayaꞌmogi apamogaga neꞌaiye. Ani kava hiyo, ina kava osiyo, huno huꞌniya gemo hosu gemo ohaneꞌnifa alagepa geꞌageꞌmo haneꞌneno apaulagamo alino ayakeno apateteno alino alagepa huno neꞌapate.
\v 9 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo koli huteꞌa mono nehaya kavaꞌmo yaveyave kavaꞌmo haneꞌneno muki afinaꞌmo hanege hanege huno hanegaiye. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alino fako huno neꞌapateya gemo alagi lama geꞌageꞌmo haneꞌneno fatago gemo haneꞌniye.
\v 10 Alopa monieꞌmo hapaꞌye nehiya kava huꞌa geꞌamo afisayafeꞌmo magoꞌe huno hapaꞌye hisiya agufa gemo haneꞌniye. Magoꞌe huno hagaꞌage gemo haneꞌneno kevegeve anumoꞌmo nehiya hagaꞌamo ago aeno agaseno haneꞌniye.
\v 11 Gekamoꞌmo, ehekae, huno nehigeꞌnaeꞌmo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌnamo afiteꞌnaeꞌmo atete nehuve. Gekamo akame nehaya vayaꞌmogimo alopa miyaꞌapimo aligae.
\p 
\v 12 Muki vayaꞌmogimo muki hosu kavaꞌapifatiꞌmo aeꞌa kasalo nepaya kavaꞌapimo alagepa huꞌa afaꞌa oꞌagegae. Ala kava nene, huꞌna, hosu kavaꞌmo haneꞌniye, huꞌna oꞌageꞌna huꞌnova hosu kavaꞌnimo aeka kalo paeka atalo.
\v 13 Hosu kavaꞌmo haneꞌniye, huꞌna ago ageꞌnova hosu kavaꞌmo halate osisuvafeꞌmo natafauka nato fiku yanageno ani hosu kavaꞌmoꞌa yagaino nategaiyanagi. Ani kava huka naha maesanageꞌnaeꞌmo vaiꞌmo oꞌaliꞌna hogote hosu kavaꞌmo aeno agaseꞌniya hosu kavaꞌmo osuguve.
\v 14 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, miya faika nateteka himamuꞌnimo alika neꞌnamina vekaꞌnimo maiꞌnane. Navayafatiꞌmo nehuva geꞌnimo ago afiteka naipafiꞌmo nagesamo neꞌafuva kavaꞌnimo kaulagafatiꞌmo ago nagetekaeꞌmo, alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌnane, huka hisanafekeꞌmo neꞌnahaiye.
\c 22
\s1 Kalaisiꞌa faliꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ava gemo huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Gotiꞌnimogae Gotiꞌnimogae, na kava higekaeꞌmo nataleka uꞌnane. Naha mao, huꞌna keya aeꞌna ge nehuvaꞌmonanafa na kava higekaeꞌmo nataleka uka afagiꞌaleꞌmo maiꞌneka naha noꞌmane.
\v 2 O Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, felugamo keya aeꞌna ge huꞌnogekaeꞌmo geꞌnimo oꞌafiꞌnane. Haniꞌilagaꞌeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge huꞌnogekaeꞌmo naha oꞌmaeꞌnanageꞌna maiꞌna falu nosuve.
\v 3 Kagaefeꞌmo ge huꞌnovaꞌmonanafa kaote vekamo maiꞌnane. Kaote vekamo maiꞌnanageꞌapaeꞌmo Isaleli vayaꞌmogimo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa nekatae.
\v 4 Laginago vayaꞌmogimo kagaefekeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago huꞌnagekaeꞌmo hapa maeꞌnane.
\v 5 Kagaefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌa ge huꞌnagekaeꞌmo apakufamo alika katika apateꞌnane. Kagaefekeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌnagekaeꞌmo hapa maeꞌnanageꞌapaeꞌmo apaipamoꞌmo kana osuꞌniye.
\p 
\v 6 Huꞌnayaꞌmonanafa nagaemo vayakana huꞌna oꞌmaiꞌnofa hagifagana huꞌna maiꞌnogeꞌapaeꞌmo ina agufa vekamo maiꞌniye, huꞌa huteꞌa apakameꞌya neꞌnamiye.
\v 7 Muki vayaꞌmogimo nageteꞌapaeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa neꞌnatae. Sagani huꞌa natege keka huꞌa natege huteꞌapaeꞌmo,
\v 8 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa ha maesiyafeꞌmo agesamo afiꞌniyana na kava higenoꞌaeꞌmo ha noꞌmae. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa amuse huno neꞌatesiyaꞌmoꞌmo na kava higenoꞌaeꞌmo ha noꞌmae, huꞌa nehae.
\v 9 Nehayaꞌmonanafa kagaemo itaꞌnimoꞌmo alagepa huka ha maeꞌnanageno alino nateꞌniye. Nute mafaꞌnemo maiꞌnogekaeꞌmo alagepa huka yagaika nateꞌnanageꞌna afaꞌa maiꞌnove.
\v 10 Nagaemo itaꞌnimoꞌmo alino nateꞌniya afinatetiꞌmo kagaefekeꞌmo nagesamo afiꞌna fatago hume hume eꞌnove. Itaꞌnimoꞌmo alino nateꞌniya afinatetiꞌmo muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo Gotiꞌnimogamo maige maige huka maiꞌnane.
\v 11 Nagufaleꞌmo hanageke yaꞌmo afole neꞌaigeꞌapaeꞌmo naha maesaya vayaꞌmo oꞌmaiꞌnayanagi nataleka uka afagiꞌaleꞌmo oꞌmaiyo.
\v 12 Kame vayaꞌnimogi Masani kotega afela ve pulumaka anagaꞌmogi nehaya kava huꞌa faiꞌa ku aiꞌa neꞌnatae.
\v 13 Laiyoni anagaꞌmogi apaka tegeꞌapaeꞌmo kae kae nehaya kava huꞌa nagaetegamo apavayamo aka nehae.
\v 14 Aniꞌmo aliꞌa mopafiꞌmo lakitalageno lamino hano nehiya kava huno lokiyaꞌnimo alagi ohaneꞌniye. Muki nayamufaꞌnimo uno aeno haniꞌniya nayamufamo aino hatu maeꞌniye. Naipamoꞌmo ani hegekana huꞌniye.
\v 15 Hapamo leno hau nehiya kava huno lokiyaꞌnimo hau huꞌnigeno lokiyaꞌnimo alagi ohaneꞌniye. Ani kava huno navenafuꞌnamo hau huꞌnigeno navayafiꞌmo aeno kamaeꞌniye. Nataleꞌnanageꞌna faligefeꞌmo nehuve.
\v 16 Afela kalamogi afumo hapaesayafeꞌmo faiꞌa ku aiꞌa neꞌapataya kava huꞌa hosu vayaꞌmogimo faiꞌa ku aiꞌa neꞌnatae. Nayapiꞌmo nili aige naiyafiꞌmo nili aige huꞌnae.
\v 17 Muki nayamufaꞌnimo afole aiꞌnigeꞌna ageꞌnove. Kame vayaꞌnimogimo nageteꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiye.
\v 18 Muki kukenaꞌaꞌnimo aliꞌa fako huꞌa aliteꞌa yatala kukenaꞌnilefeꞌmo yokalo leteꞌapaeꞌmo aeno apakaseꞌniya vekamoꞌmo aliꞌniye.
\v 19 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, afagiꞌaleꞌmo uka oꞌmaiꞌneka naha neꞌmana vekaꞌnimogae, huꞌna, malage huka eka naha mao.
\v 20 Nagupi mafaꞌnemo lageso osisiyafeꞌmo naha maeteka afela kalagana agufa vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 21 Alopa afela laiyonimo avayafatiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato. Afela ve pulumaka anagaꞌmogimo oꞌnahaesayafeꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\p Keya aeꞌna ge nehugekaeꞌmo nageleꞌmo aliꞌnane.
\v 22 Naganaꞌnimogifeꞌmo kagaemo naha maeꞌnana kavafeꞌmo nava gemo huꞌna aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paiguve. Aliꞌa anupa huꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌai folagaꞌapifatiꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huguve.
\v 23 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo koli hutetapa mono nehaya vayaꞌmogitapamo ala agiꞌamo amiyo. Yekopu nofi vayaꞌmogitapamo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Isaleli nofi vayaꞌmogitapamo agaefekeꞌmo mono hiyo.
\v 24 Hanageke yaꞌmo neꞌaliya vayaꞌmo apataleno aino afe leno akameꞌya noꞌapamifa keya aeꞌa ge nehagenoꞌaeꞌmo geꞌapimo afiteno hapa neꞌmae.
\v 25 Asole vayaꞌmo aliꞌa anupa huꞌa neꞌmaiya folagapatiꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huguve. Kagaefeꞌmo mono nehaya vayaꞌai apaulagaleꞌmo kagaefeꞌmo ani kava huguve, huꞌna kaha paiꞌnova kavaꞌmo huguve.
\v 26 Ala apakiꞌapimo oꞌaliꞌa yagu yaga huꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogi neꞌyaꞌmo neꞌa apamu hugae. Agaefeꞌmo kahauya huꞌa agesayafeꞌmo neꞌaya vayaꞌmogi Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hugae. Muki afinaꞌmo yuꞌilaga vekatapimo alagepa huno maigiye.
\p 
\v 27 Muki ma mopamo loleꞌe loleꞌe atupaleꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo apakesamo afiteꞌa aiꞌa atagi neꞌa agaetegamo egae. Muki alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌmogimo agaefekeꞌmo mono hugae.
\v 28 Ala kava neꞌmo kini vekamo maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo muki alu nofi vayaꞌaiteꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌaiteꞌeꞌmo yagaino neꞌapate.
\v 29 Ma mopafiꞌmo alagepa huꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogimo neꞌyaꞌmo neteꞌa agaefeꞌmo mono hugae. Muki vayaꞌmogi apakaiꞌapimo afaꞌa hapa oꞌmaeꞌa faligefe huꞌnisaya vayaꞌmogi apaleꞌyamo faiꞌa ape huꞌa maigae.
\v 30-31 Afole aisaya vayaꞌmogimo aliꞌyaꞌamo aligae. Vayaꞌmogi aliꞌa oꞌapateꞌnayanageꞌa henagaꞌamo afole aisaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo Ala kava nefeꞌmo ava gemo huge lagufamo alino katino lateꞌniye huꞌa huge huꞌa maigae.
\c 23
\s1 Sipisipileꞌmo neꞌyagaigeꞌa alagepa huꞌa neꞌmaiya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Vayaꞌmogimo sipisipileꞌmo yagaiꞌa neꞌapataya kava huno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa yagaino neꞌnateyanageꞌna mago yafeꞌmo alagi kafu osuguve.
\v 2 Agaemo sipisipi anagaꞌmogimo muki hegafatalili kahaumo neꞌnaya yategamo alino havaeno neꞌnate. Uno hogoteteno navalelino age noꞌaiya ani haigiꞌale ani haigiꞌaleꞌmo neꞌviye.
\v 3 Nagupi mafaꞌnemoꞌmo halate alino alagepa huno neꞌate. Agaemo agiꞌalefeꞌmo fatago kavaꞌmo hisuvafeꞌmo alu kate alu kateꞌmo navalelino neꞌviye.
\v 4 He, nagaemo uꞌna kagoꞌmufilagamo falisuva ulunapiꞌmo faleꞌna haiꞌna umenitata nehugekaeꞌmo nagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeka maiꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo muki alu hosu kava alu hosu kavafeꞌmo alagi koli osuguve. Kayokaletiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika natege aino kalagifa hayopa kayokaletiꞌmo yagaika natege nehukaeꞌmo naipamo alika falu huka neꞌnatane.
\v 5 Kagaemo kame vayaꞌnimogi apaulagaleꞌmo neꞌyaꞌnimo aliꞌna nesuvafeꞌmo hipaꞌnileꞌmo naulagaleꞌmo neꞌmalane. Kagaemo nagenopafiꞌmo uvelimo lakika faleka neꞌnatane. Aniꞌmo kapuꞌnifiꞌmo alika lakiꞌnanageno lamino havai teteno aino vali nelamiye.
\v 6 Ma mopafiꞌmo maime maime neꞌvisugenoꞌaeꞌmo alagepa yaꞌmo nakame nakame huno alino namige namige huno maiteno hau huno nategaiye. Hutesigeꞌna Ala kava neꞌmo noꞌafiꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo haiꞌna maige maige huꞌna maiguve.
\c 24
\s1 Ha le konali kini vekaeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ma mopamo Ala kava neꞌmo mopamae. Muki ma mopafiꞌmo haneꞌniya yaꞌamo agaiꞌa yaꞌageꞌmo haneꞌniye. Ma mopaꞌe ma mopafi vayaꞌeꞌmo agaiꞌa mopamo hanege agaiꞌa vayaꞌmo maige huꞌnae.
\v 2 Agaemo ma mopamo solovala aniꞌmo agotofuleꞌmo alo hu maleꞌniye. Aniꞌmo agotofuleꞌmo faino ateꞌniye.
\p 
\v 3 Haiya agufa vayaꞌmogimo Ala kava neꞌmo aveleꞌmo afaꞌa haiꞌa maigae. Haiya agufa vayaꞌmogimo aote mono noꞌafiꞌmo afaꞌa fale haiꞌa maigae.
\v 4 Apayateꞌmo oꞌaniꞌyaꞌmo ofaiꞌnisiya yaveyave apaipa vayaꞌmogimae. Afa yatefeꞌmo mono osuge apagoꞌyamo ataleteꞌa aigofe gemo osuge nehisaya vayaꞌmogimae.
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fiku hapa maeno apamigiye. Gotiꞌa apakae apakufamo alino katino neꞌapateya vekamoꞌmo fatago kavaꞌamo alino apamigiye.
\v 6 Alino apamisigeꞌa Yekopu Gotiꞌamoꞌmo agesayafeꞌmo kahauya nehae. Kaugosafiꞌmo kagesayafeꞌmo kahauya nehae.
\p 
\v 7 Yafa lafi kegiꞌya kate kitamo yakitapa ateyo. Hanege hanege huno nehaneya mono note kitamo yakitapa ateyo. Yakitapa ategenoꞌao ha le konali kini vekamo faleno haineno.
\v 8 Ani ha le konali kini vekamo ina laꞌae. Ala kava neꞌmo himamu lokiyaꞌaꞌe vekamae. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa himamuꞌaletiꞌmo kame huno neꞌapateya vekamae.
\v 9 Yafa lafi kegiꞌya kate kitamo yakitapa ateyo. Hanege hanege huno nehaneya mono note kitamo yakitapa ateyo. Yakitapa ategenoꞌao ha le konali kini vekamo faleno haineno.
\v 10 Ani ha le konali kini vekamo ina laꞌae. Asole ami vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino neꞌapateya kini vekamo ha le konali kini vekamo maiꞌniye.
\c 25
\s1 Hosu kavaꞌaeꞌmo agesa afinoꞌaeꞌmo nunumu huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kagaefekeꞌmo nunumu nehuꞌnaeꞌmo nagupi mafaꞌnemo aliꞌna asaga nehuve.
\v 2 O Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, naha maegane, huꞌna nagesamo afiꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo fiku yanageꞌa kame vayaꞌnimogi aeꞌa nagasesageno navagage hugiyanagi oꞌnatalo.
\v 3 He, muki vayaꞌmogimo kagava neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmo hapa maegenoꞌao apavagage osino. Apakaetegamo mago hosu kavaꞌmo osuꞌnayaꞌmonanafa fiku hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo hapa oꞌmaeka afaꞌa apatalegenoꞌao apavagage hino.
\p 
\v 4 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahauꞌninageka visuva kaꞌmo nave liyo. Ani kateꞌmo visuvafeꞌmo alika naya malo.
\v 5 Nagufamo alika katika neꞌnatana Gotigamo maiꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo lama gekamo akame hisuvafeꞌmo alika naya malo. Muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo kagava neꞌmauve.
\p 
\v 6 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, akeyaꞌvilagatiꞌmo alagepa huka kahau huka apatege kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauge huka neꞌmaina kavafeꞌmo kagesamo afiyo.
\v 7 Neya vekamo maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo huge gekamo ago amagiꞌna atalege huꞌnova kavafeꞌmo kagesamo oꞌafiyo. O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahau huka apatege alagepa huka hapa maege huka maiꞌnekaeꞌmo nagaefeꞌmo kagesamo afiyo.
\p 
\v 8 Ala kava neꞌmo alagepa fatago vekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo hosu vayaꞌmogi alagepa kateꞌmo visayafeꞌmo alino apaya malegaiye.
\v 9 Agaemo fatago kavaꞌaletiꞌmo yagu yaga kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo alino ho huno neꞌapate. Agaemo yagu yaga kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo kaꞌamo alino apave ligiye.
\v 10 Agaemo kotalakemo hu maleꞌniya geꞌamo akame huge avayafatiꞌmo huꞌniya geꞌamo afige huꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo hau huno neꞌapateya kateꞌe geꞌamo akame nehiya kateꞌeꞌmo apavalelino neꞌviye.
\v 11 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, ala kagikalefeꞌmo hosu kavaꞌnimo alika atalo. Asole hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo alika atalo.
\p 
\v 12 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌmo ina lagimo maiꞌnae. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa afaꞌa alino apaya malesigeꞌa alagepa kateꞌmo ugae.
\v 13 Apakaemo alagepa huꞌa maisageꞌa apakinago vayaꞌmogi ma mopamo aligae.
\v 14 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa agaefeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌmo alino fala ki maleꞌniya geꞌamo hapa paigiye. Hapa paiteno kotalake hu maleꞌniya gemo aepaꞌamo alino apave ligiye.
\v 15 Agaemo natafauno nateꞌniya umenifatiꞌmo hatu maeno nategaiyaꞌmofeꞌmo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo aulu heꞌna neꞌagove.
\p 
\v 16 Nagaemo nagaiꞌnigeꞌmo magokeꞌageꞌmo maiꞌneꞌna kana yaꞌmo aliꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo aika afe leka nagaemo nageteka kahau huka nato.
\v 17 Naipafiꞌmo haneꞌniya kana yaꞌnimoꞌa lusi kava huno kositeno afole aiꞌniyanagi hanageke yapatiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 18 Kana yaꞌmo alige nagafu kige huꞌna maiꞌnisugeka nagetekaeꞌmo muki hosu kavaꞌnimo alika atalo.
\v 19 Kame vayaꞌnimo asole vayaꞌmo maiꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo apakaefeꞌmo kagesamo afiyo. Apakaemo nagaefeꞌmo alagi ohapauꞌnigeꞌa apaini huꞌa neꞌnatae.
\v 20 Nagupi mafaꞌneleꞌmo yagaika ateꞌneka hosu kavategatiꞌmo navalelika uka naote nato. Nagaemo kagaefekeꞌmo, naha maegane, huꞌna nagesamo afiteꞌna maiꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo navagage osino.
\v 21 Nagaemo kagava maiꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo naha maegeꞌnao lama ge huꞌna fatago kavakamo akame huteꞌna alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌna maino.
\p 
\v 22 O Gotiyo, huꞌna kagaemo Isaleli vayaꞌmo hanageke yapiꞌmo maiꞌnagi miya faika hatu maeka apato.
\c 27
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa naha maesigeꞌna aeꞌna apakasegauve, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmo ha le yaꞌnimo aepa vekamo maiꞌneno nagufamo alino katino neꞌnateya vekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo ina lagifeꞌmo koliꞌapimo huguve. Ala kava neꞌmo himamuꞌnimo aepa vekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo ina lagifeꞌmo atete huguve.
\v 2 Hosu vayaꞌmo kame vayaꞌnimogi nagaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo nagufamo nahaeꞌa nesayafeꞌmo nagaetegamo eꞌapaeꞌmo apagoꞌya faiꞌa asagauꞌa aiꞌnae.
\v 3 Asole vayaꞌmogimo kame huꞌa natesayafeꞌmo eꞌa maiꞌnisageꞌnaeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo atete osugiye. Kame huꞌa natesayana naipamoꞌmo lokiya vaigiye.
\v 4 Nagaemo Gotiꞌa magoke yaꞌmo alino namisiyafeꞌmo nahauꞌniyanageꞌna ani yaꞌmo alisuvafekeꞌmo kahauya huguve. Nagaemo Ala kava neꞌmo nopiꞌmo muki afaꞌa maisuva afinaꞌmo maiꞌneꞌna Ala kava neꞌmo konali yaꞌamo aulu heꞌna ageteꞌnaeꞌmo alopa mono noꞌafiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌna ge huꞌna afi gesuvafeꞌmo maigesuve.
\v 5 Hanageke yaꞌmo afole aisiya afinaꞌmo alino fala kino natege alopa mono noꞌafiꞌmo alino fala kino natege huteno yatala yafateꞌmo nasaga huno faino nategaiye.
\v 6 Nagaemo kame vayaꞌnimo aeꞌna apakaseteꞌna alopa mono noꞌafiꞌmo ofalinimo amiteꞌna alopa gefatiꞌmo nehuꞌnaeꞌmo namogaga aiguve. Ala kava nefekeꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo yokemo huteꞌna agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huguve.
\p 
\v 7 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kagaefeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge hisugekaeꞌmo geꞌnimo afiyo. Kahau huka nateteka geꞌnileꞌmo aeka atagaina huka naha paiyo.
\v 8 Kagaemo nagaefeꞌmo hukaeꞌmo nagaefeꞌmo kahauya hulika eno huka nehanageꞌnaeꞌmo kagaefeꞌmo nagaemo kahauya huliꞌna uguve, huꞌna nehuve.
\p 
\v 9 Kaugosamo alika fala kiliꞌneka kaipamo leka nateteka aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamo naha faika oꞌnatalo. O Gotiyo, huꞌna, naha maeꞌnananagi kakameꞌyamo namiteka nataleka oꞌuvo.
\v 10 Itaꞌni afoꞌnilaꞌmoganimo anakameꞌyamo namisaꞌana Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa yagaino nategaiye.
\v 11 Kame vayaꞌnimo maiꞌnayanagi kagae kaꞌmo nave ligeꞌna agetesugeka ani kateꞌmo navalelika uvo.
\v 12 Kame vayaꞌnimogi aigofe gemo huge kamagigune huꞌa huge nehayanagi navaleka apayapiꞌmo oꞌapamiyo.
\v 13 Nagaemo ofaliꞌna afaꞌa maiꞌnisugeno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alagepa yaꞌamo alino namigiye, huꞌna nagesamo afiꞌna fatago nehuve.
\v 14 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo agava maiyo. Lokiya vaitapa maiꞌnigenoꞌao lokiya vaino lapateno. Ala kava nefekeꞌmo agava maiyo, huꞌna nehuve.
\c 32
\s1 Hosu kavaꞌaeꞌmo aeno hakalo huno ha paiꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Gotiꞌa keꞌaepa geꞌamo amagiꞌa ataleꞌnaya kavaꞌapimo alino atalege hosu kavaꞌapimo aeno ati kaeno atalege huꞌnisiya vayaꞌmogimo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\v 2 Gotiꞌa hosu kavaꞌapimo haneꞌniye, huno nosigeꞌa humi nami kavaꞌmo osuꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\v 3 Nagaemo hosu kavaꞌnieꞌmo aeꞌna hakalo osuꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo aviꞌya huge huge huꞌna maiꞌnogeno lokiyaꞌnimo ago hano huꞌniye.
\v 4 Ani kava huꞌna maiꞌnogekaeꞌmo felugaꞌe haniꞌilagaꞌeꞌmo kana yaꞌmo alika namiꞌnanagenoꞌaeꞌmo amuko nehiya afinaꞌmo aniꞌmo leno nelaneya kava huno lokiyaꞌnimo ago hano huꞌniye.
\v 5 Ani afinaꞌmo hosu kavaꞌnieꞌmo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna kaha paiꞌnova afinaꞌmo hosu kavaꞌnimo aeꞌna ati okaeꞌnove. Nagaemo, keꞌaepa gekamo ago amagiꞌna ataleꞌnova kavaꞌnieꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmogaeꞌmo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna kaha paiguve, huꞌna huꞌnogekaeꞌmo hosu kavaꞌnimo ago alika ataleꞌnane.
\p 
\v 6 Ani kava nehanaꞌmofeꞌmo muki kakame nehaya vayaꞌmogimo kahauya huꞌa kagesaya afinaꞌmo nunumu hiyo. Aniꞌmo henoꞌaeꞌmo hapaopaleꞌmo oꞌmegaiye.
\v 7 Kagaepiꞌmo eꞌna fala kiꞌnisugekaeꞌmo hanageke yaꞌmo oꞌalisuvafeꞌmo yagaika nategane. Kagaemo nagufamo alika katika natesana yokemo nehisugekaeꞌmo faika ku aika yagaika nategane.
\p 
\v 8 Gotiꞌa hunoꞌaeꞌmo, nagaemo visana kaꞌmo alagepa huꞌna aliꞌna kaya maleteꞌna aliꞌna kave liguve, huno huꞌniye. Naulagaletiꞌmo visana kaꞌmo aliꞌna kave liguve.
\v 9 Hosimogi apakesamo oꞌafiꞌnageꞌa vayaꞌmogigeꞌmo geꞌapimo afisayafeꞌmo apavayafiꞌmo aenimo ateteꞌa nofi aeteꞌa yagaiꞌa apateꞌneꞌa aliꞌa api aiꞌa neꞌapatae. Hosigana hutapa oꞌmaiyo.
\v 10 Hosu vayaꞌmo lusi kava huꞌa kana yaꞌmo aligayaꞌmonanafa Ala kava nefeꞌmo apakesamo neꞌafiya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo hau huno neꞌapateya kavaꞌamoꞌmo yagaino ku aino apategaiye.
\v 11 Alagepa vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava nefekeꞌmo lapamogaga aitetapa amuse hiyo. Geꞌamo akame nehaya vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, lapamogaga neꞌaitapaeꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo hiyo.
\c 34
\s1 Fatago vayaꞌmogi ge nehageno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa neꞌafiye, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Nagaemo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo muki afinaꞌae afinaꞌaeꞌmo hao ke hegauve. Agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huge huge huꞌna maiguve.
\v 2 Agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna atesugeꞌapaeꞌmo apakufamo aliꞌa afepi neꞌataya vayaꞌmogi afiteꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga aigae.
\v 3 Nagaegiꞌeꞌmo hutaeꞌmo, Ala kava neꞌmo ala agi vekamo maiꞌniye, huta magokepi higetao. Agiꞌaleꞌmo magokepi alita asaga higetao.
\v 4 Koli huꞌna maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo naha maesiyafeꞌmo kahauya huꞌna nunumu huꞌnogeno afitenoꞌaeꞌmo naha maeꞌnigeꞌna koli osuꞌna afaꞌa maiꞌnove.
\v 5 Vayaꞌmogimo ageteꞌapaeꞌmo amuse huꞌa maiꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo ani kava hutapa agegenoꞌao lapaipamoꞌmo kana osino.
\v 6 Nagaemo lokiya vekamo oꞌmaiꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge huꞌnogeno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa afiꞌniye. Afitenoꞌaeꞌmo muki hanageke yapatiꞌmo nagufamo alino katino nateꞌniye.
\v 7 Ala kava neꞌmo enisole vekaꞌamoꞌmo Ala kava nefeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino ku aino apateteno apakufamo alino katino neꞌapate.
\v 8 Ala kava neꞌmo kanale vekamo maiꞌniye hutapa agegayanagi ageyo. Ala kava nepiꞌmo fala kiꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\v 9 Lapaote vayaꞌmo maiꞌnayanagi Ala kava nefeꞌmo koli hutetapa akame hiyo. Koli huteꞌa akame nehaya vayaꞌmogimo kafu osugae.
\v 10 Laiyoni anaꞌaumogi apaka neteyaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmo agesayafeꞌmo kahauya nehaya vayaꞌmogimo muki alagepa yaꞌmo aliteꞌapaeꞌmo kafu nosae.
\p 
\v 11 Mafaꞌne anagaꞌmogitapamo etapa geꞌnimo afiyo. Ala kava nefekeꞌmo koli hutetapa akame hisaya kavaꞌmo aliꞌna lapaya malegauvanagi eyo.
\v 12 Alagepa hutapa yatala afinaꞌmo maiꞌnetapa lapamogaga aisayafeꞌmo lapauꞌnifiye.
\v 13 Inagi lapauꞌnisiyana hosu gemo osuge aigofe gemo osuge hisayafeꞌmo alagepa hutapa yagaitapa lapateyo.
\v 14 Hosu kavategatiꞌmo maitapa halove hutapa eta alagepa kavakeꞌmo hiyo. Kaveta osutapa alagepa hutapa magokepi lokaetapa maisayafeꞌmo kahauya hutapa vegala aeyo.
\p 
\v 15 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alagepa kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino apateꞌneno aukaya huꞌa ge nehaya geꞌapimo neꞌafiye.
\v 16 Neꞌafiyaꞌmonanafa hosu kava nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo kame huno neꞌapategeꞌa faliꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo ago apake nekaniye.
\v 17 Fatago vayaꞌmogimo keya aeꞌa ge nehageno afitenoꞌaeꞌmo muki hanageke yapatiꞌmo apakufamo alino katino neꞌapate.
\v 18 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa yulagefa neꞌaiya vayaꞌai hapaopaleꞌmo maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo afepilagamo faleꞌa haiꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌai apakufamo alino katino neꞌapate.
\p 
\v 19 Alagepa vayaꞌmogimo lusi hanageke yaꞌmo neꞌaliyaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa muki hanageke yapatiꞌmo apakufamo alino katino neꞌapate.
\v 20 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa kanale vekaleꞌmo alagepa huno yagaino ateꞌnigeno magoke ayamufamo alagi lo oꞌaeꞌniye.
\v 21 Hosu vayaꞌmo hosu kavaꞌapimoꞌmo apamagisigeꞌa faligae. Alagepa kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo nohapaiya vayaꞌmo kayoꞌmo apamigiye.
\v 22 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vayaꞌai apakufamo miya faino alino katino neꞌapate. Agaepiꞌmo eꞌa fala nekiya vayapatiꞌmo magoke vekaeꞌmo, hosu vekamo maiꞌnane, huno huteno alagi alino hafaino oꞌatalegaiye.
\c 36
\s1 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo hosu kava huꞌa maiꞌnayaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa vayaꞌamo hapa neꞌmae, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Gotiꞌa hosu vayaꞌai hosu kavaꞌapieꞌmo apava gemo huno naha paiꞌniya gemo naipafiꞌmo haneꞌniyana apakaemo Gotiꞌmo apakameꞌya amiteꞌa koli nosae.
\v 2 Ala vayaꞌmo maiꞌnone, huꞌa nehayaꞌmofeꞌmo Gotiꞌa hosu kavatimo oꞌagege hosu kavaꞌmo nehae, huno osuge nehiye, huꞌa apakesamo neꞌafiye.
\v 3 Hosu gemo huge aigofe gemo huge huꞌa neꞌmaiye. Afiteꞌa ageꞌnaya kavaꞌe alagepa kavaꞌapiꞌeꞌmo ataleꞌa afaꞌa neꞌmaiye.
\v 4 Hipaꞌapileꞌmo havaeꞌa maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo hisayafekeꞌmo apakesamo neꞌafiye. Muki nehaya kavaꞌapimo hosu kavaꞌageꞌmo haneꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo muki hosu kavaꞌapieꞌmo, haꞌao, alagi oꞌnahaiye, huꞌa nosae.
\p 
\v 5 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, olataleka lagaefeꞌmo kahau huka nelatana kavakamoꞌmo lusi yatala yaꞌmo kokuꞌnapiꞌmo nehaiya agufa yatala yakana huno haneꞌniye. Ani kavaꞌmo huguve, huka nehana gekamo alagi amagika oꞌataleka akame huka nehana kavakamoꞌmo ina kava huno hiyateꞌmo nehaiya agufa yakana huno haneꞌniye.
\v 6 Alagepa kavakamoꞌmo avegana huno lusi yaꞌmo haneꞌniye. Alagepa huka alika fako huka neꞌapatana kavakamoꞌmo solovala aniꞌmo vasilonagana huno haneꞌniye. Ala kava nene, huꞌna, vayatenagi afulenagi yagagafalenagi huka yagaika neꞌapatanageꞌa afaꞌa neꞌmaiye.
\p 
\v 7 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, olataleka lagaefeꞌmo kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauꞌniya kavakamoꞌmo alagepa kanale kavaꞌmo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo lahauꞌniye. Kahakumo auneꞌafiꞌmo uta fala kita neꞌmaune.
\v 8 Lusi neꞌyaꞌmo nelaminageta alita neꞌnonagenoꞌaeꞌmo lamu nepae. Nelaminagetaeꞌmo lamogaga aisunafeꞌmo alopa anipatiꞌmo aniꞌmo neꞌnone.
\v 9 Maige maige huta maisuna kavaꞌmo aepa vekamo maiꞌnane. Ha le yakamoꞌmo aeno ha nelegetaeꞌmo ha le yakamo ageta alagepa huta neꞌagone.
\v 10 Kageꞌnaya vayaꞌmo oꞌapataleka magoꞌe huka kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahaino. Api kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌaitegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo huvo.
\v 11 Himuꞌnamuꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo nagaetegamo oꞌmesayafeꞌmo esaya kateꞌmo kaꞌmo akani malo. Hosu vayaꞌmogimo aliꞌa nahafaiꞌa oꞌnatalesayafeꞌmo naha mao.
\p 
\v 12 Ageyo, huꞌna, Gotiꞌa hosu vayaꞌmo apamagiꞌnigeꞌa mopafiꞌmo asagauꞌa aiteꞌa havaeꞌa maiꞌnae. Halate he otigae.
\c 37
\s1 Ala kava nefeꞌmo agava neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogimo ma mopamo alisaya kavafe huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Hosu vayaꞌmogi nehaya kavaꞌapieꞌmo lapakesa alaꞌamo afitetapa lapausoli osiyo. Hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌa neꞌmaiyanageta apakaekana huta maigesune, hutapa osiyo.
\v 2 Kahaumo malage huno leno falu neteya kava huꞌa malage huꞌa falu tegae. Aise yosamo neꞌvaiya kava huꞌa vaigae.
\v 3 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo lapakesamo afita fatago hutetapa alagepa kavaꞌmo higenoꞌao lapa maesigetapa ma mopafiꞌmo alagepa hutapa maigayanagi.
\v 4 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo amuse hutapa ategenoꞌao lapaipafiꞌmo lapauꞌnisiya kavaꞌmo alino lapamino.
\v 5 Lapakaemo lapakesamo afitapaeꞌmo lagaetegamo na agufa kavaꞌmo afole aisifi, hutapa lapakesa afisaya kavaꞌmo alitapa Ala kava neꞌmo amitetapa agaefekeꞌmo lapakesamo afita fatago higeno lapa maeno.
\v 6 Lapa maesigenoꞌaeꞌmo alagepa kavatapimo yegekana huno aeno ha legaiye. Ani kava huno fatago kavatapimo vayaꞌai apaulagaleꞌmo alino afole aino ategaiye.
\v 7 Ala kava neꞌmo aulagaleꞌmo afaꞌa maiꞌnetapaeꞌmo agava maige maige hutapa maiyo. Hosu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa alagepa huꞌa neꞌmaiya kavafeꞌmo lapakesa alaꞌamo afitetapa lapausoli osiyo.
\p 
\v 8 Lapaipamo oletapa hosu kavategamo alagi lapayamukiki osiyo. Lapakaemo hosu kavaꞌmo hisayafeꞌmo lapakesa alaꞌamo afitetapa ataletapa lapausoli osiyo.
\v 9 Hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo kayoꞌmo aliteꞌa faligayaꞌmonanafa Ala kava nefeꞌmo agava neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogimo ma mopamo aligae.
\v 10 Aise afinaꞌmo utesigeꞌa hosu vayaꞌmo alagi lageso hisagetapaeꞌmo maiꞌnaya kotegamo utapa kahauya hutapa oꞌapakegae.
\v 11 Oꞌapakegayaꞌmonanafa falu fala apaipa vayaꞌmogimo ma mopamo aliteꞌa alagepa huꞌa magokepi lokaeꞌa maiꞌneꞌa apamogaga aiꞌa maigae.
\p 
\v 12 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo fatago vayaꞌaitegamo hosu kavaꞌmo hisayafeꞌmo ina kava hugune, ma kava hugune, huꞌa huteꞌa maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo hosu apaugosamo kaliꞌneꞌa maku make huꞌa neꞌapatae.
\v 13 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alino apagoꞌya lagauno apatalesiya afinafeꞌmo afaꞌa apakeno maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo apakaefeꞌmo kigi huno neꞌapate.
\v 14 Hosu vayaꞌmogi hosu yaꞌmo neꞌaliya vayaꞌe ina agufa vayaꞌeꞌmo afaꞌa apateꞌneꞌa api kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo naipeletiꞌmo apaisayafeꞌmo asagige atiletiꞌmo hapaesayafeꞌmo atimo alige huꞌa neꞌmaiye.
\v 15 Naipeꞌapimoꞌmo apakaiꞌapi apaipafiꞌmo aesigenoꞌaeꞌmo atiꞌapimo lo aegaiye.
\p 
\v 16 Mago fatago vekamoꞌa aise kagemi yaꞌamo haneꞌniya yaꞌamoꞌmo muki hosu vayaꞌai alopa kagemi yaꞌapimo ago aeno agaseno haneꞌniye.
\v 17 Na kava higenoꞌaeꞌmo ago aeno neꞌagase. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hosu vayaꞌai himamuꞌapimo alino hano huno atalegaiyaꞌmonanafa fatago vayaꞌaiteꞌmo alagepa huno yagaino neꞌapateyaꞌmofeꞌmae.
\v 18 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fatago vayaꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maigae, huno apakeꞌniye. Hetamaꞌapimo afaꞌa hanege hanege huno hanegaiye.
\v 19 Hanageke yaꞌmo afole aisiya afinaꞌmo hosu hanageke yaꞌmo oꞌalige kafu hisaya afinaꞌmo kafu osuge huꞌa alagepa huꞌa maigae.
\v 20 Maigayaꞌmonanafa hosu vayaꞌmo faligae. Kahaumo ausegana huꞌa maige halinagana huꞌa maige huꞌa neꞌmaiyaꞌmofeꞌmo alagi lageso hugae.
\p 
\v 21 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo fiku aliteꞌapaeꞌmo anonaꞌapilefeꞌmo noꞌapamiyaꞌmonanafa fatago vayaꞌmogimo hapau huꞌa apateteꞌa fiku neꞌapamiye.
\v 22 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fiku hapa neꞌmaeya vayaꞌmogimo ma mopamo alitesagenoꞌaeꞌmo huno faipa huno neꞌapateya vayaꞌmo alagi lageso hugae.
\p 
\v 23 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alagepa vayaꞌmogi hisaya kavaꞌmo aepa vekamo maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo ago hu maleꞌniye. Ani kava huno nehaya kavaꞌapimo agetenoꞌaeꞌmo amuse huno neꞌapate.
\v 24 Apakaemo asagauꞌa neꞌaigenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa apayateꞌmo alino he tino neꞌapateyaꞌmofeꞌmo alagi asagauꞌa oꞌaigae.
\p 
\v 25 Nagaemo yatala afinaꞌmo maime maime eꞌna hemenimo ago kosuna lovaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fatago vayaꞌamo apataleno uꞌniya kavaꞌamo oꞌagege mafaꞌneꞌapimogi neꞌyafeꞌmo aukaya huꞌnaya kavaꞌmo oꞌagege huꞌna oꞌageꞌnove.
\v 26 Fatago vayaꞌmogimo muki afinaꞌmo hapau huꞌa apateteꞌa magoꞌe yaꞌmo aliꞌa apamiteꞌa anonaꞌapilefeꞌmo neꞌapamiye. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa mafaꞌneꞌapimo fiku hapa maeno neꞌapamiye.
\p 
\v 27 Hosu kavaꞌmo ataletetapa alagepa kavakeꞌmo hiyo maige maige hutapa alagi maigayanagi.
\v 28 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alagepa kavafekeꞌmo hauꞌniyanageno aote vayaꞌamo alagi apataleno oꞌugiye. Yagaino apatenageꞌa hano osuꞌa maige maige huꞌa maigayaꞌmonanafa hosu vayaꞌai mafaꞌneꞌapimo alino hapa faino apatalegaiye.
\v 29 Fatago vayaꞌmo mago mopamo apamisigeꞌa aliteꞌa ani mopaleꞌmo maige maige huꞌa alagi maigae.
\p 
\v 30 Fatago vayaꞌmogimo ageteꞌa afiꞌnaya gemo huge gefiꞌmo alagepa huꞌa aliꞌa fako huꞌa afiteꞌa ge huge huꞌa neꞌmaiye.
\v 31 Goti keꞌaepa geꞌamo apaipafiꞌmo haneꞌniyanageꞌa afaꞌa aeꞌa halu oꞌvalegae.
\v 32 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo fatago vayaꞌmo apamagisayafeꞌmo aulu hapaeꞌa neꞌapakae.
\v 33 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hosu vayaꞌai apayapiꞌmo apavaleno oꞌapamino hapa maesigeꞌa hosu vayaꞌmogimo agoti huꞌa apateteꞌapaeꞌmo hosu vayane, huꞌa osugae.
\p 
\v 34 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo agava maiꞌnetapa geꞌamo afigenoꞌao lapakitapileꞌmo alino asaga huno lapateteno mopamo hakino lapamino. Agaemo hosu vayaꞌmo alino hapa faitalesigeꞌa visagetapa apakegae.
\v 35 Agovana hosu vekamoꞌa lokiya vaino yagaino apateno maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo mago yatala yosagana huno haino apakaseno maiꞌniye.
\v 36 Maiꞌniyaꞌmonanafa henagaꞌamo uꞌna agovana oꞌmaiꞌnigeꞌna ageꞌnove. Kahauya huꞌnovana oꞌageꞌnove.
\v 37 Lapakaemo alagepa vayaꞌmo aulu hapaetapa apaketetapaeꞌmo fatago vayaꞌmo apaketapa maiyo. Kanaꞌapimo hano hisigeꞌapaeꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maigayaꞌmonanafa
\v 38 gemo amagiꞌa neꞌatalaya vayaꞌmo alagi alino hano huno apatalegaiye.
\p 
\v 39 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fatago vayaꞌai apakufamo alino katino neꞌapateya kavaꞌamo aepa vekamo maiꞌniye. Hanageke yaꞌmo afole neꞌaiya afinaꞌmo himamuꞌaletiꞌmo hapa neꞌmae.
\v 40 Apakaemo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago nehayaꞌmofeꞌmo hatu maeno apateteno hosu vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo apavalelineno apakufamo alino katino neꞌapate.
\c 38
\s1 Hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnigeno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa kayoꞌmo alino amiꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kaipamo leka neꞌnatekaeꞌmo ge oꞌnahauvo. Kaipamo leka neꞌnatekaeꞌmo oꞌnamagiyo.
\v 2 Kevekaletiꞌmo nahaeꞌnanageno eno nagufafiꞌmo haniꞌnigekaeꞌmo kayatetiꞌmo namagiꞌnane.
\v 3 Kaipamo leka nateꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo nagufamoꞌmo alagi kanale nosiye. Hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo nayamufaꞌnimoꞌa alagi lokiya noꞌvaiye.
\v 4 Hosu kavaꞌnimoꞌmo anikana huno nagenopaleꞌmo aeno nati kaeꞌnigeꞌnaeꞌmo lusi kana yaꞌmo aliꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo aeno nagaseꞌniye.
\p 
\v 5 Negi kavaꞌmo huꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo namuꞌmo naleteno kolaꞌe oꞌeꞌmo huꞌnigeno atu neꞌaiye.
\v 6 Nagufamoꞌmo kanaꞌageꞌmo nahauꞌnigeꞌna muki afinaꞌmo ape huꞌnageꞌmo maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo yulagefa aiꞌna neꞌmauve.
\v 7 Amukomo nahauꞌnigeꞌna faligefeꞌmo nehuve.
\v 8 Lusi kava huno alagaꞌmo nahaeꞌnigeno lokiyaꞌnimo alagi ohaneꞌniye. Naipamoꞌmo kanale osuꞌnigeꞌna avovo nehuve.
\v 9 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, na agufa naipamo nekalufi huka ago nageꞌnanageꞌnaeꞌmo avovo nehuꞌna yulagefa neꞌaugeka afiꞌnane.
\v 10 Lutunopaꞌnifatiꞌmo fako pako nehigenoꞌaeꞌmo lokiyaꞌnimo alagi ohaneꞌniye. Naulagafatiꞌmo haniꞌageꞌmo huꞌniye.
\v 11 Lusi kaitaꞌmo nahauꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo nao vayaꞌe nafaluꞌnimogiꞌeꞌmo nagaetegamo oꞌmeꞌnae. Afamo anagaꞌnimogiꞌeꞌmo nataleꞌa uꞌa afagiꞌaleꞌmo maiꞌnae.
\v 12 Namagisayafeꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo aneꞌaimo hanagi maleꞌnae. Namagigefeꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo nagaetegamo hisaya kavafeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo apakesa afifi huꞌa maiꞌneꞌa namagisaya kafeꞌmo kahauya huꞌa agesayafeꞌmo nehae.
\p 
\v 13 Nehayaꞌmonanafa agesamo akanigeno gemo noꞌafiya vekagana huꞌna maiꞌneꞌna gemo noꞌafuve. Negi vekamoꞌmo age noꞌaiya vekagana huꞌna neꞌmauve.
\v 14 He, gemo nehaya gemo noꞌafiya vekagana huꞌna maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo gemo nohapauve.
\v 15 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kagava neꞌmauve. Ala kava neꞌnimo Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, geꞌnimo afiteka naha maegane.
\v 16 Hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnova kavafeꞌmo fiku yanageꞌa apamogaga aigae. Aeꞌna halu vale lamiꞌna asagauꞌna aisugeꞌapaeꞌmo fiku yanageꞌa ago aeta agaseꞌnone, huꞌa hugae.
\v 17 Asagauꞌna aigefeꞌmo nehugenoꞌaeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo nagafu nekiye.
\v 18 Hosu kavaꞌnieꞌmo nahau huteꞌnaeꞌmo aeꞌna hakalo nehuve.
\v 19 Apakaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo osuꞌnogeꞌa afaꞌa neꞌmaiya kame vayaꞌnimogiꞌeꞌmo lokiya vayaꞌageꞌmo maiꞌnae. Asole vayaꞌmogimo fiku apaini huꞌa neꞌnatae.
\v 20 Nagaemo alagepa kateꞌmo visuvafeꞌmo nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo kame huꞌa nateteꞌa alagepa kavaꞌnimo anonaꞌalefeꞌmo nagaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo nehae.
\p 
\v 21 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, nataleka oꞌuvo. O Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, afagiꞌaleꞌmo uka oꞌmaika nahaopaꞌalekeꞌmo eka maiyo.
\v 22 Ala kava neꞌnimogae, huꞌna, nagufamo alika katika neꞌnatana vekaꞌnimogamae, huꞌna, malage huka eka naha mao.
\c 40
\s1 Ge huꞌnigeno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa afiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo yokemo huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Nagaemo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa naha maesiyafeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge huteꞌnaeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo falu huꞌnigeꞌna agava maiꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo ape huno agetafo huꞌneno geꞌnimo afiꞌniye.
\v 2 Agaemo alagi hosu ive kelifatiꞌmo nayate alino heno navayu huno navalelino haino yafateꞌmo nateteno alagepa kateꞌmo visuvafeꞌmo alino lokiya vaino nateꞌniye.
\v 3 Saufa yokemo alino naya maleꞌnigeꞌna Goti agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huteꞌna ani yokemo nehuve. Asole vayaꞌmogimo nageteꞌapaeꞌmo koli huteꞌa Ala kava nefeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago huteꞌapaeꞌmo, laha maegaiye, huꞌa huteꞌa maigae.
\p 
\v 4 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago huteꞌapaeꞌmo, laha maegaiye, huꞌa nehaya vayaꞌmogimo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogagamo aigae. Apakaemo himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmofi aigofe gotiꞌapimogifeꞌmo mono nehaya vayaꞌmofi huno ala apakiꞌapimo noꞌapamiye.
\v 5 O Ala kava neꞌnimo Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, lagaetegamo alu kava alu kavaꞌmo huka aliꞌyaꞌmo aliteka laha maeꞌnane. Lagaefeꞌmo kagesa afifi huka neꞌmaine. Lagaemo lekana opaisuna agufa kavaꞌmo huka lagaefeꞌmo kagesamo neꞌafine. Nagaemo muki huꞌnana kavakaꞌe kagesamo neꞌafina kavakalefeꞌmo alagi alagepa huꞌna aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa opaiguve.
\p 
\v 6 Afumo amagiꞌa nekamiya kavaꞌe ofalinimo nekamiya kavaꞌefeꞌmo okahauꞌniye. Kagaemo, hosu kavatapilefeꞌmo afumo amagitapa hiꞌyalamuteꞌmo atafiꞌmo kaetapa namiyo, huka osuꞌnanaꞌmonanafa gekamo afisuva agufa nagesageꞌmo namiꞌnane.
\v 7 Namiꞌnanageꞌnaeꞌmo, Nago, huꞌna, nagaemo neꞌove. Goti mukufiꞌmo nava gemo haneꞌniye.
\v 8 O Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, keꞌaepa gekamo naipafiꞌmo haneꞌniye. Kagaemo huvo, huka naha paiꞌnana gekamo akame hisuvafeꞌmo amuse huteꞌna namogaga neꞌauve.
\v 9 Nagaemo asole vayaꞌmo eꞌa aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maiꞌnaya yateꞌmo fatago kavakaeꞌmo alagepa faigoko gekamo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paiꞌnove. Ago nageꞌnanana afaꞌa oꞌmaiꞌna gekamo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa nepauve.
\v 10 Nagaemo fatago kavakamo naipafiꞌmo aeꞌna ati kaeꞌna oꞌmaleꞌnofa nagaemo, geꞌamo alagi amagino oꞌataleno akame nehunoꞌaeꞌmo apakufamo alino katino neꞌapate, huꞌna aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paiꞌnove. Nagaemo asole vayaꞌmo eꞌa aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo kahau kayamopafiꞌmo nekahaiya kavakaꞌe lama ge gekaꞌeꞌmo aeꞌna ati okaeꞌna aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paiꞌnove.
\p 
\v 11 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, oꞌnataleka kahau huka nato. Nagaefeꞌmo kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauꞌninageka lama gekamo akame hugeꞌnao muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa maino.
\v 12 Lekana opaisuna agufa hanageke yaꞌmoꞌmo nagufaleꞌmo faino ku aino nateꞌniye. Hosu kavaꞌnimoꞌa natafauꞌniyanageꞌna afaꞌa aliꞌna maku huꞌna okagegauve. Nayokaꞌmo asole yaꞌmo haneꞌniya kava huno hosu kavaꞌnimo magoꞌe huno haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo lokiya oꞌvaiꞌnigeno lokiyaꞌnimo alagi ohaneꞌniye.
\v 13 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahauꞌnisigeka nagufamo alika katika nato. Ala kava nene, huꞌna, malage huka naha mao.
\v 14 Kagaemo naha maegeꞌapao kamiti namagigefe nehaya vayaꞌmo apavagage hisigeꞌa negi nagi hiyo. Hosu yaꞌmo aliꞌa namigefe nehaya vayaꞌmo apakamelagatiꞌmo asagauꞌa aiꞌa heleve hisageno apakiꞌapimo asagauno aino.
\v 15 Kigi huꞌa nateteꞌa nagaefeꞌmo, vaehae, vaehae, huꞌa nehaya vayaꞌmo apavagage hisiya yaꞌmo alika apamigeꞌa hapau aiyo.
\p 
\v 16 Hapau aigayaꞌmonanafa kagaefeꞌmo kahauya huliꞌa neꞌaya vayaꞌmogimo apamogaga aiteꞌa kagaefeꞌmo amuse hiyo. Apakufamo alika katika neꞌapatana kavafeꞌmo hapauꞌnisiya vayaꞌmogimo, Ala kava neꞌmo ala agiꞌamo amiyo, huꞌa hiyo.
\v 17 Inagi nagaemo afa vekamo maiꞌneꞌna kafu huꞌna maiꞌnovaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa nagaefeꞌmo agesamo neꞌafiye. O Gotiyo, huꞌna, naha maeka nagufamo alika katika neꞌnatana vekaꞌnimogae, afaꞌa oꞌmaika malage huka naha mao.
\c 42
\s1 Yulagefa aiꞌniya kavafeꞌmo nunumuꞌmo huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Afela afu anagaꞌmogimo anifeꞌmo nehapaigeꞌapaeꞌmo anitegamo neꞌvaya kava huꞌna Gotiyo, huꞌna, kagaefeꞌmo neꞌnahaiye.
\v 2 Afaꞌa neꞌmaina Gotigae, huꞌna, kagaefeꞌmo neꞌnahaiye. Hainu afinaꞌmo uꞌna kaulagaleꞌmo mono huguve.
\v 3 Apakaemo huꞌa faipa huꞌa nateteꞌapaeꞌmo Gotikamoꞌmo haiyate maiꞌniye, huꞌa hute hute huꞌnageꞌnaeꞌmo felugaꞌe haniꞌilagaꞌeꞌmo neꞌyaꞌmo oꞌneꞌna aviꞌya huge huge huꞌna neꞌmauve.
\v 4 Nagaemo huꞌnova kavafeꞌmo nagesamo afiteꞌna naipafiꞌmo haneꞌniya kavaꞌaꞌnimo aeꞌna laku faeꞌna kaha nepauve. Hogoteta nagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeta neꞌutaeꞌmo mono yokemo huge Goti agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga huge hulita Goti mono notegamo uꞌnone. Mukiꞌamogitamo mono hisunafeꞌmo aote afinaꞌmo hu maleꞌnone.
\v 5 Nagaemo na kava higeꞌnaeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo kana nehiye. Na kava higeꞌnaeꞌmo nagesa alaꞌamo neꞌafuve. Nagupi mafaꞌneyo, huꞌna, Gotiꞌa naha maesiyafeꞌmo agava maiꞌneka kavayagunagu nehugeꞌnao halate naha neꞌmaeya vekaꞌnimo Gotiꞌnimo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga hino.
\v 6-7 Naipamoꞌmo lusi kava huno kana nehiyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefeꞌmo halate nagesamo afiguve. Aniꞌmo Hemoni avefatiꞌe Misa avefatiꞌeꞌmo emineno alopa aniꞌmo Yoneni anipiꞌmo nelaminoꞌaeꞌmo lamino haꞌyamo asagauno neꞌaigenoꞌaeꞌmo alopa agemo neꞌaiya kava huno alopa hanageke yaꞌmoꞌa nagufaleꞌmo nati nekae.
\v 8 Nati nekaeyaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa aipamo falu huꞌniya kavaꞌaꞌe hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauꞌniya kavaꞌaꞌeꞌmo felugamo alino nave lisigeꞌnaeꞌmo haniꞌilagamo yokemo huge afaꞌa maisuva yaꞌmo namiꞌniya Gotifeꞌmo nunumu huge huꞌna maiguve.
\v 9 Nagaemo Gotiꞌa yafaꞌnigana vekaeꞌmo na kava higeka nataleka nagaefeꞌmo alagi kagesamo noꞌafine. Na kava higeka kame vayaꞌnimo apakeka apataleꞌnanageꞌa hosu yaꞌmo neꞌnamigeno nagafu nekiye.
\v 10 Geꞌapiletiꞌmo keveletiꞌmo neꞌnahaya kava huꞌa Gotikamoꞌmo haiyateꞌmo maiꞌniye, huꞌa huteꞌa huꞌa faipa huꞌa neꞌnatae.
\p 
\v 11 Nagaemo na kava higeꞌnaeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo kana nehiye. Na kava higeꞌnaeꞌmo nagesa alaꞌamo neꞌafuve. Nagupi mafaꞌneyo, huꞌna, Gotiꞌa naha maesiyafeꞌmo agava maiꞌneka kavayagunagu nehugeꞌnao halate naha neꞌmaeya vekaꞌnimo Gotiꞌnimo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga hino.
\c 45
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa aꞌmo aliꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Alagepa gemoꞌmo naipafiꞌmo havai teteno aino vali nelamigeꞌnaeꞌmo kini vekaekeꞌmo ava gemo nehuve. Alagepa huno avoꞌmo nekaeya vekamoꞌa avoꞌmo kaesiyafeꞌmo avo kayoꞌmo aliteno alo huno neꞌmaiya kava huꞌna navayafatiꞌmo gemo hisuvafeꞌmo alo huꞌna maiꞌnove.
\p 
\v 2 Kagaemo aeto agufa kumani vekamo maiꞌneka muki vayaꞌmo alagi aeka apakaseka maiꞌnane. Gotiꞌa fiku hapa maeno neꞌapamiya gemo kavayafiꞌmo alino maleꞌnigeka ani gemo nehane. Gotiꞌa muki afinaꞌmo kaha maeꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmae.
\v 3 Lokiya vekae, huꞌna, kagaemo ha le konali yakaꞌe ala kagikaleꞌefeꞌmo hapau aiteꞌa amuse huꞌa nekataya vekamo maiꞌnananagi naipekamo alika anoꞌafiꞌmo mapalukafiꞌmo falu kaeteka uka kame huvo.
\v 4 Kagaemo ala kagikamo alika apavelitekaeꞌmo lama gekamogi yagu yaga kavakamogi fatago kavakamogi huka ha maeka alika afole aika ato. Alika afole aika atesanafeꞌmo hosileꞌmo fai maiꞌneka uka kame huka aeka apakaso. Lokiyakaletiꞌmo kame huteka hapau aisaya agufa kavaꞌmo hugane.
\v 5 Kevekamo lusi kava huno akoꞌya huꞌniya kevemo haneꞌniyanageka kame vayakamogi apaipafiꞌmo nehapanageꞌapaeꞌmo kaiyafiꞌmo asagauꞌa neꞌaiye.
\p 
\v 6 O Gotiyo, huno, muki afinaꞌmo yagaika apatege apatege huka yagaika apategane. Fatago kavaꞌmo huka vayakaleꞌmo alagepa huka yagaika neꞌapatane.
\v 7 Kagaemo alagepa kavafeꞌmo lusi kava huno kahauꞌnigeno hosu kavafeꞌmo alagi okahauꞌniye. Ani kava nehanaꞌmofeꞌmo Gotiꞌa Gotikamoꞌmo uvelimo faleno katetenoꞌaeꞌmo lekana paino kateꞌniyanageka alagepa huka kamogaga aika maisanafeꞌmo magoꞌe huno kamiꞌnigeka kafalukamogimo aeka apakaseka alagepa huka maiꞌnane, huno ha paiꞌniye.
\v 8 Alagepa atumo neꞌaiya yaꞌmo agiꞌamo meyagi alosigi kasiyagi huno haneꞌneno kukenakalegatiꞌmo alagepa atumo neꞌaiye. Alagepa noꞌmo kini vekamo nopiꞌmo konali aliꞌa ateꞌnaya nopiꞌmo yokemo huꞌnagekaeꞌmo kamogaga aiteka emikeꞌnane.
\v 9 Ala apaki aꞌnekamogiꞌeꞌmo kini vayaꞌai aꞌmafaꞌneꞌapimo maiꞌnae. Akamoꞌmo hogote goli yafatetiꞌmo alo huꞌnaya konalimo aliteno lamaga kahaopaleꞌmo he tino maiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 10-11 Kini vekaleꞌmo maisana aꞌmafaꞌnemogae, huꞌna, kagesa afifi huteka kaipamo namiyo. Vayakaeꞌmo kagesamo oꞌafige afokamo vayaꞌaifeꞌmo kagesamo oꞌafige huteka kage kanika apatalegenoꞌao kini vekamoꞌa, aeto agufa kumani aꞌnimo maiꞌnane, huno huteno amuse huno kateno. Ala kava nekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo mono huteka aiyafiꞌmo maiꞌneka geꞌamo afiyo.
\v 12 Taiya taonifiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo malaga vayaꞌmogimo fiku kaha maeꞌa kamigae. Kagemi yaꞌapiꞌe vayaꞌmogimo hapa maesanafeꞌmo kagaetegamo ugae.
\p 
\v 13 Kini vekamo aꞌmafaꞌneꞌamoꞌmo agupiꞌmo aeto agufa alagepa kanale yaꞌmo haneꞌnigeno goli nofitetiꞌmo alo huꞌnaya kukenamo alino vaiꞌniye.
\v 14 Konali kukenamo leꞌniya kukena alino vaitesigeꞌapaeꞌmo kini vekalegamo avaleliꞌa ugae. Afaluꞌamogimo veꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌa ohavaeꞌnaya aꞌmafaꞌne anagaꞌmogi akame huꞌa neꞌvayanageꞌa kagaetegamo apavaleliꞌa ugae.
\v 15 Uꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga aiteꞌa kini vekamo noꞌafiꞌmo apavaleliꞌa haigae.
\p 
\v 16 Kagaemo asole mafaꞌnemo alika apatesanageꞌa kaginago vayaꞌai apaimuꞌyaleꞌmo maigae. Kagaemo muki ma mopafi vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaiꞌa apatesaya vayaꞌmo lekana paika apategane.
\v 17 Nagaemo ala kagikamo kamisugeꞌa henagaꞌamo afole aisaya vayaꞌmogimo kagaefeꞌmo apake okaniꞌa ala kagikamo kamigae. Muki vayaꞌmogimo kagikaleꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huge huge huꞌa maigae.
\c 46
\s1 Gotiꞌa lagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeno maiꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Uta fala kita neꞌmauna kotimo Gotiꞌmae. Lokiyatimo Gotiꞌmae. Hanageke yaꞌmo afole neꞌaisigenoꞌaeꞌmo lahamaesiyafeꞌmo lahaopaleꞌmo alo huno maiꞌniye.
\v 2-3 Ani kava huno maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo imima alige avemo aino nakupaeno emineno solovala anipiꞌmo asagauno aisigeno solovala aniꞌmo aino holakau holakau hisigeno alopa agemo aige avemoꞌa kanage huge nehisigetaeꞌmo koli osugune.
\p 
\v 4 Gotiꞌa Ala kava neꞌmo aeno apakaseꞌniya vekamo maiꞌniya aote taonifiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo mago aniꞌmo nelamisigeꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga aigae.
\v 5 Gotiꞌa ani taonifiꞌmo maiꞌniyanageno ani taonimo afaꞌa hanegaiye. Gotiꞌa kotilamisiyapiꞌmo eno taonifiꞌmo maiꞌnisaya vayaꞌmo hapa maegaiye.
\v 6 Alu nofi vayaꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌeꞌmo apayamukiki huꞌa kame huteꞌapaeꞌmo yagaiꞌa neꞌapataya vayaꞌe vayaꞌapiꞌeꞌmo alagi asagauꞌa aiꞌnae. Gotiꞌa alopa gefatiꞌmo ge nehigenoꞌaeꞌmo lokiyaꞌapimo alagi hano huꞌniye.
\v 7 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa asole vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino neꞌapateya vekamoꞌa lagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeno maiꞌniye. Yekopu Gotiꞌamoꞌmo uta fala kita neꞌmauna kotigana huno maiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 8 Etapa Ala kava neꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌamo ageyo. Mopafiꞌmo alino ayu noꞌmo kino apateꞌniye.
\v 9 Agaemo muki ma mopafiꞌmo kame nehaya kavaꞌmo alino hano huno neꞌatale. Agaemo ati keveꞌapimo alino lo aeno ataleteno alini uꞌa kame nehaya talalaꞌapimo alino atafiꞌmo nekae.
\v 10 Gotiꞌa hunoꞌaeꞌmo, muki kavaꞌamo ataletapa afaꞌa maiꞌnetapaeꞌmo, Gotigamo maiꞌnane, hutapa nageyo, huno nehiye. Nagaemo muki alu nofi vayaꞌaitegatiꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌaitegatiꞌeꞌmo ala nagiꞌnimo aliguve. Muki ma mopafiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaitegatiꞌmo ala nagiꞌnimo aliguve, huno nehiye.
\v 11 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa asole vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino neꞌapateya vekamoꞌa lagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeno maiꞌniye. Yekopu Gotiꞌamoꞌmo afaꞌa uta fala kita neꞌmauna kotigana huno maiꞌniye.
\c 48
\s1 Gotiꞌa alagepa taoniꞌamo haneꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa ala agiꞌamo aliꞌniye. Lagaemo aote alino maleꞌniya aveleꞌmo haiteta Gotitimo taoniꞌafiꞌmo faleta haita agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga huta ategetao.
\v 2 Ani avemo Saiyoni avemo kanale yatala avemo haneꞌniye. Muki ma mopafi maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo ani aveeꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiye. Hoga haopalega haneꞌnigeno Ala kini vekamo taoniꞌamo ani aveleꞌmo haneꞌniye.
\v 3 Gotiꞌa ani taonifiꞌmo maiꞌneno taonifiꞌmo neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmo hapa neꞌmae.
\p 
\v 4 Afiyo, huꞌna, kini vayaꞌmogimo Saiyoni taonifiꞌmo kame hisayafeꞌmo aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maiꞌneꞌa taoni haopaleꞌmo eꞌnae.
\v 5 Apakaemo ageteꞌapaeꞌmo hapau aiꞌnae. Apakaemo koli huteꞌa malage huꞌa ataleꞌa uꞌnae.
\v 6 Eꞌa apamoꞌya aiꞌa maiꞌnae. Aꞌnemogi mafaꞌnemo aliꞌa neꞌapataya afinaꞌmo apakafu nekiya kava huno apakafu kiꞌniye.
\v 7 Kagaemo yegemo haine neꞌeya kotegatiꞌmo alopa yasimo aliyo, huka huꞌnanageno aliteno Tasisi vayaꞌai alopa sipiꞌapimo aeno atava aiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 8 Gotiꞌa akeyaꞌvilagamo ani agufa kavaꞌmo huꞌniya ava gemo afiteta Gotitimoꞌmo taoniꞌafiꞌmo ageꞌnone. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa asole vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino neꞌapateya vekamoꞌmo taoniꞌafiꞌmo lokiya kavaꞌamo huꞌnigeta ageꞌnone. Gotiꞌa taoniꞌamo alino lokiya vaino atesigeno muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa hanege hanege huno hanegaiye.
\p 
\v 9 O Gotiyo, huta, Lagaemo mono nokafiꞌmo maiꞌnetaeꞌmo lagaefeꞌmo kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauge kahauge huno kahauꞌniya kavafeꞌmo lagesamo afiꞌnone.
\v 10 O Gotiyo, huta, Ala kagikamo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo muki ma mopafi vayaꞌmogimo ala kagikamo nekamiye. Lamaga kayatetiꞌmo fatago kavaꞌmo nehane.
\v 11 Kagaemo alagepa huka alika fako nehanaꞌmofeꞌmo Saiyoni aveleꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayanagi Yuta nofi vayaꞌai aꞌmafaꞌneꞌapigi huꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\p 
\v 12 Saiyoni avefiꞌmo umenitata nehutapa taoni yafa lafi kegiꞌyaleꞌmo faita ku aiꞌnetapa kegiꞌyaleꞌmo haneꞌniya yatala nofeꞌmo lekana paiyo.
\v 13 Lapakaemo afole aisaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo hapa paisayafeꞌmo taonileꞌmo lokiya yafa lafi kegiꞌyaeꞌmo lapakesamo afiyo. Lapakaemo taonifiꞌmo lokiya nofeꞌmo lapakesa afifi hutapa maiyo.
\v 14 Ani Gotiꞌa muki afinaꞌmo Gotitimoꞌmo maige maige huno maigiye. Agaemo uno hogoteteno visuna kaꞌmo alino lave lite lave lite hume hume neꞌvisigeta faligune.
\c 49
\s1 Hosu vayaꞌmo alagepa huꞌa oꞌmaisaya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Muki vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, afiyo. Muki ma mopafi maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo mani gemo afiyo.
\v 2 Ala apaki vayanagi apaki ohaneꞌnisiya vayanagi kagemi yatapiꞌe vayanagi kagemi yatapimo ohaneꞌniya vayanagi hutapa afiyo.
\v 3 Nagaemo naipafiꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna nagesamo afiteꞌna agegauve. Navayafatiꞌmo alagepa gemo lapa paisugetapa afitetapaeꞌmo agegae.
\v 4 Gotiꞌa aeno kalafefa gefatiꞌmo hisigeꞌna afisuvafeꞌmo maiꞌneꞌna afiguve. Nagaemo ani gemo alino fala ki maleꞌniya gemo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna lapa paiguve.
\p 
\v 5 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo faiꞌa ku aiꞌa nateꞌneꞌa namagigefeꞌmo nehisageꞌnaeꞌmo koli osuguve.
\v 6 Apakaemo, kagemi yatimoꞌa laha maegaiye, huꞌa huge alopa kagemi yatimo aliꞌnone, huꞌa huge nehaya vayaꞌmogimo
\v 7 konagaꞌapimo falisaya kavategatiꞌmo afaꞌa miya faiꞌa oꞌapategae. Konagaꞌapimogimo alagepa huꞌa afaꞌa maisayafeꞌmo Gotiꞌa miya amiteꞌa miya faiꞌa oꞌapategae.
\v 8-9 Apakupi mafaꞌnemo miya faisaya monimo alopa monimo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmae. Apakaemo kelifiꞌmo lamiꞌa oꞌmaiꞌa muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa maige maige huꞌa maisayafeꞌmo afaꞌa miya faita apategaune, huꞌa hugayana haiꞌa metalegae.
\p 
\v 10 Apakaemo ago apakeꞌnayana ageteꞌa afiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo ago nefaliya kava huꞌa muki vayaꞌmogi oꞌafiꞌnaya vayaꞌe negi vayaꞌeꞌmo faliꞌapaeꞌmo kagemi yaꞌapimo ataleꞌnageꞌapaeꞌmo alu vayaꞌmogi neꞌaliye.
\v 11 Apakaemo apaipafiꞌmo, notimo muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa hanesigeno neꞌmauna kotimo afaꞌa hanege hanege huno hanegaiye, huꞌa apakesa neꞌafiye. Mopaꞌapileꞌmo apakiꞌapimo neꞌatayaꞌmonanafa
\v 12 ala apaki vayaꞌmo afu anagaꞌmo afaꞌa oꞌmaiꞌa nefaliya agufa afugana huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\p 
\v 13 Apakaemo negi nagi apakesamo neꞌafigeꞌapaeꞌmo mafaꞌneꞌapimogimo lama gegeꞌmo nehae, huꞌa huteꞌa apakame nehae.
\v 14 Sipisipimo faliꞌnaya kava huꞌa nefaligeꞌa kanolufiꞌmo kiꞌa neꞌapatae. Sipisipileꞌmo yagaiꞌa neꞌapataya kava huno falisaya kavaꞌmoꞌa yagaino apategaiye. Lama ge vayaꞌmogimo kotilamisiyapiꞌmo yagaiꞌa apategae. Kanolufiꞌmo koꞌapimo haneꞌniyanageno alagepa apakufaꞌe konali yaꞌapiꞌeꞌmo kasaligiyamonanafa
\v 15 Gotiꞌa kanolumo lokiyaꞌafatiꞌmo nagupi mafaꞌnemo miya faino nateteno navalegaiye.
\p 
\v 16 Mago vekamoꞌa alopa kagemi yaꞌmo aliꞌnisigeꞌapaeꞌmo afamo anagaꞌamogi ala apakimo alisagetapaeꞌmo koli osiyo.
\v 17 Falisiya afinaꞌmo kagemi yaꞌamo alinino oꞌugiye. Muki konali yaꞌamoꞌa agaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaelino olamigiye.
\v 18 Afaꞌa maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo agaiꞌaeꞌmo alagepa huka maiꞌnananageka afaꞌa kamogaga aigane, huno nehiye. He, lapakaitapimo alagepa hutapa lapa maesageꞌapaeꞌmo vayaꞌmogimo ala lapakitapimo lapamigae.
\v 19 Ani vekamoꞌa aginago vayaꞌmo maiꞌnaya kotegamo lamino hanipiꞌmo maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo ha le yaꞌmo oꞌagegaiye.
\v 20 Ala apakimo aliteꞌa alagepa huꞌa ageteꞌa oꞌafiꞌnisaya vayaꞌmo afumo nefaliya agufa afugana huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\c 50
\s1 Gotiꞌa agoti huno apatesiya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Gotiꞌa Ala kava neꞌmo lokiyaꞌage vekamoꞌa ge huꞌniye. Agaemo yegemo haine neꞌeya kotegamo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌe yegemo lamino nefaleya kotegamo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌefeꞌmo keya aeno ge huꞌniye. Muki ma mopafi vayaꞌaifeꞌmo keya aeno ge huꞌniye.
\v 2 Gotiꞌa Saiyoni taonimo hogote konali taonifatiꞌmo aeno ha legaiye.
\v 3 Gotitimoꞌa eminenoꞌaeꞌmo ge osuno afaꞌa oꞌmaigiye. Atamo lelino uno hogotetesigeno eminegaiye. Lusi yasimo alige ko aige hulino haopaꞌaleꞌmo egaiye.
\p 
\v 4 Agaemo vayaꞌageꞌmo alino fako huno apatesiyafeꞌmo kokuꞌnapi vayaꞌe ma mopafi vayaꞌefeꞌmo ge hugiye.
\v 5 Ina ge huno hapa paigiye. Lapakaemo utapa naote vayaꞌnimo nagaeteꞌmo apavaleta alita anupa hutapa apateyo. Sipisipimo amagiꞌa ofalinimo namiꞌnaya kavatetiꞌmo nagaeꞌeꞌmo kotalakemo hu maleꞌnaya vayaꞌnimo apavaleta alita anupa hutapa apateyo.
\v 6 Kokuꞌnapiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogi, alagi fatago vekamo maiꞌniye. Agaiꞌageꞌmo alino fako huno apategaiye, huꞌa hugae.
\p 
\v 7 O vayaꞌnimogitapae, huꞌna, afiyo. Nagaemo gemo hugesuve. O Isaleli vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Nagaemo agoti huꞌna lapategauve. Nagaiꞌnigeꞌmo alagi Gotiꞌnamo maiꞌnove. Gotitapimoꞌnamo maiꞌnove.
\v 8 Lapakaemo muki afinaꞌmo naulagaleꞌmo afumo amagitapa ofalinimo namige atafiꞌmo kaege nehaya kavatapilefeꞌmo agoti huꞌna olapategauve.
\v 9 Nagaemo notapifiꞌmo maiꞌnaya pulumakamo apavaleliꞌna oꞌuguve. Kegiꞌyafatiꞌmo memetapimo apavaleliꞌna oꞌuguve.
\v 10 Haꞌao, muki yahaofilaga maiꞌnaya afumo nagaiꞌni afumo maige tauseniꞌa aveleꞌmo maiꞌnaya pulumakamo nagaiꞌni pulumakamo maige huꞌa maiꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmae.
\v 11 Muki aveꞌalegamo maiꞌnaya nama anagaꞌe muki kotega maiꞌnaya afela afu anagaꞌeꞌmo nagaiꞌni yaꞌmo maiꞌnae.
\p 
\v 12 Ma mopaꞌe muki ma mopafi vayaꞌe yaꞌeꞌmo nagaiꞌni yaꞌmo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo naga tesigeꞌnaeꞌmo lapa opaiguve.
\v 13 Nagaemo pulumakamo ameꞌamo nesufiye. Mememo kolaꞌamo nesufiye.
\v 14 Gotifekeꞌmo hao ke hesaya agufa ofalinimo alitapa amiyo. Lapakaemo ani kavaꞌmo hugune, hutapa ha paiꞌnaya gemo akame hutapa ani agufa ofalinimo alita hogote vekamo anaga vekamo amiyo.
\v 15 Hanageke yaꞌmo alisaya afinaꞌmo nagaefekeꞌmo ge higeꞌnao alagepa huꞌna lapa maesugetapa ala nagiꞌnimo namigae.
\p 
\v 16 Gotiꞌa ani gemo huꞌniyaꞌmonanafa hosu vayaꞌaifeꞌmo, Na kava higetapaeꞌmo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa geꞌnimo aeta hakalo hutapa hapa paiꞌnae. Na kava higetapaeꞌmo kotalake geꞌnimo nehae.
\v 17 Lapakaemo aliꞌna lapaya malesuvafeꞌmo alagi olapauꞌniye. Geꞌnimo alita lapakamelagamo yaga autapa neꞌatalae.
\v 18 Lapakaemo kumaya neꞌaliya vayaꞌmo apaketetapaeꞌmo magoke lapaipa lapakesamo aliꞌnae. Kumai kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌai apafaluꞌapimogitapamo maiꞌnae.
\v 19 Muki afinaꞌmo hosu gemo huge aigofe gemo huge hutapa maiꞌnae.
\v 20 Itopaleꞌmo maiꞌnetapaeꞌmo konagatapimogifeꞌmo apakamelaga gemo nehae. Lapakaemo itatapimogi mafaꞌneꞌapieꞌmo hutapa faipa hutapa neꞌapatae.
\v 21 Ani agufa kavaꞌmo huꞌnageꞌnaeꞌmo ge osuꞌna afaꞌa maiꞌnove. Lapakaemo nagaefeꞌmo, lagaekana huno maiꞌniye, hutapa lapakesamo afiꞌnayaꞌmonanafa hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnae, huꞌna lapa paiguve. Nagaemo hosu kavatapimo lapaulagaleꞌmo aliꞌna kale kaeꞌna lapave liguve.
\p 
\v 22 Gotifeꞌmo lapake kaniꞌnisiya vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, geꞌnieꞌmo lapakesa afifi hutapa maiyo. Fiku yanageꞌna lapaeꞌna katali katalu hisugeꞌapaeꞌmo lapa maesaya vayaꞌmo oꞌmaigae.
\v 23 Nagaefeꞌmo, alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌniye, huꞌa nehaya vayaꞌmogimo ala nagiꞌnimo neꞌnamiye. Nehaya kavaꞌapilefeꞌmo apakesa afifi huꞌa maiꞌnisaya vayaꞌmo Gotiꞌa apakufamo alino katino neꞌapateya kavaꞌamo aliꞌna apave liguve.
\c 51
\s1 Neviniꞌa Matasimaꞌeꞌmo kumai kavaꞌmo huꞌnigeno mago polofeti vekamo Netaniꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnane, huno ha paiꞌnigeno huꞌniya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauꞌnigeka hapa neꞌmana kava huka kahau huka nato. Lusi kava huka kahau huka neꞌapatana kava huka gekamo amagiꞌna neꞌatalova kavaꞌnimo aeka kalo paeka atalo.
\v 2 Muki hosu kavaꞌnimo alagi aeka kalo paeka atalo. Hosu kavaꞌnimo alika ataleteka alika alagepa huka nato.
\v 3 Nagaemo ma hosu kava huꞌnove, ina hosu kava huꞌnove, huꞌna aeꞌna hakalo nehuve. Nagaemo hosu kavaꞌnimo ageꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo ani hosu kavaꞌnimoꞌmo naulagaleꞌmo afole neꞌaigeꞌna neꞌagove.
\v 4 Kagae kaulagaleꞌmo hosu kavakeꞌmo huꞌna maiꞌnove. Nagaemo hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo kagaemo fatago kavaꞌmo huka agotimo huka nateꞌnane. Kagaemo nagaefeꞌmo fatago gemo hukaeꞌmo, hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnane, huka huꞌnane.
\v 5 Vae, huꞌna, itaꞌnimoꞌmo nagae aipaguꞌeꞌmo aepa faiꞌniya afinaꞌmo hosu kavapiꞌmo maiꞌnove. Itaꞌnimo aipafiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo hosu mafaꞌnemo maiꞌnove.
\p 
\v 6 Vae, huꞌna, lama ge kavaꞌmo naipafiꞌmo hanesiyafeꞌmo kahauꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo ageꞌna aeto hisuvafeꞌmo naipafiꞌmo alika naya malegane.
\v 7 Aika fuli fuli huka faleka nategeꞌnao yaveyave vekamo maino. Sese huka nategeꞌnao yaveyave yafakana huꞌna yaveyaveꞌageꞌmo huꞌna magoꞌe huꞌna yaveyave vekamo maino.
\v 8 Falu fala gemo huka naha paigeꞌnao namogaga aino. Nagupi mafaꞌnemo aeka lata paiꞌnanaꞌmonanafa halate namogaga aiguve.
\v 9 Hosu kavaꞌnimo oꞌageka aika afe leka maiyo. Muki hosu kavaꞌnimo aeka kalo paeka atalo.
\p 
\v 10 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, yaveyave naipamo alo huka nateteka gekamo afisuvafeꞌmo nauneꞌnameꞌmo alika hegafa huka ato.
\v 11 Kagaetegatiꞌmo alika naha faika oꞌnataleka kaote Kaunekamekamo nagaepatiꞌmo oꞌaliyo.
\v 12 Hogoteka nagufamo ago alika katika nateꞌnanageꞌnaeꞌmo namogaga aiꞌnovanagi halate namogaga aisuva kavaꞌmo alika namiyo. Hatu maeno natesiya Kaunekametetiꞌmo natafauka maiyo.
\v 13 Ani kava hisanageꞌnaeꞌmo gekamo amagiꞌa neꞌatalaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo ina kavaꞌmo huvo, huka nehana gekamo aliꞌna apaya malesugeꞌapaeꞌmo aiꞌa afe leꞌa kagaetegamo egae.
\p 
\v 14 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, nagaemo mago vekamo kamiti amagiꞌnove. Ani hosu kavaꞌnimo alika atalo. Alika atalesanageꞌnaeꞌmo, nagufamo ago alino katino nateꞌniye, huꞌna huteꞌna yokemo huguve.
\v 15 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, navayamo alika aka huka nategeꞌnao kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna kateno.
\v 16 Nagaemo ofalinimo kamisuvafeꞌmo kahauꞌniyesinana kamuvesine. Nagaemo afumo amagiꞌna atafiꞌmo kaeꞌna kamisuvana amuse osugane.
\v 17 Afu ofalinimo kamisuvafeꞌmo okahauꞌnifa naipamo aino atalagausiyafekeꞌmo kahauꞌniye. O Gotiyo, huꞌna, apaipamo aliꞌa afepi ateteꞌa apaipamo aliꞌa afe nelaya kavafeꞌmo kahauꞌniye.
\p 
\v 18 Saiyoni kotega vayaꞌaifeꞌmo kagesamo afiteka hapa mao. Yulusalemu taonifi yafa lafi kegiꞌyamo halate hisayafeꞌmo hapa mao.
\v 19 Ani kava hisanageꞌapaeꞌmo alagepa ofalinimo atafi nekaya ofalinimo kamisageka amuse huka apategane. Ani afinaꞌmo ve pulumakamo amagiꞌa hiꞌyalamuteꞌmo atafiꞌmo kaeꞌa kamigae.
\c 53
\s1 Hosu vayaꞌai kavaꞌapieꞌmo ava ge huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Negi nagi vayaꞌmogimo apaipafiꞌmo, Gotiꞌa oꞌmaiꞌniye, huꞌa nehae. Afumo nefaligenoꞌaeꞌmo apakufamo nekasaliya kava huꞌa hosu vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae. Gotiꞌa avenatuꞌnaꞌmo heno neꞌapateya kavaꞌmo nehae. Magoke vekamoꞌa alagepa kavaꞌmo nehiya vekamo alagi oꞌmaiꞌniye.
\v 2 Gotiꞌa kokuꞌnapatiꞌmo apakenoꞌaeꞌmo, Mago ageteꞌa afiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo maiꞌnafi mago vayaꞌmogi kahauya huꞌa nagesayafeꞌmo nehafi huno apakeꞌniye.
\v 3 Apakeꞌniyaꞌmonanafa mukiꞌamogimo alagepa kaꞌmo ago ataleꞌa magoke aiyaya huꞌa hosu vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae. Alagepa kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo alagiꞌato oꞌmaiꞌnae. Magokeꞌatomo alagi oꞌmaiꞌniye.
\v 4 Gotiꞌa hunoꞌaeꞌmo, oꞌafiꞌneꞌa hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo negi nagi vayaꞌmo maiꞌnafi. Neꞌyaꞌmo aliꞌa neꞌnaya kava huꞌa vayaꞌnimo apamagiꞌa hano huꞌa apataleteꞌa Gotifeꞌmo nunumu nosae, huno huꞌniye.
\v 5 Hemenimo aiseꞌamo koli nehayaꞌmonanafa henagaꞌamo lusi kava huꞌa koli hugae. Gotiꞌa hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo apamagisigeꞌa falisagenoꞌaeꞌmo lokiyaꞌapimo aino atagu faegaiye. Gotiꞌa akameꞌya apamiꞌniyanageꞌa alagi asagauꞌa aigae.
\v 6 Nahauꞌniyanageno mago vekamoꞌa Saiyoni kotegatiꞌmo eno Isaleli vayaꞌmo hapa maesigeꞌa aeꞌa apakasegae. Gotiꞌa hapa maesigeꞌapaeꞌmo Isaleli vayaꞌmo halate alagepa huꞌa maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo lusi kava huꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\c 61
\s1 Gotiꞌa alino fala kino latesiya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, Alopa gefatiꞌmo ge nehuvanagi afiyo. Nunumu nehuva geꞌnieꞌmo kagesa afifi huka maiyo.
\v 2 Ma mopamo atupalegatiꞌmo kagaefeꞌmo ge huguve. Lusi kana yaꞌmo alisugeno aino nati kaesiya afinaꞌmo navalelika haika yafateꞌmo faika nato. Nagaemo afepiꞌmo maiꞌnovanagi navalelika haika anaga haneꞌniya yafateꞌmo faika nato.
\p 
\v 3 Kagaemo fala kiꞌna maiꞌnova nokana huka maiꞌnekaeꞌmo alagepa huka yagaika nateꞌnane. Kagaemo yatala noꞌmo lokiya nokana huka maiꞌnanageꞌnaeꞌmo kame vayaꞌnimo apataleꞌna haiꞌna alagepa huꞌna maiꞌnove.
\v 4 Nagaemo alagepa seli nokafiꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo maige maige huꞌna maiguve. Naha maegane, huteꞌna uꞌna kahakufiꞌmo fala kiguve.
\p 
\v 5 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, ma kava huguve, huꞌna kaha paiꞌnova geꞌnimo ago afiꞌnane. Mafaꞌneꞌapimogimo afoꞌapimogi kagemi yaꞌapimo neꞌaliya kava huꞌa kagikaeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌmogimo alagepa yakamo aligae. Ani kava huka alika namisanageꞌna aliguve.
\v 6 Kagaemo kini vekamo ha maesanageno asole kafugamo maigiye. Agaemo mafaꞌneꞌamogi mafaꞌneꞌapimo apakegaiye.
\v 7 Agaemo Goti aulagaleꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo alagepa huno maige maige huno maigiye. Kahau huka atesana kavaꞌe agaetefeꞌmo lama geꞌeꞌmo alo huvo. Kahau huka ateteka alagepa huꞌna yagaiꞌna kategauve, huka huꞌnana lama gekaletiꞌmo yagaika ategane.
\p 
\v 8 Naha maesanageꞌna muki afinaꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna katege katege huꞌna maiguve. Huguve, huꞌna kaha paiꞌnova geꞌniletiꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo akame hisuvafeꞌmo muki afinaꞌae afinaꞌaeꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna kategauve.
\c 62
\s1 Gotiꞌa agaiꞌageꞌmo nagufamo alino katino nategaiye, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Nagupi mafaꞌnemoꞌa ge osuno Gotifekeꞌmo agava maiꞌniye. Agaiꞌageꞌmo nagufamo alino katino nategaiye.
\v 2 Agaiꞌageꞌmo yafaꞌnimo maiꞌneno nagufamo alino katino neꞌnateya Gotiꞌnimoꞌmo maiꞌniye. Naha maesigeꞌna afaꞌa maiguve.
\p 
\v 3 Lapakaemo na magi afinaꞌmo kame hutapa nategae. Lapakaemo aino aega huꞌniya yafa kegiꞌyagana hutapa maige uti uti neꞌaiya kegiꞌyagana hutapa maige huꞌnayanagetapa asagautapa aitetapa faligae.
\v 4 Apakaemo aliꞌa afepiꞌmo yaga auꞌa atalesayafeꞌmo vege nehae. Aigofe gemo hisayafeꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiye. Apakaemo apavayaꞌaletikeꞌmo Gotiꞌa ha maeno, huꞌa nehayaꞌmonanafa apaipafiꞌmo Gotiꞌa amagino, huꞌa apakesamo neꞌafiye.
\p 
\v 5 Nagaemo Gotiꞌa naha maegaiye, huꞌna nagesamo afiꞌna fatago nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo nagupi mafaꞌneyo, huꞌna, ge osuka Gotifekeꞌmo agava maiyo.
\v 6 Agaiꞌageꞌmo yafaꞌnimo maiꞌneno nagufamo alino katino neꞌnateya Gotiꞌnimoꞌmo maiꞌniye. Naha maesigeꞌna afaꞌa maiguve.
\v 7 Gotiꞌa nagufamo alino katino nateteno nagiꞌnileꞌmo alino asaga huno nategaiye. Gotiꞌa lokiya yafaꞌnimo maiꞌniye. Nagaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo afole neꞌaigeꞌnaeꞌmo agaepiꞌmo alagepa huꞌna fala kiꞌna neꞌmauve.
\p 
\v 8 Vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, muki afinaꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo lapakesamo afitapa fatago hutetapaeꞌmo, laha maegaiye, hutapa hiyo. Lapaipafatiꞌmo aniꞌmo alitapa lakigekana hutapa nunumu hutapa ha paiyo. Lagaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo afole neꞌaigetaeꞌmo Gotipiꞌmo alagepa huta fala kita neꞌmaune.
\p 
\v 9 Apaki oꞌaliꞌnisaya vayaꞌmo afa vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae. Apaki aliꞌnisaya vayaꞌmo aigofe vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae. Sigelileꞌmo asaisunagenoꞌaeꞌmo kanaꞌapimo ohanegaiye.
\v 10 Lapakaemo agoti hutapa apatege kumaya alige hisayafeꞌmo lapakesamo oꞌafiyo lapa oꞌmaegayanagi. Monitapimo magoꞌe huno afole aisigetapaeꞌmo, laha maegaiye, hutapa lapakesamo oꞌafiyo.
\p 
\v 11 Gotiꞌa magoke afinaꞌmo ge huꞌniye. Nagaemo lole afinaꞌmo afiꞌnovana Goti lokiyaꞌamo haneꞌniye, huꞌna ago afiꞌnove.
\v 12 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, vayakaeꞌmo kahau huka neꞌapatane, huꞌna ago afiꞌnove. Kagaemo kavaꞌapilefeꞌmo apamete apamete huka alika fako huka neꞌapamine.
\c 63
\s1 Gotifekeꞌmo neꞌnahaiye, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, Gotiꞌnimogamo maiꞌnane. Kagesuvafeꞌmo kotilamisiyapiꞌmo kahauya huguve. Nauneꞌnameꞌmoꞌa kagaefeꞌmo nehaiye. Aniꞌmo ohaneꞌniya koteꞌmo maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo vayaꞌmogimo anifeꞌmo nehapaiya kava huno kagaefeꞌmo neꞌnahaiye.
\v 2 Hogoteꞌna kaote mono nokafiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌna lokiyakaꞌe ha le konali yakaꞌeꞌmo ageꞌnova kava huꞌna hemeniꞌeꞌmo agesuvafeꞌmo huve.
\v 3 Ofaliꞌna afaꞌa neꞌmauva kavaꞌmo kanale kavaꞌmo haneꞌniyaꞌmonanafa oꞌnataleka kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauꞌnigeka naha neꞌmana kavaꞌmo aeno agaseꞌniya kavaꞌmo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna kategauve.
\v 4 Muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo kahao ke hege hege huꞌna maiguve. Nayaꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huliꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo kagaefekeꞌmo nunumu huguve.
\v 5 Afumo afayaꞌaꞌe atuꞌaꞌeꞌmo neꞌa apamu nehaya kava huno nagupi mafaꞌnemoꞌa neno amu hugiye. Nagaemo namogaga aiteꞌna navayafatiꞌmo yokemo huꞌna kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna kategauve.
\p 
\v 6 Hipaꞌnileꞌmo havaegefeꞌmo nehuꞌnaeꞌmo kagaefekeꞌmo nagesamo afiteꞌna muki haniꞌilagaꞌamo kagaefekeꞌmo nagesa afifi nehuve.
\v 7 Naha maeꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo kahakufiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo namogaga aiguve.
\v 8 Nagupi mafaꞌnemoꞌa magokepi lokaeno maisiyafeꞌmo kakame nehigeka nayapiꞌmo natafauka alika lokiya vaika neꞌnatane.
\p 
\v 9 Nehanaꞌmonanafa kahauya huꞌa nageꞌa nahaegefeꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo mopamo afepilaga faliꞌnaya vayaꞌmo lamiꞌa neꞌmaiya kotegamo lamigae.
\v 10 Kame vayaꞌapimogi hapaesageꞌa afela kalamogi apakufaꞌamo negae.
\v 11 Negayaꞌmonanafa kini vekamoꞌa Gotifeꞌmo amogaga aigiye. Agiꞌalefeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo ha le konali yaꞌapimo aligayaꞌmonanafa aigofe gemo nehaya vayaꞌai apavayaleꞌmo alino akanigiye.
\c 67
\s1 Ala agiꞌamo amiyo, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Gotiꞌa fiku laha maeno lamiteno alino maku huno lageno.
\v 2 Ani kava hisanageꞌapaeꞌmo muki ma mopafi vayaꞌmogimo kaꞌmo agesagekaeꞌmo apakufamo alika katika apategane.
\v 3 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, muki alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hiyo. Muki alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hiyo.
\v 4 Kagaemo fatago kavaꞌmo huka alika fako huka apateteka muki alu nofi vayaꞌaiteꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌaiteꞌeꞌmo yagaika neꞌapatanaꞌmofeꞌmo apamogaga aiteꞌa yoke hiyo.
\v 5 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hiyo. Muki alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hiyo.
\v 6 Ma mopafatiꞌmo neꞌyaꞌmo ago afole aiꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo Gotiꞌa Gotitimoꞌmo laha maeno lamiꞌniye.
\v 7 Gotiꞌa laha maeno lamiꞌniyanagi muki ma mopafi vayaꞌmogimo agaefekeꞌmo koli huteꞌa mono hiyo.
\c 69
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa kana yaꞌmo aliꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, aniꞌmoꞌa lugoꞌnifiꞌmo haineꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 2 Naiyamo aeꞌna maisuva yaꞌmo ohaneꞌnigeꞌna hapafikeꞌmo aeꞌna lapaneꞌnove. Aniꞌmo heteno aeno nati kaeꞌniye.
\v 3 Keya aeꞌna ge huge huge huꞌna maiꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo lusi kava huno alagaꞌmo nahaeꞌniye. Lugoꞌnileꞌmo hau huꞌnigeꞌna Gotiꞌnimofeꞌmo agava maiꞌnogeno naulagafatiꞌmo nagafu nekiye.
\p 
\v 4 Nayokaꞌmo lusi asole yaꞌmo haneꞌniya kava huꞌa kame vayaꞌnimo magoꞌe huꞌa maiꞌnae. Apakaetegamo mago agufa hosu kavaꞌmo osuꞌnovaꞌmonanafa fiku apaini huꞌa neꞌnatae. Afaꞌa fiku nahaesayafeꞌmo huꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo lokiya vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae. Mago yaꞌapimo kumaya oꞌaliꞌnovaꞌmonanafa anonaꞌnilefeꞌmo afaꞌa amiguve.
\v 5 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, negi kavaꞌmo huꞌna kavaꞌnimo ago ageꞌnane. Hosu kavaꞌnimo kaulagaleꞌmo fala okiꞌnigeka ago ageꞌnane.
\v 6 O Gotiyo, huꞌna asole ami vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaika neꞌapatana Ala kava nene, huꞌna, fiku yanageꞌna hosu kavaꞌmo hisuvana kagaefeꞌmo kagava neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogimo apavagage hugiye. O Isaleli vayaꞌmogita Gotitimogae, huꞌna, fiku yanageꞌna hosu kavaꞌmo hisuvana kagaemo kagesayafeꞌmo kahauya nehaya vayaꞌmogimo hosu apakiꞌapimo aligae.
\v 7 Kagaetefeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa nateꞌnageno navagage huꞌniye.
\v 8 Naganaꞌnimogimo oꞌapakeꞌnaya vayaꞌaitegamo nehaya agufa kavaꞌmo nagaetegamo nehae. Itaꞌnimo mafaꞌne anagaꞌamogimo alu kotega vayaꞌaifeꞌmo apakesamo noꞌafiya kava huꞌa nagaefeꞌmo apakesamo noꞌafiye.
\v 9 Kagaemo nokamo alagepa huno hanesiyafeꞌmo nayamukiki nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo noꞌnagae. Huꞌa faipa huꞌa nekataya gemoꞌmo nagaeteꞌmo asagauno aiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 10 Aviꞌya huge nagufamo aliꞌna afepi atesuvafeꞌmo neꞌyaꞌmo mo sige huꞌna maiꞌnogeꞌapaeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa nateꞌnae.
\v 11 Hosu kogu kukenamo aliꞌna vaiꞌnogeꞌapaeꞌmo muki vayaꞌmogi kigi yokalo gemo huꞌa nateꞌnae.
\v 12 Kateꞌmo aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogi huꞌa faipa huꞌa neꞌnatae. Alopa aniꞌmo neteꞌa negi nagi gemo nehaya vayaꞌmogi nagaefeꞌmo yoke nehae.
\p 
\v 13 Nehayaꞌmonanafa nagaemo kagaefekeꞌmo nunumu nehuve. O Ala kava nene, O Gotiyo, huꞌna, kahauꞌnisiya afinaꞌmo kahau huka nateteka geꞌnimo afaꞌa afitekaeꞌmo lama gekaletiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 14 Hapafiꞌmo aeꞌna olapanesuvafeꞌmo hapafatiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato. Apaini huꞌa neꞌnataya vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo hapa faleka nato. Aniꞌmo neheya yapatiꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 15 Aniꞌmo neheya aniꞌmoꞌa aeno nati kaesifi alopa anipiꞌmo aeꞌna lapanesufi yatala kelifiꞌmo avayamo aino akanino natesifi hisigeꞌna maisuvafeꞌmo oꞌnato.
\p 
\v 16 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahau kayamopafiꞌmo nekahaiya kavakamo alagepa kavaꞌmo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo geꞌnimo afiyo. Magoꞌe huka kahau huka neꞌapatana kavakalefeꞌmo nagaetegamo aika afe leka eno.
\v 17 Hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌnamo kaugosafiꞌmo okagesuvafeꞌmo aika ati okao. Malage huka geꞌnimo afiyo.
\v 18 Nahaopaleꞌmo eka miya faika hatu maeka nato. Kame vayaꞌnimogi apayapatiꞌmo hatu maeka nato.
\v 19 Ago apakeꞌnanageꞌapaeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa natege navagage yaꞌmo aliꞌa namige nagiꞌnileꞌmo aliꞌa afepi atege nehageka apakeꞌnane. Kame vayaꞌnimo kaulagaleꞌmo maiꞌnae.
\v 20 Huꞌa faipa huꞌa nateꞌnageꞌna lusi kana yaꞌmo aliꞌnogeno kanamo nahauꞌniye. Hau huno natesiya vekamo agesuvafeꞌmo kahauya huꞌnovaꞌmonanafa magoke vekamo alagi oꞌmaiꞌniye. Mago vayaꞌmogi naipamo aliꞌa lokiya vaiꞌa natesageꞌna naipamoꞌmo falu hisiyafeꞌmo nagesamo afiꞌnovaꞌmonanafa alagi oꞌmaiꞌnae.
\v 21 Nesuvafeꞌmo atu neheya fipikana agufa yaꞌmo aliꞌa namiꞌnae. Anifeꞌmo nahauꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo atu neheya aniꞌmo aliꞌa namiꞌnae.
\p 
\v 22 Hapa oꞌmaegenoꞌao hosu kavaꞌapimo anonaꞌapilefeꞌmo magokepiꞌmo alopa neꞌyaꞌmo neꞌnesagenoꞌaeꞌmo apaneꞌmu aegekana huno aeno. Alagepa huꞌa neꞌmaiya kavaꞌapimoꞌa aneꞌaifiꞌmo hegekana huno haneno.
\v 23 Magoꞌe huꞌa oꞌagesayafeꞌmo apaulagafatiꞌmo haniꞌageꞌmo hino. Lusi kana yaꞌmo alika apamigeꞌapao aliteꞌa muki afinaꞌmo ape hulitata huꞌa maiyo.
\v 24 Kaipamo neleya kavakamo apakaeteꞌmo aniꞌmo lakigekana huka alika apamiyo. Kaipamo leka apateꞌneka apatafauvo.
\v 25 Koꞌapimo no atufaꞌageꞌmo hanegaiye. Fiku yanageꞌa mago alu vayaꞌmogi seli noꞌapifiꞌmo maigae.
\v 26 Na kava nehayaꞌmofeꞌmae. Apakaemo amagiꞌnana vekaeꞌmo apaini huꞌa neꞌatae. Apakaemo hapaeꞌnana vayaꞌaifeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa apateteꞌa kana yaꞌmo aliꞌa neꞌapamiye.
\v 27 Alu hosu kava alu hosu kavaꞌapilefeꞌmo agoti huka apato. Apakaemo fatago kavakamo oꞌalisageka naulagaleꞌmo fatago vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae, huka hapa opaiyo.
\v 28 Maige maige huꞌa maisaya vayaꞌai apakiꞌapimo haneꞌniya mukufatiꞌmo apakiꞌapimo aeka kalo paeka atalo. Fatago vayaꞌai apakiꞌapimo haneꞌniya mukufiꞌmo apakiꞌapimo avoꞌmo kaeka oꞌmalo.
\p 
\v 29 Huꞌa maiꞌnayaꞌmonanafa nagaemo muki yaꞌnimo ohaneꞌniya vekamo maiꞌneꞌna kana yaꞌmo aliꞌnove. O Gotiyo, huꞌna, nagufamo alika katika nateteka alika asaga huka nato.
\v 30 Nagaemo yoke huꞌna Gotiꞌmo ala agiꞌamo amiguve. Hao ke heꞌnaeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna ategauve.
\v 31 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa ani hisuva kavafeꞌmo lusi kava huno amuse hugiye. Pulumakamo heꞌna amisugenoꞌaeꞌmo amuse osugiye.
\v 32 Ala vayaꞌmo maiꞌnone, huꞌa apakesamo noꞌafiya vayaꞌmogi ani kavaꞌmo ageteꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga aigae. Lapakaemo Gotiꞌmo agesayafeꞌmo kahauya nehaya vayaꞌmogitapamo lapaipamo alagepa huno hanesigetapa maige maige hutapa maigae.
\v 33 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa muki yaꞌapimo ohaneꞌniya vayaꞌai geꞌapimo neꞌafiye. Agaemo agaiꞌa vayaꞌamo kalavusifiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogifeꞌmo afa vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae, huno agesamo noꞌafifa apakaefeꞌmo alagepa huno agesamo neꞌafiye.
\p 
\v 34 Kokuꞌnaꞌmoꞌagi ma mopamoꞌagi solovala aniꞌmoꞌagi muki noyamemogimogi solovala anipiꞌmo maiꞌnaya yaꞌmogimogi huꞌa ala agiꞌamo amiyo.
\v 35 Na agufa kavatefeꞌmo ala agiꞌamo amigae. Gotiꞌa Saiyoni kotega vayaꞌamogi apakufamo aliꞌa katiꞌa apategae. Apakaemo Yuta kotega taoniꞌafi taoniꞌafiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa ani hetamaꞌapimo alisayafeꞌmo Gotiꞌa taoniꞌaꞌe taoniꞌaꞌeꞌmo kigiye.
\v 36 Aliꞌyakamo neꞌaliya vayaꞌai apakinago vayaꞌmogi ani mopamo alisageꞌa Gotifeꞌmo hapauꞌnisiya vayaꞌmogimo ani mopaleꞌmo maige maige huꞌa alagi maigae.
\c 72
\s1 Ala kini vekaeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1-2 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, kagaemo kini vekamo alagepa aipa agesamo alika amiꞌnegenoꞌao vayakaleꞌmo alagepa huno yagaino apateno. Fatago kavakamo alika kini vekamo mafaꞌneꞌamo amiꞌnegenoꞌao kagemi yaꞌapimo oꞌmaleꞌnisaya vayaꞌaiteꞌmo alagepa huno yagaino apateno.
\v 3 Fatago kavaꞌaletiꞌmo yagaino apateꞌninageꞌa aise aveleꞌe alopa aveleꞌeꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maisageno hoyaꞌapifatiꞌmo alagepa neꞌyaꞌmo afole aigiye.
\v 4 Kini vekamoꞌa kagemi yaꞌapimo oꞌmaleꞌnisaya vayaꞌmo hapa maege kafu nehaya vayaꞌmo hapa maege huteno apakaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo apamagiteno alino afepi apategaiye.
\p 
\v 5 Yegemo lege kaimo lege nehisigeꞌapaeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo kagaefekeꞌmo mono hugae.
\v 6 Ko neꞌaigenoꞌaeꞌmo hoyaꞌe mopaꞌeꞌmo alagepa huno nehaneya agufa kavaꞌmo huno hapa maesigeꞌa alagepa huꞌa maigae.
\v 7 Maige maige huno maiꞌnisigeꞌapaeꞌmo fatago vayaꞌmo magoꞌe huꞌa alagepa huꞌa maigae. Muki afinaꞌmo kaimo nelegeꞌapaeꞌmo alagepa huꞌa magokepi lokaeꞌa maigae.
\p 
\v 8 Solovala aniꞌmo aluga aluga atupaleꞌmo yagaino apategaiye. Alopa aniꞌmo nelamiya aniteꞌe mugagaya faligaꞌeꞌmo muki vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino apategaiye.
\v 9 Kaꞌme kotega maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo agaeteꞌmo ape huꞌa maisageꞌapaeꞌmo kame vayaꞌamogimo agaefeꞌmo atete huteꞌa apagoꞌya faigae.
\v 10 Sipeni koteꞌmo neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogiꞌe muki solovala agiꞌnaleꞌmo neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo muki yaꞌmo fiku alini eꞌa amigae. Alepiya koteꞌmo neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogiꞌe Itiyopiya koteꞌmo neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo ofalinimo fiku amigae.
\v 11 Muki kini vayaꞌamogimo agaeteꞌmo ape huꞌa maisageꞌapaeꞌmo muki alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌmogimo geꞌamo afiteꞌa akame hugae.
\p 
\v 12 Kagemi yaꞌapimo oꞌmaleꞌnisaya vayaꞌmogimo agaefeꞌmo keya aeꞌa ge nehisagenoꞌaeꞌmo apakufamo alino katino apategaiye. Kafu nehaya vayaꞌmo hapa maege hapa noꞌmaeya vayaꞌmo hapa maege huno hapa maegaiye.
\v 13 Agaemo lokiyaꞌapimo nohaneya vayaꞌe kafu nehaya vayaꞌefeꞌmo hau huno apategaiye. Kafu nehaya vayaꞌai apakufamo alino katino apategaiye.
\v 14 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo humi apatege apakufamo aliꞌa afepi apatege huteꞌa neꞌapamagigenoꞌaeꞌmo miya faino hatu maeno apategaiye. Apakaemo kolaꞌapimo hisiyafeꞌmo ohauꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo, kolaꞌapieꞌmo hogote yaꞌmo haneꞌniye, huno agesamo neꞌafiye.
\p 
\v 15 Agaemo ofalino afaꞌa maigiye. Alepiya kotegatiꞌmo monimo aliniꞌeꞌa amigae. Muki afinaꞌmo nunumu huꞌa ategae. Muki afinaꞌae afinaꞌaeꞌmo ala agiꞌamo amigae.
\v 16 Avina yaꞌmo apayapiꞌmo neꞌaliya agufa yakana huno ma mopafiꞌmo mago anaga aveleꞌmo hakalegaiye. Hagetenoꞌaeꞌmo asole neꞌyaꞌmo aesigenoꞌaeꞌmo Lemani avefatiꞌmo alopa yosamoꞌmo uti uti neꞌaiya agufa kavaꞌmo hugiye. Asole kahaumo alagepa huno nelagiya kava huꞌa taonifiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo lusi kava huꞌa asole vayaꞌmo afole aigae.
\v 17 Yegemo haneꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo agiꞌamo hanege hanege huno haneꞌnisigeꞌa agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huge huge huꞌa maigae. Gotiꞌa agaetetiꞌmo muki vayaꞌmo hapa maegaiye. Muki alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa ategae.
\v 18 Agaiꞌageꞌmo hapau neꞌaiya agufa alagepa kavaꞌmo nehiyaꞌmofeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo Isaleli vayaꞌai Gotiꞌapimo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa ateyo.
\v 19 Ha le konali agiꞌaleꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hiyo. Ala agiꞌamoꞌmo muki ma mopafiꞌmo aino atagu faeno uneno hisigeꞌa muki vayaꞌmogimo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hiyo. He, lama ge, lama ge.
\p 
\v 20 Neviniꞌmo Yesi mafaꞌneꞌamoꞌmo muki alu ge alu gemo huno nunumu huge huge huno maiꞌniya nunumu geꞌamo alagi huno hano huꞌniye.
\c 73
\s1 Esafiꞌa hosu kavafeꞌmo haꞌye huꞌnigeno Gotiꞌa alino api aino ateꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ina gemo alagi lama gemo huꞌnae. Gotiꞌa Isaleli vayaꞌmo yaveyave apaipa vayaꞌalegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo huno hapa neꞌmae. Yaveyave apaipa vayaꞌalegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo nehiye.
\v 2 Alagepa kavaꞌmo nehiyaꞌmonanafa nagaemo alagi ago hogoꞌamo asagauꞌna aisuva agufa kavaꞌmo huꞌnove. Alagi hogoꞌamo lole nagesamo afiteꞌna aeꞌna halu vale lamiꞌna asagauꞌna aisuva agufa kavaꞌmo huꞌnove.
\v 3 Apakovana himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogi alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnageꞌna apaketeꞌnaeꞌmo maiꞌnaya agufa kavaꞌmo huꞌna maiguve, huꞌna huteꞌnaeꞌmo nahaꞌye huꞌniye.
\p 
\v 4 Faligefeꞌmo nehagenoꞌaeꞌmo apakufamoꞌmo lokiya vaiteno apakafu nokiye.
\v 5 Muki vayaꞌmogimo hanageke yaꞌmo neꞌaliyaꞌmonanafa noꞌaliye. Muki vayaꞌmogimo hosu yaꞌmo neꞌaliyaꞌmonanafa noꞌaliye.
\v 6 Himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo nehaya kavaꞌapimoꞌa ha le konali yaꞌapigana huno haneꞌniye. Kame nehaya kavaꞌapimoꞌa kukenaꞌapigana huno haneꞌniye.
\v 7 Apafayaꞌe vayaꞌmo maiꞌnageno apakufamo ko nesiye. Hosu kavaꞌapimoꞌa apaipafiꞌmo havai teteno aino vali nelamiye.
\v 8 Huꞌa faipa huꞌa apatege apaini huꞌa apatege nehae. Himuꞌnamu gemo huteꞌapaeꞌmo alita afepi lapategaune, huꞌa nehae.
\v 9 Kokuꞌnapi maiꞌniya Gotifeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa neꞌatae. Hosu geꞌapimoꞌmo aino atagu faeno uneno huꞌniye.
\p 
\v 10 Ani kavaꞌmo nehayaꞌmofeꞌmo Goti vayaꞌamogimo aiꞌa atagineꞌa manileꞌmo neꞌae. Apakaemo kapufiꞌmo aniꞌmo havai teꞌnigeꞌa aliꞌa neꞌnae.
\v 11 Apakaemo, Haiya kava huno Gotiꞌa afigiye, huꞌa nehae. Anaga vekamo aeno apakaseꞌniya vekamoꞌmo lageꞌnifiye, huꞌa nehae.
\v 12 Apako, huꞌna, ani vayaꞌmogi Gotifeꞌmo mono nosaya vayaꞌmogimo muki afinaꞌmo maiꞌa falu huꞌa maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo magoꞌe magoꞌe huꞌa kagemi yaꞌmo afaꞌa neꞌaliye.
\v 13 Nagaemo naipafatiꞌmo hosu kavaꞌnimo aeꞌna kalo paeteꞌna nayaꞌmo sese huꞌnovaꞌmonanafa aliꞌyaꞌnimo afole noꞌaiye.
\v 14 Netepiꞌmo kaita nahautenoꞌaeꞌmo nahaulinuno unetiꞌniye. Muki neteꞌae neteꞌaeꞌmo kayoꞌmo neꞌnamine.
\v 15 Nagaemo, ani kavafeꞌmo ava gemo huꞌna hapa paiguve, huꞌna huꞌnovesinana mafaꞌnekalegamo hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnogeꞌa asagauꞌa aiꞌnaesine.
\v 16 Ani kavaꞌmo aepaꞌamo agesuvafeꞌmo lusi kava huno alagaꞌmo nahaeꞌniye.
\v 17 Alagaꞌmo nahaeꞌnigeꞌna oꞌageꞌna maime maime neꞌeꞌna Gotitegamo neꞌuꞌnaeꞌmo hano hisiya afinaꞌmo ageꞌnove.
\p 
\v 18 Alagi lama gemo nehuve. Kagaemo alika halu neꞌvaleya katekeꞌmo apateꞌnane. Kagaemo alika yaga auka neꞌapatalanageꞌapaeꞌmo alagi uꞌa lamiꞌa hano nehae.
\v 19 Lusi hosu yaꞌmo alika neꞌapaminageꞌapaeꞌmo malage huꞌa uꞌa lamiꞌa hano nehae. Lusi kava huꞌa apamoꞌya neꞌaiya kavaꞌmoꞌa atafi kaegekana huꞌa aliꞌa hano huꞌa neꞌapatalae.
\v 20 Haniꞌilagamo alagamuna ageteꞌapaeꞌmo apaupatiꞌmo he netigenoꞌaeꞌmo ani alagamunamo ago apake nekaniya kava huꞌa malage huꞌa hano hugae. Ala kava nene, huꞌna, ani kavaꞌmo huka kaupatiꞌmo he tika apauneꞌageꞌmo apaketekaeꞌmo alagi okahaugiye.
\p 
\v 21 Naipamoꞌmo kana huꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo naipafatiꞌmo atu nahaeꞌniye.
\v 22 Negi nagi kavaꞌmo huteꞌna oꞌagege oꞌafige huteꞌna kaulagaleꞌmo maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo afela afugana huꞌna maiꞌnove.
\v 23 Ani kavakeꞌmo huꞌna maiꞌnovaꞌmonanafa nagaemo muki afinaꞌmo kagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌna maiꞌnogeka nayapiꞌmo natafauka maiꞌnane.
\v 24 Hemenimo kagaemo gekaletiꞌmo alika ho huka nateteka henagaꞌamo ha le konali koteꞌmo navalelika haigane.
\v 25 Kokuꞌnapiꞌmo mago naha maesiya vekamo oꞌmaiꞌniyaꞌmonanafa kagaekeꞌmo maiꞌnane. Ma mopafi vekaeꞌmo nahaꞌye nehiya vekamo mago oꞌmaiꞌniyaꞌmonanafa kagaekeꞌmo maiꞌnane.
\v 26 Nagufaꞌe naipa nagesaꞌeꞌmo hano hugiyaꞌmonanafa naipamo alika lokiya vaika nateteka muki afinaꞌmo hetamaꞌnimo kagaekeꞌmo maiꞌnane.
\p 
\v 27 Kahaopaleꞌmo eꞌa oꞌmaiꞌa afagiꞌaleꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo alagi lageso hugae. Kagaemo kataleꞌa neꞌvaya vayaꞌmo alika apagoꞌya laga nehanaꞌmonanafa
\v 28 kahaopaleꞌmo uꞌna maisuva kavaꞌmo kanale kavane. Nagaemo muki nehana kavafeꞌmo ava gemo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paisuvafeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo Gotiꞌnimoꞌa alagepa huno naha maegaiye, huꞌna huteꞌna maiꞌnove.
\c 78
\s1 Isaleli vayaꞌai hosu kavaꞌapieꞌmo apava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Vayaꞌnimogitapae, huꞌna, aliꞌna lapaya malegefeꞌmo huvanagi geꞌnimo afiyo. Gemo lapa paigefeꞌmo huvanagi mani gemo alagepa hutapa afiyo.
\v 2 Akeyaꞌvilaga kavafeꞌmo aeꞌna kalafefa gemo huꞌna aepaꞌaeꞌmo lapa paiguve.
\v 3 Laginago vayaꞌmogi laha paiꞌnageta afiꞌnona gemo halate lapa paiguve.
\v 4 Lagaemo aeta ati okaeta Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa lokiya kavaꞌaꞌe hapau aiꞌnaya kavaꞌaꞌefeꞌmo ava gemo huta mafaꞌnetieꞌmo hapa paiteta henagaꞌamo afole aisaya mafaꞌnetieꞌmo hapa paigune.
\v 5-6 Agaemo Isaleli vayaꞌaifeꞌmo keꞌaepa geꞌamo hapa paiꞌniya agufa gemo huno Yekopu aginago vayaꞌaifeꞌmo ma kava hiyo, huno hapa paiꞌniye. Laginago vayaꞌaifeꞌmo, keꞌaepa geꞌnimo mafaꞌnetapimo alita apaya malegeꞌapao aliꞌa apatesaya mafaꞌneꞌapimogi afiteꞌapaeꞌmo mafaꞌneꞌapieꞌmo halate hapa paiyo, huno hapa paiꞌniye.
\v 7 Afiteꞌapaeꞌmo Gotifeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago huteꞌa Gotiꞌa huꞌniya kavafeꞌmo apake okaniꞌa keꞌaepa geꞌamo akame hugae.
\v 8 Apakinago vayaꞌmogimo himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa geꞌamo oꞌafiꞌa Gotifeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago osuꞌa ataleꞌa uꞌnae. Fiku yanageꞌa apakaeꞌeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo huꞌa maigae.
\v 9 Ifalemi nofi vayaꞌmogimo atiꞌapimo aliteꞌa uꞌnayaꞌmonanafa kame osuꞌa ataleꞌa aiꞌa atagi neꞌa eꞌnae.
\v 10 Apakaemo Goti kotalake geꞌamo akame osuꞌa keꞌaepa geꞌamo ago amagiꞌa ataleꞌnae.
\v 11 Huꞌniya aune kavafeꞌmo ago apake kaniꞌniye.
\v 12 Agaemo afoꞌapimogi apaulagaleꞌmo Isipi kotega Sovani koteꞌmo aune kavaꞌmo huꞌniye.
\v 13 Solovala aniꞌmoꞌa folagapatiꞌmo aino akaka vaelino ani anagamo haino hanete ani afelagamo lamino hanete huꞌnigeꞌa folagapatiꞌmo uꞌnae.
\v 14 Agaemo felugamo hiyaꞌmo uno hogoteno apavalelino uꞌniya kava huno haniꞌilagaꞌeꞌmo ata vaiꞌmo leno halelino uno hogoteno apavalelino uꞌniye.
\v 15 Agaemo kaꞌme koteꞌmo aniꞌmo ohaneꞌniya koteꞌmo yafaꞌmo amagino apalo atiꞌnigeno afepatiꞌmo alopa aniꞌmo haineno asagauno aiꞌnigeꞌa neꞌnae.
\v 16 Yafapatiꞌmo alopa aniꞌmo emineꞌnigeꞌa nege nege huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\p 
\v 17 Huꞌniyaꞌmonanafa kaꞌme kotegamo hogote vekamo anaga vekalegamo magoꞌe magoꞌe huꞌa hosu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa geꞌamo ago amagiꞌa ataleꞌnae.
\v 18 Gotifeꞌmo, lahauꞌniya neꞌyaꞌmo alika lamiyo, huꞌa amalageka huꞌnae.
\v 19 Apakaemo Gotifeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa ateteꞌapaeꞌmo, Gotiꞌa kaꞌme koteꞌmo alopa neꞌyaꞌmo afaꞌa lamigifiye, huꞌa huꞌnae.
\v 20 Agaemo yafaꞌmo amagiꞌnigeno alopa aniꞌmo eminetenoꞌaeꞌmo ani aniꞌmo afaꞌa heꞌniye. Ani kavaꞌmo huꞌniyaꞌmonanafa neꞌyaꞌe afumo ameꞌaꞌeꞌmo afaꞌa lamigifiye, huꞌa huꞌnae.
\v 21-22 Huꞌa huꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa afitenoꞌaeꞌmo lusi kava huno aipamo leno apateꞌniye. Yekopu vayaꞌmo atamoꞌmo emineno leno apasaga liꞌniye. Lagufamo alino katino lategaiye, huꞌa apakesa afiꞌa fatago osuꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo aipamo leno apateꞌniye.
\v 23-24 Apakesa afiꞌa fatago osuꞌnayaꞌmonanafa kokuꞌnafeꞌmo aika akaka vao, huno huꞌnigeno aino akaka vaeꞌnigeno koꞌmo aigekana huno mago neꞌyaꞌmo agiꞌamo mana neꞌyaꞌmo asagauno aiꞌnigeꞌa aliꞌa neꞌnae.
\v 25 Gotiꞌa enisole vayaꞌmogi neꞌyaꞌmo ma mopafi vayaꞌmo alino apamiꞌnigeꞌa ago aliꞌa neꞌa apamu huꞌnae.
\v 26 Agaemo, yasimo aliyo, huno huꞌnigeno yegemo haine neꞌeya kotegatiꞌmo yasimo aliꞌniye. Himamuꞌaletiꞌmo yasimo aliyo, huno huꞌnigeno aluga aluga haopalegatiꞌmo yasimo aliꞌniye.
\v 27 Yasimoꞌmo nama anagaꞌmo mumusopakana huno lekana opaisaya agufa nama anagaꞌmo apavalelino eꞌnigeꞌa eꞌa ani kahaepagana huꞌa asagauꞌa aiꞌnae.
\v 28 Maiꞌnaya folagapiꞌmo asagauꞌa aige muki seli noteꞌmo asagauꞌa aige huꞌa asagauꞌa aiꞌnae.
\v 29 Agaemo hapauꞌniya neꞌyaꞌmo alino apamiꞌnigeꞌa aliꞌa neꞌa apamu huꞌnae.
\v 30-31 Neꞌyaꞌmo afaꞌa alino lamigifiye, huꞌa huteꞌa amalageka huteꞌa apakesamo afiꞌa fatago osuꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo apamiꞌniya neꞌyaꞌmo neꞌa oꞌnakaiꞌa apavayafiꞌmo haniliꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo Gotiꞌa aipamo leno apateteno Isaleli vayapatiꞌmo hogote lokiya vayaꞌageꞌmo ago apamagiꞌnigeꞌa faliꞌnae.
\v 32-33 Ani kavaꞌmo huꞌniyaꞌmonanafa agaetegamo magoꞌe magoꞌe huꞌageꞌmo hosu kavakeꞌmo huꞌa maiꞌnae. Aune kavaꞌmo huꞌniyaꞌmonanafa apakesa afiꞌa fatago osuꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo afa aliꞌya aliteꞌa koli hume hume uꞌa faliꞌnae.
\v 34 Apamagiꞌnigeꞌa faliꞌnageꞌapaeꞌmo mago vayaꞌamogimo apaipamo aliꞌa afe leꞌa Gotiꞌmo agesayafeꞌmo lokiya vaiꞌa kahauya huꞌnae.
\v 35 Apakaemo, Gotiꞌa yagaino nelateya vekamo maiꞌniye. Lokiya vekamoꞌa laha neꞌmaeya vekamo maiꞌniye, huꞌa halate apakesamo afiꞌnae.
\v 36 Kanale vekamo maiꞌniye, huꞌa huꞌnayana apaipafatiꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa osuꞌnafa apavayaꞌaletikeꞌmo aigofe gemo huꞌnae.
\v 37 Agaetefeꞌmo apaipamo kanale osigeꞌa kotalake geꞌamo ago amagiꞌa ataleꞌnae.
\v 38 Ani kavaꞌmo huꞌnayaꞌmonanafa hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauꞌniya vekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo muki vayaꞌamo kamiti oꞌapamagiꞌnifa hosu kavaꞌapigeꞌmo alino ataleꞌniye. Muki afinaꞌmo aipamo lege lege huno maiꞌniyaꞌmonanafa ataleteno aipamo leno apateꞌniya kavaꞌaꞌeꞌmo ataleꞌniye.
\v 39 Agaemo, Vayatafaꞌmo maiꞌnae. Apava musa neꞌaiya yaꞌmo malage huno hano nehiya kava huꞌa neꞌmaiye, huno agesa afiꞌniye.
\v 40 Muki afinaꞌmo kaꞌme kotegamo maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo geꞌamo ago amagiꞌa ataleꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo aipamoꞌmo kana huꞌniye.
\v 41 Apakaemo muki afinaꞌmo Gotiꞌmo amalageka huge Isaleli vayaꞌai aote Gotiꞌapimo kaꞌamo akani malege huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 42 Apakaemo himamuꞌaletiꞌmo huꞌniya kavaꞌaeꞌmo ago apake kanige kame vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo apakufamo alino katino apateꞌniya kavaꞌaeꞌmo ago apake kanige huꞌnigeꞌa apakesamo oꞌafiꞌnae.
\v 43 Hogoteno himamuꞌaletiꞌmo aune kavaꞌmo Isipi kotegamo mago Sovani koteꞌmo huꞌniya kavafeꞌmo apakesamo oꞌafiꞌnae.
\v 44 Agaemo alopa aniꞌe aise aniꞌeꞌmo alino kola aniꞌmo hamaleno ateꞌnigeꞌa Isipi vayaꞌmogimo oꞌneꞌnae.
\v 45 Agaemo asole kosiꞌmo alino apateꞌnigeꞌa eꞌa hapaege esoꞌmo alino apateꞌnigeꞌa eꞌa muki mopaꞌapileꞌmo haneꞌniya yaꞌmo aliꞌa hosu huꞌa atege huꞌnae.
\v 46 Agaemo mago kafamo alino apateꞌnigeꞌa eꞌa hoyaꞌapifiꞌmo haneꞌniya neꞌyaꞌmo nege akenuꞌmo alino apateꞌnigeꞌa eꞌa hoyaꞌapifiꞌmo hakale maleꞌnaya neꞌyaꞌmo nege huꞌnae.
\v 47 Agaemo ko mopa koꞌmo alino ataleꞌnigeno emineno alagamo neꞌaeya nofiꞌapimo amagino falu atiꞌniye. Agaemo haniꞌilagamo ko mopagana huno lao yaꞌmo alino ataleꞌnigeno emineꞌnigeno alagamo neꞌaeya yosa hoyaꞌapimo falu teꞌniye.
\v 48 Agaemo ko mopa koꞌmo alino ataleꞌnigeno emineno pulumakaꞌapimo apamagiꞌnigeꞌa faliꞌnae.
\v 49 Gotiꞌa aipamo leno apatege hai vaino apatege huteno hanageke yaꞌmo alino apamiꞌnigeno apakafu kiꞌniye. Ani kava huꞌa enisole vayaꞌmogimo apamagiꞌnageꞌa faliꞌnae.
\v 50 Aipamo leno apatetenoꞌaeꞌmo afaꞌa apakeno oꞌapataleꞌnifa apamagiꞌnigeno kaita hapauꞌnigeꞌa ago faliꞌnae.
\v 51 Agaemo Isipi kotega vayaꞌai muki yege mafaꞌneꞌapimo kamiti apamagiꞌnigeꞌa ago faliꞌnae.
\v 52 Apamagiꞌniyaꞌmonanafa sipisipimo apavaleliꞌa neꞌvaya kava huno vayaꞌamo kaꞌme kotegamo apavalelino uꞌniye.
\v 53 Alagepa huno yagaino apateꞌnigeꞌa koli osuꞌa afaꞌa uꞌnayaꞌmonanafa solovala aniꞌmoꞌa kame vayaꞌapimo ago aeno apati kaeꞌniye.
\v 54 Apavalelino uno aote mopaleꞌmo himamuꞌaletiꞌmo aliꞌniya aveleꞌmo apateꞌniye.
\v 55 Agaemo alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌmo ago alino hapa faitaleno mopaꞌapimo hapafaleno hakino apamiteno seli noꞌapifiꞌmo alino apateꞌniye.
\p 
\v 56 Ani kavaꞌmo huꞌniyaꞌmonanafa hogote anaga vekamo Gotiꞌa amalageka huteꞌa himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa ma kavaꞌmo hiyo, huno huꞌniya gemo ago amagiꞌa ataleꞌnae.
\v 57 Afoꞌapimogi himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa ataleꞌnaya kava huꞌa maiꞌneꞌa kayagiꞌniya kevemo hetalageno kahaufilagamo neꞌviya kava huꞌa ataleꞌa hosu kateꞌmo uꞌnae.
\v 58 Apakaemo aveꞌale aveꞌaleꞌmo aigofe gotiꞌapimogifeꞌmo mono huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo aipamo leno apateꞌniye. Aigofe gotiꞌapimo auneꞌamo alo hu maleꞌneꞌa mono huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo hosu aipamo kaliꞌniye.
\v 59 Gotiꞌa apaketenoꞌaeꞌmo aipamo leno apateteno agaiꞌa vayaꞌamo akameꞌya apamiꞌniye.
\v 60 Agaemo Sailo kotega seli mono nopiꞌmo neꞌmaiya nopatiꞌmo ataleno uꞌniye.
\v 61 Agaiꞌa vayaꞌamo hapa oꞌmaeno kame vayaꞌapimo alino apateꞌnigeꞌa eꞌa kame huꞌa aeꞌa apakaseteꞌa kotalake gemo hu maleꞌniya kesimo kumaya aliniꞌa uꞌnae. Ani kesimo apakaeꞌeꞌmo ohaneꞌniya kava huno himamuꞌaꞌe ha le konali yaꞌaꞌeꞌmo apakaeꞌeꞌmo ohaneꞌniye.
\v 62 Agaemo agaiꞌa vayaꞌaifeꞌmo aipamo leno apateteno kame vayaꞌapimo alino apateꞌnigeꞌa eꞌa naipeletiꞌmo apaiꞌnae.
\v 63 Kame huteꞌapaeꞌmo neya vayaꞌapimo kamiti apaiꞌnageꞌa faliꞌnageꞌapaeꞌmo aꞌmafaꞌneꞌapimo veleꞌmo oꞌmaiꞌa afaꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 64 Kame vayaꞌapimogimo mono huꞌa neꞌapataya vayaꞌapimo kamiti apaiꞌnageꞌapaeꞌmo aꞌneꞌapimogimo yulagefa oꞌaige aviꞌya huꞌa oꞌapatege huꞌnae.
\p 
\v 65 Ani kavaꞌmo huꞌa maiꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo apaupatiꞌmo he netiya kava huno Ala kava neꞌmo he tiꞌniye. Lokiya vekamoꞌa nofi alagafati aniꞌmo netenoꞌaeꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo ge nehiya kava huno Ala kava neꞌmo malage huno he tiꞌniye.
\v 66 Malage huno kame vayaꞌamo alino hapa faino apataleꞌnigeno apavagage huꞌnigeꞌa uꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 67-68 Agaemo vayaꞌaleꞌmo yagaiꞌa apatesayafeꞌmo Yosefe aginago vayapatiꞌmo lekana paino oꞌapateno apataleno uno Ifalemi nofi vayapatiꞌmo lekana paino oꞌapateno apataleno uno Yuta nofi vayapatikeꞌmo lekana paino apateteno Saiyoni aveeꞌmo hauꞌniya avemo lekana paino ateꞌniye.
\v 69 Agaemo ani aveleꞌmo mono noꞌamo avegana huno ki maleꞌniye. Ma mopamo lokiya vaino haneꞌniya kava huno noꞌamo lokiya noꞌmo ki maleꞌniye.
\v 70-71 Agaemo Yuta nofi vayapatiꞌmo Neviniꞌmo lekana paino ateteno sipisipileꞌmo yagaino maiꞌniya kotegatiꞌmo avalelino uno Isaleli vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino apatesiya kini vekamo ateꞌniye.
\v 72 Ateꞌnigeno Neviniꞌa aliꞌyaꞌalefekeꞌmo agesamo afiteno alagepa huno yagaino apateꞌniye.
\c 84
\s1 Gotiꞌa laha maegaiye, huꞌa nehaya vayaꞌmogigeꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maisaya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, muki vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaika neꞌapatana vekae. Nagaemo maiꞌnanatega mono nokaeꞌmo lusi kava huno neꞌnahaiye.
\v 2 Nokafiꞌmo maisuva yafeꞌmo lusi kava huno naipamoꞌmo nehaiye. Muki nagufamoꞌe naipa nagesafatiꞌeꞌmo afaꞌa neꞌmaiya Gotifekeꞌmo nehaiye.
\v 3 Aise nama anagaꞌmogi apanoꞌmo kiteꞌa maiꞌnageꞌapaeꞌmo kisaveꞌyavemogi apanoꞌmo haneꞌnigeꞌa apamuꞌmo maleteꞌa aiꞌa apalo atiteꞌa neꞌyagaiye. Nokafiꞌmo neꞌmaiyaꞌmonanafa muki vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaika neꞌapatana vekae, huꞌna, kini vekaꞌnimo Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, nokafiꞌmo oꞌmaiꞌneꞌna ofalinimo kamisuva hiꞌyalamukaleꞌmo ofalinimo nehaya hiꞌyalamukaleꞌe hiꞌyalamukaleꞌefeꞌmo nagesamo neꞌafuve.
\v 4 Nokafiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa yokemo huꞌa kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga nehaya vayaꞌmogi kaulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\p 
\v 5 Lokiyaꞌapimo kagaetegatiꞌmo aliꞌnisaya vayaꞌmogimo kaulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa apamogaga aigae. Kagaetegamo visaya apaipamo nekaliye.
\v 6 Kaꞌmo umenitata nehuꞌapaeꞌmo aniꞌmo leno laneꞌniya kalokalopafiꞌmo apaunumo uno nelamigeꞌa umenitata nehuꞌapaeꞌmo kelimo kafi maleꞌnageno koꞌmo aiteno aniꞌmo maleno havai teꞌnigeꞌa neꞌnae.
\v 7 Lokiya vaime vaime uꞌa magoꞌe huꞌa lokiya vaiꞌa uꞌa aigofe gotiꞌapimogimo aeno apakaseꞌniya Gotitegamo Saiyoni kotegamo agegae.
\p 
\v 8 Muki vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaika neꞌapatana vekae, huꞌna, nunumu nehuvanagi geꞌnimo afiyo. Yekopu Gotiꞌamogae, huꞌna, afiyo.
\v 9 O Gotiyo, halegutimogae, huꞌna, ago. Lekana paika ateꞌnana vekamo augosafiꞌmo ago.
\v 10 Mago alagepa haopalegamo uꞌna yatala afinaꞌmo maisuvana namogaga aiguvaꞌmonanafa nokafiꞌmo aise afinaꞌmo maisuvana magoꞌe huꞌna namogaga aiguve. Nagaemo Gotiꞌnimo noꞌafiꞌmo afa ina agufa vekamo kipateꞌmo neꞌyagauva vekamo maisuvafeꞌmo nahauꞌniyaꞌmonanafa hosu vayaꞌai noꞌapifiꞌmo haiꞌna maisuvafeꞌmo oꞌnahauꞌniye.
\v 11 Ala kava netimoꞌa yegetiꞌe halegutiꞌeꞌmo maiꞌniye. Agaemo ala apakiꞌapimo apamiteno alagepa yaꞌmo fiku hapa maeno apamigiye. Agaemo api kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo magoke alagepa yaꞌmo magokeꞌageꞌmo aliꞌna lapamiguve huno osugifa muki alagepa yaꞌamo afaꞌa alino apamigiye.
\v 12 Muki vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaika neꞌapatana vekae, huꞌna, Kagaefekeꞌmo, laha maegaiye, huꞌa apakesamo neꞌafiya vayaꞌmogi kaulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogagamo aigae.
\c 85
\s1 Hau huno neꞌapateya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kagaemo mopakaleꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo alagepa huka hapa maeꞌnane. Kagaemo Yekopu nofi vayaꞌmo hatu maeka apateteka apavalelika eka apakaiꞌapi mopaleꞌmo apateꞌnane.
\v 2 Kagaemo vayakamogi hosu kavaꞌapimo alika ataletekaeꞌmo, afaꞌa ateyo, huka huꞌnane. Muki hosu kavaꞌapimo aeka ati kaeka ataleꞌnane.
\v 3 Hogoteka kaipamo leka apateꞌnanaꞌmonanafa henagaꞌamo kaipamo falu huka apateꞌnane. Lusi kava huno kaipamo leꞌniyana afaꞌa ataleꞌnane.
\p 
\v 4 O, Gotiyo, huꞌna, lagufamo alika katika nelatana vekamae. Halate alika alagepa huka lateteka alika aika atagi neka lavalelika eno. Kaipamo falu huka lato.
\v 5 Muki afinaꞌmo kaipamo leka latesapiye. Hemenimo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaifenagi henagaꞌamo afole aiꞌa maisaya vayaꞌaifenagi huka kaipamo leka apateka hano osuka leka apateme apateme ugapiye.
\v 6 Faligekana huta maiꞌnonagi halate alika he tika olategapiye. Vayakamogimo kagaefekeꞌmo apamogaga aisayafeꞌmae.
\v 7 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahau huka lato. Lagufamo alika katika lato.
\p 
\v 8 Nagaemo Ala kava neꞌmo Gotiꞌa hisiya gemo afiguve. Agaemo agaiꞌa vayaꞌmo apaote vayaꞌaifeꞌmo alino nanu aeno apatesiya geeꞌmo hunoꞌaeꞌmo, lapaipamoꞌmo falu hino, huno hapa paigiye. Hapa paigiyaꞌmonanafa fiku kavanageꞌa aiꞌa atagineꞌa eꞌa halate negi kavaꞌmo hugae.
\v 9 Ha le konali yaꞌamoꞌmo lagae mopaleꞌmo hanege hanege huno hanesiyafeꞌmo agaefeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌmo hapaopaleꞌmo eno apakufamo alino katino apategaiye.
\p 
\v 10 Hau huno apatesiya kavaꞌaꞌe lama geꞌaꞌeꞌmo eꞌana fotu huꞌnaꞌae. Fatago kavaꞌaꞌe alino nanu aeno apatesiya kavaꞌaꞌeꞌmo eꞌana hanaeꞌana neꞌnaꞌae.
\v 11 Lama ge kavaꞌmoꞌa ma mopafatiꞌmo hagegekana huno afole aisigeno fatago kavaꞌmoꞌa kokuꞌnapatiꞌmo he tino aeno kamafaino apakegaiye.
\v 12 He, Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alagepa yaꞌmo alino lamisigeno lagae mopafatiꞌmo neꞌyaꞌmo hagegaiye.
\v 13 Fatago kavaꞌmo hogoteno neꞌvisigenoꞌaeꞌmo agaemo egaiye. Fatago kavaꞌamo aiyakamo alisunafeꞌmo kaꞌmo valino lategaiye.
\c 87
\s1 Saiyoni taonimo haneꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Gotiꞌa taoniꞌamo aoteꞌmo hu maleꞌniya aveleꞌale aveleꞌaleꞌmo faino ateꞌniye.
\v 2 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa Yekopu aginago vayaꞌamogimo noꞌapifi noꞌapifiꞌmo apaote apaote huꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauꞌniyaꞌmonanafa Saiyoni mono no yafa lafi kegiyafiꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo magoꞌe huno hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauꞌniye.
\v 3 Gotiꞌa agaiꞌa taonifatiꞌmo ha le konali yaꞌamo mago vayaꞌmo alino apave liꞌnigeꞌa ageteꞌapaeꞌmo ava gemo nehae.
\p 
\v 4 Nagaemo, Isipi kotega maiꞌnaya vayaꞌe Mamiloni kotega maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo nageꞌa aeto huꞌnae, huꞌna huguve. Afiyo, Filisitiya vayanagi Taiya vayanagi Itiyopiya vayanagi huno Gotiꞌa taoniꞌafiꞌmo apavaleno apatesigeꞌa vayaꞌamo maigae.
\p 
\v 5 Apakaemo, ani vayaꞌe ani vayaꞌeꞌmo Gotiꞌa taoniꞌafiꞌmo apavaleno apateꞌniye, huꞌa hugae. Anaga hogote vekamoꞌmo agaiꞌamo ani taonimo alino lokiya vaino atesigeno afaꞌa hanege hanege huno hanegaiye.
\v 6 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa agaiꞌa taonifiꞌmo apavaleno apateꞌniya vayaꞌai apakiꞌapimo mukufiꞌmo avoꞌmo kae malegaiye.
\p 
\v 7 Yokemo huꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo, muki yaꞌamo aepa vekamo maiꞌnanagetaeꞌmo kagaetegatikeꞌmo muki yaꞌamo neꞌalune, huꞌa yokemo nehae.
\c 89
\s1 Kotalake hu maleꞌniya geꞌaeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 O, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, nagaemo kahau huka neꞌapatana kavaꞌaleꞌe kavaꞌaleꞌefeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo yokegeꞌmo huge huge huꞌna maiguve. Kagaemo gekamo alagi akame nehana kavakaeꞌmo hemenimo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌe aliꞌa apateme apateme visaya vayaꞌefeꞌmo navayafatiꞌmo hapa paiguve.
\v 2 Nagaemo, kagaemo noꞌmo kigekana huka muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa hanesiyafeꞌmo kahau huka apatege apatege huka maigane, huꞌna hapa paiꞌnove. Kagaemo gekamo alagi akame nehana kavakamoꞌmo kokuꞌnapiꞌmo noꞌmo faika ategekana huka maleꞌnane.
\p 
\v 3 Gotiꞌa, Nagaemo mago vekamo lekana paiꞌna ateteꞌna agaeꞌeꞌmo kotalake geꞌnimo magokepiꞌmo hu maleꞌnove. Aliꞌyaꞌnimo neꞌaliya vekamo Nevinifeꞌmo,
\v 4 kagae nofi vayaꞌmogi muki afinaꞌmo lokiya vaiꞌa maigae. Kini vekamo maiꞌneka yagaika neꞌapatana kava huꞌa kini vayaꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa yagaiꞌa apatete apatete hume hume uꞌa maigae, huꞌna ha paiꞌnove.
\p 
\v 5 O, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kokuꞌnapiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogi nehana kavakamo ageteꞌapaeꞌmo hapau aiteꞌa ala kagikamo kamigae. Apaote vayaꞌmo aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo gekamo akame nehana kavakalefeꞌmo alagepa kavaꞌageꞌmo nehiye, huꞌa hugae.
\v 6 Kokuꞌnapiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayapatiꞌmo ina laꞌmo Ala kava nekana huno maiꞌniye. Lokiya vayapatiꞌmo mago vekamoꞌa Ala kava nekana huno oꞌmaiꞌniye.
\v 7 Apaote vayaꞌmo aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maiꞌnayategamo Gotifekeꞌmo lusi kava huꞌa koli huꞌnae. Gotiꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogi agaefeꞌmo koli huꞌnae.
\v 8 O Gotiyo, muki vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaika neꞌapatana Gotigae, huꞌna, Lokiyakaꞌe vekamo maiꞌnanageno ina laꞌmo kagaekana huno maiꞌniye. Gekamo alagi akame nehana kavakamoꞌmo faino ku aino nekate.
\v 9 Solovala aniꞌmoꞌa aino holakau holakau nehigekaeꞌmo yagaika neꞌatane. Solovala aniꞌmoꞌa aepa faino aino holakau hugefe nehigekaeꞌmo afaꞌa hano huka nehanagenoꞌaeꞌmo afaꞌa nehane.
\v 10 Kagaemo Isipi kotega maiꞌnaya vayaꞌai himamuꞌapimo ago alika hano huka ataleꞌnane. Lokiya kayatetiꞌmo kame vayakamo apamagiꞌnanageꞌa atagu faeꞌa uꞌeꞌa huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\p 
\v 11 Kokuꞌnaꞌe ma mopaꞌeꞌmo kagaika yaꞌmo haneꞌniye. Ma mopaꞌe muki ma mopafiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌe yaꞌeꞌmo alo huꞌnane.
\v 12 Aluga aluga haopalegaꞌeꞌmo alo huꞌnane. Alopa avemo Tamo aveꞌmoꞌe Hemoni avemo alopa avemoꞌeꞌmo kagikalefeꞌmo anamogaga neꞌaiꞌae.
\v 13 Himamukaletiꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌmo neꞌaline. Kayaꞌmo lokiya kayaꞌmo haneꞌniye. Lamaga kayatetiꞌmo aeka apakaseꞌnane.
\v 14 Kini vekamo maiꞌneka fatago kavaꞌmo huka alagepa huka alika fako huka apateteka yagaika neꞌapatane. Kahau huka apatege lama geꞌageꞌmo huge huka maiꞌnane.
\v 15 Afiteꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiya gemo afiꞌa aeto huꞌnaya vayaꞌmo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae. Kaugosafatiꞌmo aeno ha neleya yategamo umenitata hugae.
\v 16 Apakaemo kagikalefeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiye. Apakaemo fatago kavakaletiꞌmo ala apakiꞌapimo neꞌaliye.
\v 17 Ha le konali himamuꞌapimo kagaetegatiꞌmo aliꞌnae. Kagaemo fiku laha maeka lamiꞌnanageta aeta apakaseꞌnone.
\v 18 Ala kava neꞌmo halegutigana huno maiꞌniye. Isaleliꞌa aote vekamo kini vekatimo maiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 19 Aote vekakamoꞌa alagamuna agegekana huno ageꞌnigekaeꞌmo ina ge huka ha paiꞌnane. Nagaemo himamuꞌaꞌe vekamo lokiya vaiꞌna ateꞌnove. Nagaemo mago vekamo vayapatiꞌmo lekana paiꞌna ateteꞌna aliꞌna asaga huꞌna ateꞌnove.
\v 20 Nagaemo aliꞌyaꞌnimo alisiya vekamo Neviniꞌmo kahauya huꞌna ageteꞌnaeꞌmo aote uveliletiꞌmo faleꞌna ateꞌnove.
\v 21 Muki afinaꞌmo himamuꞌnimo agaeteꞌmo maleteꞌnaeꞌmo lokiya vaiꞌna ategauve.
\v 22 Kame vekaꞌamoꞌmo anonaꞌalefeꞌmo asole yaꞌmo oꞌalisigeno hosu vekamoꞌa kana yaꞌmo alino oꞌamigiye.
\v 23 Nagaemo kame vayaꞌamo apamagisugeꞌa aulagaleꞌmo asagauꞌa aigae. Nagaemo apaini huꞌa neꞌataya vayaꞌmo kaitaꞌmo apamiguve.
\p 
\v 24 Apamiguvaꞌmonanafa agaefeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo huguve, huꞌna ha paiꞌnova geꞌnimo alagi akame huꞌna nahau huꞌna ategauve. Nagiꞌnilefeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna ategauve.
\v 25 Nagaemo alopa mopaleꞌmo yagaisiyafeꞌmo lokiya vaiꞌna ateꞌnisugeno mago ayaꞌmo solovala aniteꞌmo maleteno mago ayaꞌmo anilafateꞌmo malegaiye.
\v 26 Agaemo alopa gefatiꞌmo nagaefeꞌmo keya aeno ge hunoꞌaeꞌmo, Kagaemo afoꞌnimogamo maiꞌnane. Gotiꞌnimogae, huno, nagufamo alika katika natesana yafaꞌnimo maiꞌnane, huno naha paigiye.
\v 27 Yege mafaꞌneꞌnimo maiꞌniye, huꞌna hu malegauve. Agaemo muki ma mopafiꞌmo maiꞌnaya kini vayaꞌmo ago aeno apakaseno hogote kini vekamo maigiye.
\v 28 Nagaemo muki afinaꞌmo nahau huꞌna atege atege huꞌna maiguve. Agaeꞌeꞌmo kotalake geꞌnimo hu maleꞌnova geꞌnimoꞌa afaꞌa hanege hanege huno hanegaiye.
\v 29 Agae nofi vayaꞌamo afaꞌa maige maige huꞌa maigae. Kokuꞌnaꞌmoꞌa hanege hanege huno hanesiya kava huno muki afinaꞌmo kini vekamo maiꞌneno yagaino apategaiye.
\v 30 Mafaꞌneꞌamogimo keꞌaepa geꞌnimo ataleꞌa aliꞌna fako hu maleꞌnova geꞌnimo akame osuge
\v 31 avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya geꞌnimo amagiꞌa atalege hiyo, huꞌna hapa paiꞌnova gemo akame osuge huꞌa maiꞌnisayaꞌmoꞌmo
\v 32 nagaemo hosu kavaꞌapilefeꞌmo kayoꞌmo apamiteꞌna kayotetiꞌmo apamagisugeno apamuꞌmo apalegaiye.
\v 33 Kayoꞌmo apamiguvaꞌmonanafa alagi aliꞌna hafaiꞌna oꞌataleꞌna agaefeꞌmo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo nahauꞌnisigeꞌna ha maegauve, huꞌna huꞌnova geꞌnimo amagiꞌna oꞌataleꞌna alagi akame huguve.
\v 34 Kotalake geꞌnimo amagiꞌna oꞌataleꞌna navayafatiꞌmo hu maleꞌnova geꞌnileꞌmo alu gemo halate osuguve.
\v 35 Nagaemo magoke afinaꞌmo naote kavaꞌnilefeꞌmo huꞌnaeꞌmo, Nevinifeꞌmo aigofe gemo alagi osuguve, huꞌna nagoꞌyamo ago ataleteꞌna ha paiꞌnove.
\v 36 Agae nofi vayaꞌamo alagi hano osuꞌa afaꞌa maige maige huꞌa maigae. Yegemoꞌmo naulagaleꞌmo lege lege huno neꞌmaiya kava huno muki afinaꞌmo kini vekamo maiꞌneno yagaino apategaiye.
\v 37 Kaimoꞌmo hanege hanege huno nehaneya kava huno fai maiꞌneno yagaino neꞌapateya sialeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo fai maiꞌneno yagaino apategaiye. Kokuꞌnapatiꞌmo kaimoꞌmo, Gotiꞌa maiꞌniye, huno lama gemo nehiye, huno nehiya kaigana huno maiꞌneno yagaino apategaiye.
\p 
\v 38 Kagaemo ani gemo huꞌnanaꞌmonanafa kagaemo ago alika yaga auka ataleteka kakameꞌyamo amiꞌnane. Kagaemo uvelimo faleka ateꞌnana vekaeꞌmo kaipamo leka ateꞌnane.
\v 39 Kagaemo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaliya vekaꞌeꞌmo kotalake gemo hu maleꞌnana gemo ago alika hano huka ataleꞌnane.
\v 40 Kagaemo kegiꞌyaꞌamo ago aeka halagape vaiꞌnane. Halagape oꞌvaisaya agufa lokiya nokoꞌmo heka halagape vaiꞌnane.
\v 41 Muki u eꞌa nehaya vayaꞌmogimo kagemi yaꞌamo kumayaꞌmo neꞌaliye. Haopaleꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo huꞌa faipa huꞌa neꞌatae.
\v 42 Kagaemo kame vayaꞌamo hapa maeꞌnanageꞌa kame huꞌa aeꞌa agaseꞌnae. Hapa maeꞌnanageꞌa apamogaga aiꞌnae.
\v 43 Kagaemo ati vayaꞌamo lokiya vaika oꞌapateꞌnanageꞌa kame huꞌa aeꞌa oꞌapakaseꞌnae. Kagaemo afaꞌa ataleꞌnanageno kame vayaꞌaꞌeꞌmo kame huno aeno oꞌapakaseꞌniye.
\v 44 Kagaemo ha le konali yaꞌamo alika hano huka ataleꞌnane. Yagaino apatesiya himamuꞌamo ago alika hano huka ataleꞌnane.
\v 45 Kagaemo ataleꞌnanageno malage huno ago kosuna leꞌniye. Lokiyaꞌamo ohaneꞌnigeno avagage kavaꞌamoꞌmo aeno ati kaeꞌniye.
\p 
\v 46 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, na magi afinaꞌmo fala kika maigane. Muki afinaꞌmo fala kika maigapiye. Atagana huno kaipamo lesifiye.
\v 47 Maisuva afinaꞌmo aise afinaꞌmo haneꞌniyaꞌmofemo kage okanika kagesamo afiyo. Fiku maisayafeꞌmo muki vayaꞌmo alo huka apateꞌnapiye.
\v 48 Haiya vekamoꞌa ofalino afaꞌa maige maige huno maigiye. Kanolufiꞌmo oꞌmaino faino kasalo paegaifiye.
\p 
\v 49 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Hogoteka Nevinifeꞌmo kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauꞌnigeka alagepa huka ha maeꞌnane. Na kava higeka hemenimo ani kavaꞌmo nosane. Kagaemo Nevinifeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo huguve, huka huteka kagoꞌyamo ataleꞌnane.
\v 50 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, aliꞌyakamo neꞌaliya vayakaeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa neꞌapataya kavafeꞌmo kage okanika kagesamo afiyo. Muki asole vayaꞌmogimo huꞌa faipa huꞌa nelatageꞌnaeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo lusi kava huno kana nehiye.
\v 51 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kame vayakamogi huꞌa faipa huꞌa lateꞌnae. Apakaemo uvelimo faleka ateꞌnana vekamoꞌa nehiya kavafeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa ateꞌnae.
\p 
\v 52 Ala kava neꞌmo alagepa huno maino. He, Lama ge. Lama ge.
\c 90
\s1 Moseseꞌa nunumuꞌmo huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, lagaemo afole aige afole aige huta neꞌmaunagekaeꞌmo kagaemo muki afinaꞌmo notigana huka maiꞌnane.
\v 2 Akeyaꞌvilaga aveꞌe ma mopaꞌeꞌmo alo osuꞌnana afinaꞌmo hogoteka maiꞌnananageka maige maige huka alagi maigane.
\p 
\v 3 Kagaemo vayaꞌaifeꞌmo, halate mopamo alita hamaleyo, huka huteka nefaligekaeꞌmo mopamo alika hamaleka neꞌapatane.
\v 4 Vani tauseniꞌa kafugamo magoke afinakana huno haneꞌniye, huka kagesamo afiꞌnane. Egamo malage huno hano huꞌniya kava huno vani tauseniꞌa kafugamo malage huno hano nehiye. Magoke haniꞌilagamo malage huno hano huꞌniya kava huno kaulagaleꞌmo vani tauseniꞌa kafugamo malage huno hano nehiye.
\v 5-6 Aniꞌmo heteno alinino neꞌviya kava huka lavalelika uka nelatanageta nefalune. Alagamunamo ageꞌnageno malage huno apake nekaniya kava huta malage huta nefalune. Kahaumoꞌmo netepiꞌmo lagiteno ause hetenoꞌaeꞌmo uneꞌamo ago falu neteya kava huta maiꞌneta nefalune.
\v 7 Kaipamo leka latetekaeꞌmo nelamagine. Kayamukiki nehanagetaeꞌmo atete nehune.
\v 8 Hosu kavatimo afole yateꞌmo haneꞌnigeka neꞌagane. Huta fala kita neꞌatalona hosu kavatimo kaulagalekeꞌmo haneꞌnigeka alika neꞌmalane.
\v 9 Kaipamo leꞌnigeka ge nehukaeꞌmo ma mopafiꞌmo maisuna afinatimo alika hogo huka nelatane. Kaiteneꞌmo huꞌa hapa nepaigenoꞌaeꞌmo malage huno apake nekaniya kava huta malage huta nefalune.
\v 10 Lagaemo 70ꞌa kafugamo maige lokiya vayaꞌmo 80ꞌa kafugamo maige huta neꞌmaunaꞌmonanafa lokiya aliꞌyaꞌmo alige hanageke yaꞌmo alige huta aise afinaꞌmo maiꞌneta ma mopamo malage huta ataleta halelita neꞌune.
\v 11 Ina laꞌmo kaipamo leꞌniya lokiyakamo ageno alagepa huno ageꞌniye. Kaipamo nelegeka kayamukiki nehanageꞌapaeꞌmo lusi kava huꞌa koli nehaya kavakamo ina laꞌmo ageno alagepa huno ageꞌniye.
\p 
\v 12 Ma mopafiꞌmo maisuna afinatimo lekana paisunafeꞌmo alika laya malegeta alagepa huta ageteta afino.
\v 13 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, aika atagi neka lagaetegamo eno. Na magi afinaꞌmo kaipamo leka lategane. Aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluna vayakaeꞌmo kahau huka lato.
\v 14 Muki afinaꞌmo lamogaga aige amuse huge huta maisunafeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo neteꞌae neteꞌaeꞌmo olataleka kahau huka lato.
\v 15 Hanageke yaꞌmo lamiꞌnanageno laipamoꞌmo kana huꞌniye. Laha maegeta na magi afinaꞌmo laipamoꞌmo kana huꞌnifi huta ani agufa yatala afinakeꞌmo lamogaga aino.
\v 16 Aliꞌyakamo alika aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluna vayakamo lave liyo. Laginago mafaꞌnetimo himamukamo alika apave liyo.
\v 17 Ala kava neꞌmo Gotitimogae, huꞌna, amuse huka lateteka laha maegenoꞌao aliꞌyatimoꞌmo alagepa huno afole aino.
\c 91
\s1 Ala neꞌapimo fala kino maiꞌniyategamo haino neꞌmaiya vekaeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Hogote Ala neꞌapimo fala kino maiꞌniyategamo haino neꞌmaiya vekamoꞌa lokiyaꞌage vekamo aunefiꞌmo fala kino maige maige huno maigiye.
\v 2 Nagaemo Ala kava nefeꞌmo huꞌnaeꞌmo, agaepiꞌmo fala kiꞌna maiꞌnogeno faino ku aino yagaino nateꞌneno naha maeno nagufamo alino katino nateꞌniya vekaꞌnimo maiꞌniye. Gotiꞌnimoꞌmo maiꞌniyanageno, naha maegaiye, huꞌna huguve.
\p 
\v 3 Agaemo oꞌageꞌnana nofitetiꞌmo aneꞌaimo hanagiꞌa aeꞌa katafaugefeꞌmo hisaya nofiꞌmoꞌa okatafausiyafeꞌmo hatu maeno kateteno lusi kaitaꞌmo kahausigekaeꞌmo ofalisanafeꞌmo alagepa huno yagaino kategaiye.
\v 4 Agaemo hakumo alino atalelineno hakufiꞌmo alino fala kino katesigeka alagepa huka hakufiꞌmo fala kika maigane. Lama geꞌamoꞌmo kagae halegukana huno haneꞌneno yagaino katesigeka maigane.
\v 5 Apakaemo hanipifeꞌmo koli hisaya yafeꞌmo kagaemo koli osugane. Kevemoꞌmo malage huno eno haniꞌniya kava huno yegemo neleya afinaꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmoꞌa malage huno kahaesiya kavafeꞌmo koli osugane.
\v 6 Haniꞌilagamo lusi kaitaꞌmo kahausigekaeꞌmo koli osugane. Felugamo alopa hanageke yaꞌmo kagaeteꞌmo afole aisiya kavafeꞌmo koli osugane.
\p 
\v 7 Kahaopaleꞌmo vani tauseniꞌa vayaꞌmo falige lamaga kahaopaleꞌmo teni tauseniꞌa vayaꞌmo falige huꞌa falisagenoꞌaeꞌmo falisana kavaꞌmo kahaopaleꞌmo afole oꞌaigiye.
\v 8 Kahaopaleꞌmo afole oꞌaigiyaꞌmonanafa kaulagafatikeꞌmo hosu vayaꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo anonaꞌapilefeꞌmo hosu yaꞌmo alisageka apakegane.
\p 
\v 9-10 Kagaemo uꞌna fala kiꞌnova vekafifeꞌmo, agaepiꞌmo maige maige huꞌna maiguve, huka huꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo mago hosu yaꞌmoꞌa okahaesigeno hosu kaitaꞌmo nokaleꞌmo afole oꞌaigiye.
\v 11 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa enisole vayaꞌaeꞌmo, yagaitapa ateyo, huno hapa paisigeꞌa muki afinaꞌmo kategamo umenitata hisana afinaꞌmo yagaiꞌa kategayaꞌmofeꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo kagaeteꞌmo alagi afole oꞌaigiye.
\v 12 Apayatetiꞌmo kavaleꞌa kasagausageno yafaꞌmoꞌa kaiyafiꞌmo okahaegaiye.
\v 13 Kaiyaletiꞌmo laiyoniꞌe nagaloꞌyaveꞌeꞌmo aeka latapaigane.
\p 
\v 14 Gotiꞌa, nagaefeꞌmo hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agufamo aliꞌna katiꞌna ategauve, huno huꞌniye. Nagiꞌnimo afino alagepa huꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna ategauve.
\v 15 Nagaefeꞌmo keya aeno ge hisigeꞌnaeꞌmo afiguve. Hanageke yaꞌmo neꞌalisigeꞌnaeꞌmo agaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌna maiguve. Agufamo aliꞌna katiꞌna ateteꞌna ala agiꞌamo amiguve.
\v 16 Yatala kafugamo maisiya yaꞌmo amisugenoꞌaeꞌmo, haine, huno huteno hao ke hegaiye. Agufamo aliꞌna katiꞌna ateꞌnova kavaꞌnimo aepaꞌamo aliꞌna ave liguve, huno huꞌniye.
\c 93
\s1 Ala kini vekamoꞌa neꞌyagaiya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmo kini vekamo maiꞌneno yagaino neꞌapate. Agaemo ala agiꞌaꞌe ha le konali yaꞌaꞌeꞌmo alino vaino aliꞌniye. Lokiyaꞌamo alino kukenagana huno vaino aliꞌniye. Agaemo ma mopamo alino lokiya vaino ateꞌniyanageno kanage kanage osugiye.
\v 2 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Kagaemo akeyaꞌvilagatiꞌmo maime maime neꞌane. Muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo kini vekamo maiꞌnane.
\v 3 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, aniꞌmoꞌa aino holakau holakau nehiye. Aniꞌmoꞌa haiteno lamiteno nehigenoꞌaeꞌmo alopa agemo neꞌaiye.
\v 4 Ala kava neꞌmo lokiyaꞌamoꞌmo aniꞌmoꞌa aino holakau holakau nehigenoꞌaeꞌmo alopa agemo neꞌaiya aniꞌmo lokiyaꞌamo ago aeno agaseꞌniye.
\p 
\v 5 Kavayafatiꞌmo lokiya gemo huꞌnana gemo haneꞌniyanageno alagi hanege hanege huno afaꞌa hanegaiye. O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Nokamo konali yaꞌamo hanege hanege huno hanesiya kava huꞌa vayakamogi alagepa apaote kavaꞌapimo haneꞌniye.
\c 95
\s1 Gotifekeꞌmo mono higetao, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Egetao Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga huta agaefeꞌmo mono yokemo hugune. Lokiya vekatimo yafakana huno maiꞌneno lagufamo alino katino nelateya vekaekeꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo huteta lamogagamo aigune.
\v 2 Agaetegamo egetao agaefekeꞌmo hao ke hegaune. Agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga huta lamogagamo aiteta samu yokemo hugune.
\v 3 Ala kava neꞌmo ala Gotiꞌapimoꞌmo maiꞌniye. Ala kini vekamo maiꞌneno muki aigofe gotiꞌapimogimo alagi aeno apakaseno yagaino neꞌapateyaꞌmofeꞌmo mono yokemo higetao.
\v 4 Kagoꞌmufilagamo yagaige aveleꞌmo yagaige huno neꞌyagaiye.
\v 5 Solovala aniꞌe mopaꞌeꞌmo alo huꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaiꞌa yaꞌmo haneꞌniye.
\v 6 Etapa ape higetao Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alo huno lateꞌniya vekaeꞌmo laleꞌya faiꞌneta mono huta maigune.
\v 7 Gotitimoꞌmo maiꞌneno yagaino nelateya vayaꞌmo sipisipi vayaꞌamo agaiꞌa kegiꞌyafiꞌmo haita maiꞌnonaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo mono higetao.
\p Hemenimo lapakaemo Goti geꞌamo neꞌafisayana
\v 8 lapaipamo alita lokiya vaitapa oꞌateyo. Lapakinago vayaꞌmogimo kaꞌme kotegamo nata neꞌa neꞌuꞌapaeꞌmo namalageka huꞌnae. Geꞌnimo ago amagiꞌa ataleꞌnaya kava hutapa geꞌnimo amagitapa oꞌataleyo.
\v 9 Nagaemo lusi alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌna fotiꞌa kafugamo hapa maeꞌnogeꞌa alagepa kavaꞌnimo ago ageꞌnayaꞌmonanafa hosu kavakeꞌmo nehuꞌapaeꞌmo, na agufa kavaꞌmo husifi, huteꞌa namalageka huꞌnae.
\v 10 Huꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo ani afinaꞌmo muki maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo naipamo kana huꞌnaeꞌmo, muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hosu apaipa apakesageꞌmo afiteꞌapaeꞌmo neꞌnatalae. Geꞌnimo alagi alagepa huꞌa noꞌafiye.
\v 11 Naipamo leꞌnigeꞌnaeꞌmo nagoꞌya ataleteꞌna lokiya gefatiꞌmo huꞌnaeꞌmo, nagaeꞌeꞌmo haiꞌeꞌa maiꞌa falu hisaya koteꞌmo alagi haiꞌa oꞌmaigae, huꞌna huꞌnove.
\c 96
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alino asaga huno ateꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nefeꞌmo saufa yokemo hiyo. Muki ma mopafi vayaꞌmogimo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo yokemo hiyo.
\v 2 Ala kava nefeꞌmo yokemo hutetapa agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Lagufamo alino katino lateꞌniye, hutapa muki afinaꞌae afinaꞌaeꞌmo aeta hakalo hutapa hapa paiyo.
\v 3 Ala agiꞌamo amitetapaeꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌmo aliꞌniya kavaꞌaenagi lokiya kavaꞌmo huꞌniya kavaꞌaenagi huta muki vayaꞌaifeꞌmo ava gemo hutapa hapa paiyo.
\v 4 Ala kava neꞌmo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo magoꞌe hutapa agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Aigofe gotiꞌapimogimo alagi aeno apakaseꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo magoꞌe hutapa koli nehutapa mono hiyo.
\v 5 Muki alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌai gotiꞌapimogimo aigofe gotigi maiꞌnayaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa kokuꞌnaꞌmo alo huꞌniye.
\v 6 Ha le konali yaꞌamo haneꞌnigeno kini vekamo maiꞌniye. Lokiya vekamo maiꞌnigeꞌa hapaꞌye huꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo neꞌagaya vekamo maiꞌniye.
\v 7 Muki ma mopafi vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hutetapa ha le konali yaꞌaleꞌe lokiyaꞌaleꞌefeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo.
\v 8 Ala agiꞌamo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hutetapa ofalinimo alinita agaetegamo eyo.
\v 9 Aote kavaꞌmo nehutapaekeꞌmo Ala kava nefeꞌmo mono hiyo. Muki ma mopafi vayaꞌmogitapamo agaefekeꞌmo atete hutapa maiyo.
\v 10 Muki alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌaifeꞌmo, Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa yagaino neꞌmaiye, hutapa hapa paiyo. Mopamo alino lokiya vaino ateteno maleꞌniyanageno afaꞌa hanegaiye. Agaemo fatago kavaꞌmo nehunoꞌaeꞌmo muki vayaꞌmo alino fako huno apategaiye.
\v 11 Kokuꞌnaꞌmogamo kamogaga aigenoꞌao mopamoꞌeꞌmo amogaga aino. Solovala aniꞌmogaꞌe solovala anipiꞌmo maiꞌnaya yaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo huteꞌa apamogaga aiyo.
\v 12 Hoyamogaꞌe hoyafiꞌmo haneꞌnaya neꞌyaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo lapamogaga aiyo. Yahaofilaga yosamoꞌa alopa gefatiꞌmo huteno amogaga aigiye.
\v 13 Ala kava neꞌmo muki ma mopafi vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino apatesiyafeꞌmo eminegaiye. Agaemo alagi alagepa fatago kavaꞌmo huno muki ma mopafi vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino apategaiye.
\c 100
\s1 Hao ke hetetapa ala agiꞌamo amiyo, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ma mopafi muki haopalega maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogitapamo lapamogaga aitetapa Ala kava nefekeꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo hiyo.
\v 2 Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌalefeꞌmo mono nehutapaeꞌmo lapamogaga lapamagaga aitapa maiyo. Yokemo nehutapaeꞌmo agaemo maiꞌniya yategamo etapa maiyo.
\v 3 Agetapa aeto hutetapaeꞌmo Ala kava nefeꞌmo, Gotiꞌmae, hutapa hiyo. Lagaemo lagaitimo alo osuꞌnopa agaiꞌamo alo huno lateꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo lagaemo agaiꞌa vayaꞌmo maiꞌnone. Lagaemo vayaꞌamo maiꞌneta sipisipiꞌamo agae kegiꞌyafiꞌmo haita maiꞌnonagenoꞌaeꞌmo yagaino nelate.
\p 
\v 4 Kahao ke nehone, hutapa hume hume neꞌutapaeꞌmo mono noꞌamo yafa lafi kegiꞌya kate kipaꞌapifiꞌmo faletapa haiyo. Mono no kumaꞌaleꞌmo neꞌutapaeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hume hume viyo. Hao ke hetetapa ala agiꞌamo amiyo.
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmo alagepa vekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmae. Agaemo lagaefeꞌmo hau ayamopafiꞌmo haume haume neꞌviya kavaꞌamoꞌmo hauno hano osuno muki afinaꞌmo nehaiye. Lama gemo hunoꞌaeꞌmo, lapa maeꞌna lapamiguve, huno huꞌniya geꞌamo alagi oꞌataleno akame huno muki hemenimo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaitegaꞌe aliꞌa apateme apateme visaya vayaꞌaitegaꞌeꞌmo ani agufa kavaꞌmo afaꞌa hugiye.
\c 101
\s1 Neviniꞌa ina kava huguve, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Nagaemo kahau huka neꞌatana kavakaꞌe alagepa huka alika fako huka neꞌatana kavakaleꞌefeꞌmo yoke huguve. Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kagaefekeꞌmo yoke huguve.
\v 2 Ageꞌna aeto huteꞌnaeꞌmo afiteꞌna vaiꞌmo alagi oꞌalisuva kateꞌmo uguve. Hainu afinaꞌmo nagaetegamo egane. Nagaemo noꞌnifiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌnimo neꞌaliya vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaiꞌna apateꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo vaiꞌmo alagi oꞌalisuvana alagepa kavaꞌageꞌmo huꞌna maiguve.
\v 3 Nagaemo hosu kavaꞌmo hisuvafeꞌmo nagesamo oꞌafiguve. Alagepa kaꞌmo ataleꞌa neꞌvaya vayaꞌai kavaꞌapieꞌmo alagi oꞌnahauꞌniyanageno ani agufa hosu kavaꞌapimoꞌa nagaeteꞌmo aino okamaegaiye.
\v 4 Aigofe kavaꞌmo osuꞌna hosu apaipa vayaꞌmo hapafaiꞌna apatalegauve.
\v 5 Huꞌa faipa huꞌa neꞌataya vayaꞌmo hapafaiꞌna apatalegauve. Ala vayaꞌmo maiꞌnone, huꞌa huteꞌa himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo nagaeꞌeꞌmo oꞌmaigae.
\v 6 Nagaemo Goti geꞌamo oꞌataleꞌa akame nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo amuse huꞌna apatesugeꞌa nagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌa maigae. Aigofe gemo nosaya vayaꞌamogigeꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌnimo aligae.
\v 7 Aeꞌa ati nekaya vayaꞌmo noꞌnifiꞌmo haiꞌa oꞌmaigae. Aigofe gemo nehaya vayaꞌmo nagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌa oꞌmaigae.
\v 8 Malage huꞌna he tiꞌna hosu vayaꞌmo aliꞌna hano huꞌna apataleteꞌna hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo taonifatiꞌmo aliꞌna hapa faiꞌna apatalegauve.
\c 103
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hau huno lateꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Nagupi mafaꞌneo, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alika asaga huvo. Muki nagufamoꞌe naipa nagesamoꞌeꞌmo aote neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alino asaga hino.
\v 2 Nagupi mafaꞌneo, huꞌna, alagepa huno naha maeꞌniya kavafeꞌmo kage okanika agiꞌaleꞌmo alika asaga huvo.
\v 3 Agaemo muki hosu kavaꞌnimo alino ataleteno muki kaitaꞌnimo alino nahageno neꞌnate.
\v 4 Falisuva kavapatiꞌmo miya faino hatu maeno neꞌnate. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa ala nagiꞌnimo namitenoꞌaeꞌmo nagaefeꞌmo hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo hau huno neꞌnate.
\v 5 Alagepa yaꞌmo alino neꞌnamigenoꞌaeꞌmo magoꞌe yafeꞌmo naipafatiꞌmo ohauꞌniye. Naha neꞌmaegeꞌnaeꞌmo hakiki namamo neya vekagana huno maiꞌniya kava huꞌna neꞌmauve.
\v 6 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa aliꞌa afepi apatageꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmo hapa maeteno apakaiꞌapi yaꞌmo alisayafeꞌmo alino apamigiye.
\v 7 Agaemo aipafiꞌmo agesa afige hauge nehiya kavaꞌamo Moseseꞌmo alino ave lige Isaleli vayaꞌmo huꞌniya kavaꞌamo alino apave lige huꞌniye.
\v 8 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hau huno apatege fiku hapa maeno apamige vase vase huno aipamo leno apatege lusi kava huno hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauge huno neꞌmaiye.
\v 9 Halate magoꞌe huno olahaugiyaꞌmonanafa muki afinaꞌmo aipamo leno olategaiye.
\v 10 Hosu kavatimo anonatilefeꞌmo magoke aiyaya huno nolamiye. Hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnona kavatilefeꞌmo magoke aiyaya huno nolamagiye.
\p 
\v 11 Kokuꞌnaꞌmo muga anagamo haneꞌniya kava huno agaefekeꞌmo koli huteꞌa mono nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo magoke aiyaya kava huno hau huno neꞌapate.
\v 12 Yegemo haine neꞌeya aupilagaꞌe yegemo lamino nefaleya aupilagaꞌeꞌmo lusi afagiꞌaleꞌmo haneꞌniya kava huno Gotiꞌa hosu kavatimo magoke aiyaya kava huno alino afagiꞌaleꞌmo yaga auno neꞌatale.
\v 13 Afoꞌapimogi mafaꞌne anagaꞌapieꞌmo hapau huꞌa neꞌataya kava huno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa agaefeꞌmo koli huteꞌa mono nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo hau huno neꞌate.
\v 14 Agaemo, mopaletiꞌmo alo huꞌna apateꞌnove. Mumusopaletiꞌmo alo huꞌnova vayaꞌageꞌmo maiꞌnae, huno agesamo neꞌafiyaꞌmofeꞌmo lagaetegamo vase vase huno aliꞌyaꞌmo neꞌaliye.
\v 15-16 Kahaumoꞌmo aise afinaꞌmo nehaneya kava huta ma mopafiꞌmo aise afinaꞌmo maigeta nefalune. Kahau ausemo heꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo malage huno yasimo neꞌaligenoꞌaeꞌmo falu teteno hali huno mopafiꞌmo asagauno neꞌaiya kava huta aise afinaꞌmo maigeta ago nefalune.
\v 17-18 Nefalunaꞌmonanafa Ala kava nefeꞌmo koli huteꞌa mono nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo ema akeyaꞌvilagatiꞌmo hau huno apateme apateme eno henagaꞌamo afole aisiya afinaꞌeꞌmo hau huno apateme apateme uno hano osugiye. Agaemo laha neꞌmaeya kava huno alita apateꞌnonanageꞌa henagaꞌamo aliꞌa apateme apateme visaya mafaꞌnemogimo kotalake geꞌamo akame huꞌa ma kavaꞌmo hiyo, huno huꞌniya gemo neꞌafiya vayaꞌmo hapa neꞌmae.
\p 
\v 19 Ala kava neꞌmo kokuꞌnapiꞌmo maiꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo yagaino neꞌate. Muki asole vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino neꞌate.
\v 20 Enisole vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, lokiya vayaꞌmo maiꞌnetapa geꞌamo afitetapa akame nehaya vayaꞌmogitapae, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo.
\p 
\v 21 Muki kokuꞌnapi maiꞌnetapa aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vayaꞌamogitapamo hauꞌniya kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo.
\v 22 Muki alo huno lapateteno muki neꞌyagaiya kotegamo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Nagupi mafaꞌneo, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alika asaga huvo.
\c 104
\s1 Gotiꞌa muki yaꞌamo alo huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 O, Nauneꞌnameyo, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alika asaga huka ato. Ala kava neo, O Gotiꞌnimogae, huꞌna, ala kagi vekamo maiꞌnane. Ala kagikaꞌe alopa konali yakaꞌeꞌmo kukenagana huka alika vaiteka neꞌmaine.
\v 2 Ha le yakamo kukenakagana huka alika vaiteka neꞌmaine. Kokuꞌnaꞌmo seli nokana huka alika atale maleꞌnane.
\v 3 Anagamo hiyapi aniteꞌmo nokamo akalo huka ki maleꞌnane. Hiyaꞌmo kalekagana huno haneꞌnigeno yasimoꞌmo kavalelino neꞌviye.
\v 4 Agaemo enisole vayaꞌamo yasigana huno alo huno apateꞌniye. Aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vayaꞌmo ata vaikana huno alo huno apateꞌniye.
\p 
\v 5 Kagaemo ma mopamo muki afinaꞌmo hanege hanege huno hanesiyafeꞌmo faika ateꞌnane.
\v 6 Solovala aniꞌmo alika ateꞌnanageno eno ma mopamo aeno ati kaeteno avemo alino agaseꞌniye.
\v 7-8 Solovala anifeꞌmo, kaune ho, huka huꞌnanageno aune heno uꞌniye. Hakalu huꞌnanageno afitenoꞌaeꞌmo nagu nagu huno lamiꞌniye. Aveletiꞌmo aino laki lamino aune hetaleno lamino ani yamufiꞌmo asagauno aiteno ateꞌnana noꞌaleꞌmo halate haneꞌniye.
\v 9 Kegiꞌyamo huka ku aika ateꞌnananageno halate eno ma mopamo aeno ati okaegaiye.
\p 
\v 10 Meti aniꞌmo alino ateꞌnigeno ani yamufiꞌmo nelamiye.
\v 11 Nelamigeꞌapaeꞌmo muki afela afumogimo neꞌnae. Afela nokimogimo neꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo apainagamo hau nosiye.
\v 12 Ani agiꞌnaleꞌmo haneꞌniya yosafiꞌmo nama anagaꞌmogi apanoꞌmo ki maleteꞌa yosa akopaleꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa apake neꞌaiye.
\p 
\v 13 Anagamo akalo huka ki maleꞌnana nopatiꞌmo aniꞌmo alika aveleꞌmo lakiꞌnanagenoꞌaeꞌmo koꞌmo neꞌaigenoꞌaeꞌmo muki ma mopafi yaꞌmo nehage.
\v 14 Muki pulumakamogi kahaumo nesayafeꞌmo alika hageka ateteka vayaꞌmogi hoyafiꞌmo hakalesaya neꞌyateꞌmo yagaiꞌneꞌa aliꞌa nesayafeꞌmo alika hageka neꞌatane.
\v 15 Ani kava huka ma mopafi vayaꞌmogimo apamogaga aisayafeꞌmo nofi alagafati aniꞌmo alika apamige apaugosafiꞌmo uvelimo falesageno fayu fayu hisigeꞌa amuse hisayafeꞌmo uvelimo alika apamige apaipamo alino lokiya vaino apatesiyafeꞌmo peleti mayamo alika apamige huka alika neꞌamine.
\v 16 Koꞌmo neꞌaigenoꞌaeꞌmo Lemanonigayagamo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fai maleꞌniya yosamoꞌmo lusi kava huno aniꞌmo neꞌaliye.
\v 17 Ani yosaleꞌmo muki nama anagaꞌmogimo apanoꞌmo nekiye. Mago alopa namamogimo mago yosaleꞌmo apanoꞌmo nekiye.
\v 18 Afela meme anagaꞌmogimo yatala aveleꞌmo umenitata nehageꞌapaeꞌmo mago afela afu anagaꞌmo yafa kapiꞌmo uꞌa fala nekiye.
\p 
\v 19 Kagaemo kaimo alo hu maleꞌnanageno muki afinaꞌmo kaimo eno neꞌateya kavafeꞌmo lekana nepaiye. Yegemo lamino nefaleya afinaꞌmo agetageno lamino nefale.
\v 20 Kagaemo hani huvo, huka nehanageno haniꞌmo nehigeꞌapaeꞌmo muki yagagafamo fala kiꞌa maiꞌnayategatiꞌmo eꞌa umenitata nehae.
\v 21 Afela laiyoni anaꞌaumogi Gotitegatiꞌmo neꞌyaꞌmo aliꞌa nesayafeꞌmo kahauya huꞌa kae kae nehae.
\v 22 Yegemo nelegeꞌapaeꞌmo kelifiꞌmo lamiꞌa havaeꞌa neꞌmaiye.
\v 23 Fala kiꞌa neꞌmaigeꞌapaeꞌmo vayaꞌmo he tiꞌa uꞌa aliꞌyaꞌapimo neꞌaligenoꞌaeꞌmo yegemo lamino nefale.
\p 
\v 24 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, asole kavaꞌmo nehane. Ageteka afiꞌnana kavakaletiꞌmo muki ma mopafi yaꞌe vayaꞌeꞌmo alo hu maleꞌnanageꞌapaeꞌmo ma mopafiꞌmo kili paeꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 25 Solovala aniꞌmo muga afagiꞌaleꞌmo haneꞌnigeno lusi yatala aniꞌmo vasilonafiꞌmo muki apauneꞌapameꞌe yaꞌmo maiꞌnae.
\v 26 Muga alopa anipiꞌmo asole sipimo neꞌvageꞌapaeꞌmo alopa noyamemogi nagosaꞌmo ailiꞌa uꞌeꞌa huꞌa yokalomo neleꞌaeꞌmo aeꞌa hailo huꞌa haiteꞌa emi eteꞌa nehae.
\p 
\v 27 Mukiꞌamogimo neꞌyaꞌmo alika apamisanafeꞌmo apaka netegeꞌa kagava neꞌmaiye.
\v 28 Neꞌyaꞌmo alika neꞌapaminageꞌaphaeꞌmo neꞌnae. Kayapatiꞌmo aliꞌa neꞌa apamu neae.
\v 29 Kakameꞌyamo neꞌapaminageꞌapaeꞌmo kolikamo nehae. Apavamusateꞌmo neꞌalinageꞌapaeꞌmo faliteꞌa halate mopamo aliꞌa nehamalae.
\v 30 Kaunekameꞌmo alika ateꞌnanageno uno alino afole aino neꞌapate. Muki haopalegamo saufa yaꞌe vayaꞌeꞌmo alo huteka alika afole aika neꞌapatane.
\p 
\v 31 Ala kava neꞌmo ha le konali yaꞌamoꞌmo alagi hanege hanege huno haneno. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alo huꞌniya yatefeꞌmo amogaga aino.
\v 32 Agaemo mopaleꞌmo aulu heno neꞌagegenoꞌaeꞌmo imima neꞌaliye. Aveleꞌmo ame neꞌaligenoꞌaeꞌmo halinamo neꞌaiye.
\v 33 Nagaemo ofaliꞌna muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna yoke huguve.
\v 34 Ala kava nefeꞌmo namogaga neꞌauvaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna neꞌmauvanageno amuse huno natesiyafeꞌmo nahauꞌniye.
\v 35 Agaemo hosu vayaꞌmo ma mopafatiꞌmo alagi alino hano huno apatalesiyafeꞌmo nahauꞌniye.
\p O nauneꞌnameyo, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alika asaga huka ato. Ala agiꞌamo amiyo.
\c 105
\s1 Gotiꞌa Isaleli vayaꞌaiteꞌmo alagepa huno yagaino apateꞌniya kavafeꞌmae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo hao ke heyo. Agaefekeꞌmo ge hiyo. Huꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ava gemo afisayafeꞌmo muki alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌaifeꞌmo aeta hakalo hutapa hapa paiyo.
\v 2 Agaefekeꞌmo yoke huge samu yokemo huge hiyo. Lapau neꞌaiya kavaꞌae kavaꞌaeꞌmo ava gemo hiyo.
\v 3 Aote agiꞌalefeꞌmo ala lapakitapimo alitetapa lapamogaga aiyo. Ala kava nefeꞌmo kahauya nehaya vayaꞌmogimo apamogaga aiyo.
\v 4 Ala kava netegamo utapa himamuꞌamo alisayafeꞌmo kahauya hutapa maiyo. Augosamo agesayafeꞌmo kahauya hiyo.
\v 5-6 Emalehamuꞌa Ala kava neꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vekaꞌamo aginago vayaꞌamogitapae, huꞌna, Yekopuꞌa lekana paino ateꞌniya vekamo aginago vayaꞌamogitapae, huꞌna, lokiya kavaꞌaꞌe aune kavaꞌaꞌefeꞌmo lapakesamo afiyo. Alino fako huno apateteno ani kavaꞌmo hiyo, huno huꞌniya geꞌaeꞌmo lapakesamo afiyo.
\p 
\v 7 Agaemo Ala kava netimo Gotitimoꞌae. Agaemo muki ma mopafi vayaꞌmo alino fako huno apateteno ani kavaꞌmo hiyo, huno nehiye.
\v 8 Agaemo muki afinaꞌmo agaiꞌa kotalake geꞌaeꞌmo agesamo afiteno oꞌataleno akame huno neꞌmaiye. Vayaꞌmo afole aite afole aite hume hume neꞌvisagenoꞌaeꞌmo afole aino, huno huꞌniya geeꞌmo age okanino agesamo afino maiꞌniye.
\v 9-10 Agaemo Emalehamuꞌeꞌmo kotalake gemo hu maleteno Emalehamu mafaꞌneꞌamo Aisikifeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo huguve, huno hu maleteno Aisiki mafaꞌneꞌamo Yekopufeꞌmo hanege hanege huno hanesiya kotalake geꞌamo hu maleꞌniye.
\v 11 Kenani mopamo aliꞌna hakiꞌna lapamisugeno lapakaitapi mopatapimo hanegaiye, huno ha paiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 12-13 Aise vayaꞌamogi ina agufa nata vayaꞌmo maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo uꞌa mago nofi vayaꞌai mopaleꞌmo maigeꞌa atale uꞌa mago alu nofi vayaꞌai mopaleꞌmo maigeꞌa atale uꞌa ani kava huꞌa mago kini vekamoꞌa yagaiꞌniya mopaleꞌmo uꞌa maigeꞌa atale uꞌa mago alu kini vekamoꞌa yagaiꞌniya mopaleꞌmo maige maige huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 14 Ani kava huꞌa maiꞌnayaꞌmonanafa Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa agaiꞌa vayaꞌaiteꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌa yagaiꞌa oꞌatesayafeꞌmo oꞌataleno yagaino apateꞌniye.
\v 15 Inagi yagaiꞌa neꞌapataya kini vayaꞌaifeꞌmo, uvelimo faleꞌna apateꞌnova vayaꞌmo apame oꞌaliyo. Nagaetegati gemo alini eꞌa aeꞌa hakalo huꞌa hapa nepaiya vayaꞌmo maitapa halove hutapa apatetetapa hanageke yaꞌmo alitapa oꞌapamiyo, huno ke hapauꞌniye.
\p 
\v 16-17 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa, kafu hisaya kavaꞌmo aliꞌna afole aiꞌna ategauve, huno agesamo afiteno hogoteno vayaꞌamo hapa maesiya vekamo Yosefeꞌmo alino ateꞌnigeno uꞌniye. Yosefe nepuꞌamogimo avaleꞌa alu nofi vayaꞌmo apamiꞌnageꞌa kalavusi aliꞌyaꞌmo alisiya mafaꞌnemo maisiyafeꞌmo miya faiꞌa avaleliꞌa uꞌnae.
\v 18 Isipi kotegamo uno maiꞌnigeꞌa kalavusi huꞌa ateteꞌapaeꞌmo aiyalateꞌmo seli nofitetiꞌmo kiꞌa ateꞌnageno lusi kava huno kana hauꞌniye.
\v 19 Ani kava huno maiꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa amalageka huno ateme ateme neꞌvigenoꞌaeꞌmo afole aigiye, huno huꞌniya kavaꞌmo afole aiꞌniye.
\v 20 Hogote kini vekamoꞌa aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vekaeꞌmo, hatu maeka ato, huteno alino ateꞌnigeno uno Yosefeꞌmo hatu maeno ateꞌniye.
\v 21-22 Hatu maeno atetenoꞌaeꞌmo, muki Isipi mopaleꞌe vayaꞌaiteꞌeꞌmo yagaika apato, huno ha paiꞌnigeno Yosefeꞌa hogote gamani vayaꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa yagaiꞌa neꞌataya vayaꞌaiteꞌeꞌmo yagaino apateteno vayatama vayaꞌmo alino apaya maleꞌniye.
\p 
\v 23 Ani kava huno yagaino apateꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo Isaleli vayaꞌmo Isipi kotegamo eꞌnae. Yekopuꞌe muki afamo anaga vayaꞌaꞌeꞌmo eꞌa Hamu aginago vayaꞌai mopaleꞌmo Isipi kotegamo maiꞌnae.
\v 24 Maiꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa vayaꞌamo hapa maeꞌnigeꞌa asole mafaꞌnemo aliꞌa apateꞌnageꞌa aiꞌa atagu faeꞌa maiteꞌa lokiya vayaꞌmo hamaleteꞌa kame vayaꞌapimo aeꞌa apakaseꞌnae.
\v 25 Agaemo Isipi vayaꞌai apaipa apakesamo alino afe leno apateꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo agaiꞌa vayaꞌaitegamo apaini huꞌa apateteꞌa aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo humi apateꞌnae.
\v 26 Agaemo aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vekaꞌamo Moseseꞌe lekana paino ateꞌniya vekamo Eloniꞌeꞌmo alino anateꞌnigeꞌana kini vekalegamo uꞌnaꞌae.
\v 27 Anakaemo Goti lokiya kavaꞌamo noꞌagaya agufa aune kavaꞌmo Isipi kotegamo huꞌnaꞌae.
\v 28 Agaemo hani hisiya kavaꞌmo alino ateꞌnigeno emineno hani huꞌniye. Isaleli vayaꞌmogi geꞌamo oꞌataleꞌa afiꞌnae.
\v 29 Agaemo aniꞌmo kola aniꞌmo alino hamaleno ateꞌnigeꞌa noyame anagaꞌmo faliꞌa hano huꞌnae.
\v 30 Lokuloku anagaꞌmo aiꞌa atagu faeꞌa muki ani mopaleꞌmo maiꞌneꞌaeꞌmo kini vayaꞌmo nehavaya noꞌapifiꞌmo haiꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 31 Ge huꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo asole kosi anaganagi apayokapi nama anaganagi huꞌa eꞌa muki ani mopaleꞌmo aiꞌa atagu faeꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 32-33 Afa koꞌmo aiyo, huno osuꞌnifa ko mopa koꞌmo aiyo, huno huꞌnigeno muki ani koteꞌmo alino alave huteno lusi ko mopa koꞌmo aiteno nofiꞌe fiki yosaꞌeꞌmo amagiꞌniye. Hafosa haiꞌnigeno muki haopalegamo haneꞌniya yosamo amagino lo aeꞌniye.
\v 34-35 Ge huꞌnigeꞌa asole akenu anagaꞌmo neya akenuꞌage huꞌa lekana opaisuna agufa akenu anagaꞌmogimo eꞌa muki hegafatalili yaꞌe muki hoyalega haneꞌniya neꞌyaꞌapiꞌeꞌmo neꞌa hano huꞌa ataleꞌnae.
\v 36 Muki Isipi vayaꞌai yege mafaꞌneꞌapimo apamagiꞌniye.
\v 37 Apamagiteno Isaleli vayaꞌmo hatu maeno apateꞌnigeꞌa Isipi kotegamo ataleꞌa ugefeꞌmo nehuꞌapaeꞌmo Isipi vayaꞌai siluva yafaꞌapiꞌe goli yafaꞌapiꞌeꞌmo aliniꞌa uꞌnae. Muki vayaꞌamo kaita ohapauꞌnigeꞌa lokiya vaiꞌa maiꞌneꞌa uꞌnae.
\v 38 Isipi vayaꞌmogimo apakaefeꞌmo lusi kava huꞌa koli huꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo Isaleli vayaꞌmo apataleꞌa neꞌvageꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga aiꞌnae.
\v 39 Gotiꞌa muki felugaꞌamo ulunapiꞌmo uge maige hisayafeꞌmo hiyatetiꞌmo aino apati kaeteno muki haniꞌilagaꞌamo aeno ha leno apatesiyafeꞌmo kokuꞌnapatiꞌmo ata leꞌnigeno aeno ha leno apateꞌniye.
\v 40 Apakaemo Gotifeꞌmo afi geꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo hifakana agufa nama anagaꞌmo apateꞌnigeꞌa haleli uꞌa maiꞌnageꞌa apatafauꞌa kaeꞌa neꞌnae. Agaemo lusi neꞌyaꞌmo kokuꞌnapatiꞌmo alino apamiꞌnigeꞌa aliꞌa neꞌa apamu huꞌnae.
\v 41 Agaemo aniꞌmo ohaneꞌniya kotegamo yafapiꞌmo amagino apalo atiꞌnigeno yafapatiꞌmo alopa anikefamo emineꞌnigeꞌa neꞌnae.
\v 42 Agaemo aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vekaꞌamo Emalehamufeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo huguve, huno hu maleꞌniya geꞌaeꞌmo agesamo afiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo huꞌniye.
\p 
\v 43 Ani kava nehunoꞌaeꞌmo vayaꞌamo apavalelino neꞌvigeꞌapaeꞌmo lekana paino apateꞌniya vayaꞌamogimo yoke huꞌa apamogaga aiꞌnae.
\v 44 Agaemo alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌai mopamo alino apamiꞌnigeꞌa hoyaꞌapiꞌeꞌmo aliꞌnae.
\v 45 Geꞌamo afiteꞌa keꞌaepa geꞌamo akame hisayafeꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo huꞌniye. Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hutapa ateyo.
\c 106
\s1 Isaleli vayaꞌmogi hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnaya kavafeꞌmo apava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Alagepa vekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo hao ke heyo. Muki afinaꞌmo hau huno apatege apatege huno neꞌmaiye.
\v 2 Ina lagimo huꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ava gemo hugae. Alagepa kavaꞌmo lusi kanale kavaꞌmo huꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo ina lagimo ani kavaꞌmo huꞌa agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hugae.
\v 3 Geꞌamo afiteꞌa akame huꞌa muki afinaꞌmo alagepa kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\p 
\v 4 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Vayakamo hapa maesana afinaꞌmo nagaeꞌefeꞌmo kagesamo afiyo. Apakufamo alika katika apatesana afinaꞌmo nagaeꞌeꞌmo nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 5 Naha maegeꞌnao vayakamo alagepa huꞌa maisageꞌna apaketeꞌnaeꞌmo apakaegiꞌeꞌmo magokepi namogaga aiteꞌna vayakaꞌeꞌmo Goti vayaꞌamo maiꞌnone, huꞌna huteꞌna magokepi lamogaga aigune.
\v 6 Laginago vayaꞌmogimo hosu kavakeꞌmo huꞌa maiꞌnaya kava huta hosu kavakeꞌmo huta maiꞌnone.
\v 7 Laginago vayaꞌmogi Isipi kotegamo maiꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo Gotiꞌa lokiya aune kavaꞌmo huꞌniyana ageꞌa aeto osuꞌnae. Hau huno apateꞌniya kavafeꞌmo alagepa huꞌa apakesamo oꞌafiꞌnafa ago apake kaniꞌniye. Apakaemo solovala aniteꞌmo uꞌa avaꞌyi huteꞌaeꞌmo anaga hogote vekalegamo hosu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa geꞌamo ago amagiꞌa ataleꞌnae.
\v 8 Amagiꞌa ataleꞌnayaꞌmonanafa lapa maegauve, huno huꞌniya gemo akame huno himamuꞌamo alino apave lisiyafeꞌmo apakufamo alino katino apateꞌniye.
\v 9 Agaemo solovala anifeꞌmo, aika kaka vao, huno huꞌnigeno aino akaka vaeꞌnigeno aniꞌmo folagapiꞌmo hau huꞌniya mopaleꞌmo apavalelino uꞌniye.
\v 10 Agaemo kame vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo apakufamo ago alino katino apatetenoꞌaeꞌmo ani kava huno kame vayaꞌapilegatiꞌmo apavalelino eꞌnigeꞌa eꞌa afaꞌa maiꞌnae.
\p 
\v 11 Aniꞌmoꞌa kame vayaꞌapimo ago aeno apati kaeꞌnigeꞌa muki vayaꞌamo ago faliꞌnae.
\v 12 Ani kava huꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo geꞌaeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago huꞌnae.
\p 
\v 13 Huꞌnayaꞌmonanafa huꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ago apake kaniꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo agaefeꞌmo na kava hisune, huꞌa afi okeꞌneꞌa afa kavaꞌmo huꞌnae.
\v 14 Kaꞌme kotega maiꞌneꞌaeꞌmo hosu hapaꞌye huꞌnigeꞌa Gotiꞌmo amalageka huꞌa ateꞌnae.
\v 15 Agaefeꞌmo lamiyo, huꞌa ge huꞌnaya gemo afiꞌniyaꞌmonanafa kaitaꞌmo apamiꞌnigeꞌa ago faliꞌnae.
\v 16-17 Kaꞌme kotega maiꞌneꞌaeꞌmo Moseseꞌe Ala kava neꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vekamo Eloniꞌefeꞌmo, aetana laga oseꞌnaꞌaꞌmofeꞌmo yagaitana olateꞌao, huꞌa huꞌnageno mopamo aino akaka vaeꞌnigeꞌa Neteniꞌe afamo anagaꞌaꞌenagi Amilamiꞌe afamo anagaꞌaꞌenagi huꞌa asagauꞌa aiꞌnageno aino akaniteno aeno apati kaeꞌniye.
\v 18 Kokuꞌnapatiꞌmo atamo emineno hosu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa anakame huꞌnaya vayaꞌeꞌmo alagi leno apasaga liꞌniye.
\v 19 Alu afinaꞌmo apakaemo goli yafatetiꞌmo pulumakamo auneꞌamo alo huteꞌa mono huꞌnae.
\v 20 Apakaemo ani kava huꞌa ha le konali Gotiꞌmo ataleꞌa agae aimuꞌyaleꞌmo kahaumo neꞌneya pulumakamo auneꞌalefeꞌmo mono huꞌnae.
\v 21 Gotiꞌa lokiya aune kavaꞌmo Isipi kotegamo huteno apakufamo alino katino apateꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ago apake kaniꞌniye.
\v 22 Agaemo Isipi kotegamo aune kavaꞌmo huteno solovala aniteꞌeꞌmo lokiya kavaꞌmo huꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo hapau aiꞌnae.
\v 23 Henagaꞌamo Gotiꞌa aipamo leno apatetenoꞌaeꞌmo vayaꞌnimo aliꞌna apagoꞌya lagauꞌna apatalegauve, huno nehigenoꞌaeꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌamo alisiyafeꞌmo Gotiꞌa lekana paino ateꞌniya vekamo Moseseꞌa nunumu huno apatetenoꞌaeꞌmo apamagisiya kaꞌmo ago akani maleꞌnigeno Gotiꞌa afaꞌa apateꞌniye.
\v 24 Apateteno alagepa mopamo lapamiguve, huno huꞌniyana apakesamo afiꞌa fatago osuꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo ina agufa mopamo haneꞌniye, huꞌa huteꞌa alagepa mopaeꞌmo ohapauꞌniye.
\v 25 Apakaemo seli noꞌapifiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌaeꞌmo Goti geꞌamo akame osuꞌa ge nege nege huꞌageꞌmo maiꞌnae.
\v 26-27 Ani kava huꞌa maiꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo ani vayaꞌaifeꞌmo kaꞌme kotegamo lapamagiteꞌna henagaꞌamo lapakinago vayaꞌmo alagepa mopaꞌapiletiꞌmo aliꞌna hapa faitalesugeꞌa alu vayaꞌai kotegamo uꞌa falige falige huꞌa maigae, huno hapa paiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 28 Henagaꞌamo Piyo kotega aigofe gotiꞌapimo agiꞌamo Malifeꞌmo mono huteꞌa aunemeꞌamo ohaneꞌniya aigofe gotiꞌa ofalinimo amiteꞌa amiꞌnaya ofalini yaꞌmo aliꞌa neꞌnae.
\v 29 Ani kava huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa aipamo leno apateteno alopa kaitaꞌmo apamiꞌniye.
\v 30 Apamiꞌnigeno Finiyasiꞌa he tino hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnaya vayaꞌmo apamagiꞌnigeꞌa faliꞌnageno Gotiꞌa magoꞌe huno kaitaꞌmo alino oꞌapamino ataleꞌniye.
\v 31 Finiyasiꞌa ani alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo Gotiꞌa naulagaleꞌmo fatago kavaꞌmo huꞌniye, huno hu maleꞌniyanageno fatago kavaꞌamo muki afinaꞌmo hanege hanege huno hanegaiye.
\v 32-33 Apakaemo Melima kotegamo yafapatiꞌmo aniꞌmo emineꞌniya kotegamo hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo Gotiꞌa aipamo leno apateꞌniye. Hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo Moseseꞌa hosu aipamo kaliꞌnigeno agesamo oꞌafiꞌneno malage huno hosu gemo huꞌnigeno Gotiꞌa kana yaꞌmo alino amiꞌniye.
\v 34 Henagaꞌamo Gotiꞌa, alu nofi vayaꞌmo muki vayaꞌamo apamagigeꞌa faliyo, huno huꞌniya gemo oꞌafiꞌnae.
\v 35 Oꞌafiꞌa alu nofi vayaꞌai aꞌmafaꞌneꞌapimo alige aꞌmafaꞌneꞌapimo apamige huꞌa maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo hosu kavaꞌapimo akame huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 36 Aigofe gotiꞌapimogifeꞌmo mono huꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo Gotiꞌa apamagiꞌniye.
\v 37-38 Apakaemo mafaꞌneꞌapiꞌe aꞌmafaꞌneꞌapiꞌeꞌmo apamagiꞌa hosu apaune vayaꞌmo ofalinimo apamiꞌnae. Apakaemo mago kavaꞌmo osuꞌnaya nute mafaꞌneꞌapimo apamagiteꞌa Kenani vayaꞌai aigofe gotiꞌapimogimo aliꞌa apamiꞌnae. Apamagiꞌnaya mafaꞌneꞌapimogi kolaꞌmoꞌa mopamo alagi alino hosu huno ateꞌniye.
\v 39 Apakaemo Gotiꞌa apakameꞌya amiteꞌa hosu kavaꞌmo huteꞌa apakaiꞌapimo aliꞌa hosu huꞌa apateꞌnae.
\v 40 Ani kava huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa agaiꞌa vayaꞌaifeꞌmo aipamo leno apateteno ohauꞌniye.
\v 41 Hapa oꞌmaeno afaꞌa apakeno apataleꞌnigeꞌapaeꞌmo alu nofi vayaꞌmo kame vayaꞌapimogimo eꞌa yagaiꞌa apateꞌnae.
\v 42 Kame vayaꞌapimogi yagaiꞌa apateꞌnageꞌa apaiyafiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa geꞌapimo akame huꞌnae.
\v 43 Agaemo asole afinaꞌmo apakufamo alino katino apateme apateme eꞌniyaꞌmonanafa apakameꞌya amiteꞌa hosu kavaꞌmo huteꞌapaeꞌmo hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnae.
\v 44 Ani kava huꞌa maiꞌnayaꞌmonanafa agaefeꞌmo keya aeꞌa ge huꞌnageno hau huno apateꞌniye.
\v 45 Kotalake gemo huguve, huno hu maleꞌniya geꞌaeꞌmo agesamo afiꞌniye. Apakaefeꞌmo hau huno apateteno halate agesamo afiꞌniye.
\v 46 Agaemo kalavusi aliꞌyateꞌmo apavaleli uꞌa apateꞌnaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo hapa paiꞌnigeꞌa hapau huꞌa apateꞌnae.
\v 47 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, Ala kava netimogae, lagufamo alika katika lateteka alu nofi vayaꞌai apayapatiꞌmo lavaleka alika anupa huka lategetao kaote kagikaleꞌmo alita asaga huta ateteta kahao ke heteta lamogaga aino.
\p 
\v 48 Isaleli vayaꞌai Gotiꞌapimo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Hemenimo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hutetapa muki afinaꞌefeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Muki vayaꞌamogitapamo he, lama ge hutapa hiyo. Agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo.
\p Gotiꞌa hosu kavategatiꞌmo apakufamo alino katino neꞌateya kavafeꞌmo ava gemo huꞌniya gemae
\c 107
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa muki vayaꞌaitegamo nehiya kavafeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmo alagepa vekamo maiꞌneno muki afinaꞌamo hau huno apateme apateme uno hau huno apategaiyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo hao ke heyo.
\v 2 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa kame vayaꞌapimogi apayapatiꞌmo hatu maeno apateꞌniya vayaꞌmogimo, Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hatu maeno lateꞌniye, huꞌa hisaya gemo haneꞌniye.
\v 3 Agaemo yegemo haine neꞌeya kotegatiꞌmo apavalelino ege yegemo lamino nefaleya kotegatiꞌmo apavalelino ege aluga aluga haopalegatiꞌmo apavalelino ege huno apavalelino eno alino anupa huno apateꞌniye.
\p 
\v 4 Mago vayaꞌmo aniꞌmo ohaneno kaꞌme kotega vayaꞌmo oꞌmaiꞌnaya kotegamo afaꞌa umenitata nehuꞌapaeꞌmo maisaya taonieꞌmo kahauya huꞌnayaꞌmonanafa oꞌageꞌnae.
\v 5 Afaꞌa umenitata nehagenoꞌaeꞌmo apaka tege anifeꞌmo hapauge nehigenoꞌaeꞌmo apakupi mafaꞌneꞌageꞌmo apaunena aiꞌniye.
\v 6 Ani kava huꞌa hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌa ge huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo lusi hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnaya kavapatiꞌmo apavalelino eꞌniye.
\v 7 Agaemo uꞌa maisaya taonifiꞌmo visayafeꞌmo fatago kateꞌmo apavalelino uꞌniye.
\v 8 O, Vayaꞌmogi Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa muki vayaꞌaitegamo alagepa kavaꞌamo ageteꞌa hapau aiꞌnaya kavafeꞌmo hao ke heyo.
\v 9 Agaemo hapauꞌnigeꞌa hapaꞌye nehiya vayaꞌmo alino falu huno apatege apaka neteya vayaꞌmo alagepa yaꞌmo alino apamige huno neꞌmaiyaꞌmofeꞌmae.
\p 
\v 10-11 Mago vayaꞌamogimo Gotiꞌapimo geꞌamo ago amagiꞌa ataleteꞌa anaga hogote vekamoꞌa hisaya kavafeꞌmo huꞌniya geeꞌmo, afa gemo huꞌniye, huꞌa huteꞌa ataleꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo seli nofitetiꞌmo kino apateꞌnigeꞌa hani huꞌniya yapiꞌmo ulunapiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa falisaya kavapiꞌmo maiꞌnae.
\v 12 Ani kava huꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo lokiya aliꞌyaꞌmo alino apamiꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo lokiyaꞌapimo alagi hano huꞌniye. Apakaemo mopafiꞌmo asagauꞌa aiꞌnageꞌapaeꞌmo mago hapa maesaya vayaꞌmo alagi oꞌmaiꞌnae.
\v 13 Ani kava huꞌa hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌa maiꞌneꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava nefeꞌmo keya aeꞌa ge huꞌnageno afiteno hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnaya kavaꞌapifatiꞌmo apakufamo alino katino apateꞌniye.
\v 14 Agaemo seli nofiꞌmo alino kapalu aeno ataleteno hani huꞌniya yapiꞌmo ulunapiꞌmo maiꞌneꞌa falisaya kavapatiꞌmo apavalelino uꞌniye.
\v 15 O, Vayaꞌmogi Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa muki vayaꞌaitegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo nehiya kavaꞌamo ageteꞌa hapau aiꞌnaya kavafeꞌmo hao ke heyo.
\v 16 Na kava huꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo hao ke hegae. Agaemo yafa lafi kegiꞌyale kateꞌmo aeni kitamo alino lo aeteno lokiya aeniletiꞌmo ka akani maleꞌnaya aenimo alino lo ae maleꞌniye.
\p 
\v 17 Negi nagi vayaꞌmogimo Goti geꞌamo ago amagiꞌa atalege hosu kavaꞌmo huge huꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo kaita hapauꞌniye.
\v 18 Muki alu neꞌya alu neꞌyafeꞌmo ohapauꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo faligefeꞌmo huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 19 Ani kava huꞌa hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌa ge huꞌnageno hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnaya kavaꞌapifatiꞌmo apakufamo alino katino apateꞌniye.
\v 20 Gotiꞌa geꞌamo alino ateꞌnigeno emineꞌniya geꞌaletiꞌmo alino alagepa huno apateꞌniye. Agaemo falisaya agufa hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnaya kavategatiꞌmo apavalelino uꞌniye.
\v 21 O, Vayaꞌmogimo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa muki vayaꞌaitegamo huꞌniya alagepa kavaꞌamo ageteꞌa hapau aiꞌnaya kavaꞌaeꞌmo hao ke heyo.
\v 22 Apakaemo Gotifeꞌmo hao ke hesaya ofalinimo amagiꞌa amiyo. Amiteꞌa aliꞌyaꞌalefeꞌmo apamogaga aiteꞌapaeꞌmo aeꞌa hakalo hiyo.
\p 
\v 23 Alopa solovala anipiꞌmo sipifiꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌmo neꞌaliya vayaꞌmogimo
\v 24 Ala kava neꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌamo agege solovala aniteꞌmo huꞌniya kavaꞌamo ageteꞌa hapau aiꞌnaya kavaꞌmo agege huꞌa neꞌagae.
\v 25 Agaemo yasi aliyo, huno nehigenoꞌaeꞌmo lusi kava huno yasimo aliꞌnigeno aniꞌmoꞌa aino holakau holakau huteno apavalelino haiteno lamiteno nehiye.
\v 26 Sipifi maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaiteꞌmo lusi hanageke yaꞌmo afole aiꞌnigeꞌa kokuꞌnapilagamo haiteꞌa emiꞌeꞌa afepilagamo lamiteꞌa huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo apakupi mafaꞌnemoꞌmo ani hegekana huꞌniye.
\v 27 Alopa aniꞌmo neteꞌa negi nagi huteꞌa laku taka nehaya vayakana huꞌa maiꞌnae. Alagepa huta maisunafeꞌmo na kava hisupi huꞌa apakesamo oꞌafiꞌnae.
\v 28 Ani kava huꞌa hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌa ge huꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnaya kavapatiꞌmo apakufamo alino katino apateꞌniye.
\v 29 Agaemo yasieꞌmo afaꞌa maiyo, huno huꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo aniꞌeꞌmo afaꞌa haneꞌnaꞌae.
\v 30 Aniꞌmo afaꞌa haneꞌnigeꞌa apamogaga aiꞌnae. Ani kava huno apavalelino uno solovala ani agiꞌnaleꞌmo haneꞌniya taonifiꞌmo uꞌa avaꞌyi huteꞌa alagepa huꞌa maisayafeꞌmo huꞌniya taonifiꞌmo apateꞌniye.
\v 31 O, Vayaꞌmogimo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa muki vayaꞌaitegamo huꞌniya alagepa kavaꞌamo ageteꞌa hapau aiꞌnaya kavaꞌaeꞌmo hao ke heyo.
\v 32 Apakaemo aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maisayateꞌmo ala agiꞌamo amiyo. Apakaemo vayatama vayaꞌmogi aliꞌa anupa huꞌa maisayateꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa ateyo.
\p 
\v 33 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alopa aniꞌmo alino leneno neꞌatale. Haine neꞌeya meti aniꞌmo alagi alino hano huno neꞌatale.
\v 34 Vayaꞌmogimo hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo mopafatiꞌmo asole neꞌyaꞌmo neꞌaeya mopaꞌapimo alino hosu mopamo hamaleno neꞌate.
\v 35 Nehiyaꞌmonanafa hau huꞌniya mopamo alino lanitani mopamo hamaleno neꞌate. Aniꞌmo ohaneꞌniya mopafatiꞌmo aniꞌmo alo huno ateꞌnigeno haine neꞌe.
\v 36 Agaemo apaka neteya vayaꞌmo ani mopaleꞌmo maisayafeꞌmo apavalelino uno neꞌapate. Apakaemo maisaya taoniꞌapimo kisayafeꞌmo apavalelino uno neꞌapate.
\v 37 Apakaemo asole neꞌyaꞌapimo alisayafeꞌmo avina yaꞌmo hakalege nofi alagamo faige huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 38 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hapa neꞌmaegeꞌapaeꞌmo asole mafaꞌnemo aliꞌa neꞌapatae. Pulumaka anagaꞌmo hapa neꞌmaegeꞌapaeꞌmo magoꞌe huꞌa aiꞌa atagu nefae.
\p 
\v 39 Kame vayaꞌapimogi kana yaꞌmo aliꞌa apamige hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌa apamige huꞌa aliꞌa apamisagenoꞌaeꞌmo apaipamoꞌmo kana hisigeꞌa alagepa huꞌa oꞌmaisaya afinaꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hapa maegaiye.
\v 40 Agaemo kame vayaꞌapileꞌmo neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmo alino afepi apateꞌnigeꞌa kaꞌmo ohaneꞌniya kaꞌme kotegamo afaꞌa umenitata nehae.
\v 41 Alino afepiꞌmo neꞌateyaꞌmonanafa kagemi yaꞌapimo oꞌmaleꞌnaya vayaꞌmo alino asaga huno anaꞌaleꞌmo neꞌategeꞌa hanageke yaꞌmo noꞌaliye. Hapa neꞌmaegeꞌa afamo anagaꞌmo magokepiꞌmo lokaeꞌa maiꞌnaya sipisipi anagakana huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 42 Fatago vayaꞌmogimo ani kavaꞌmo ageteꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiyaꞌmonanafa hosu vayaꞌmo apavayaleꞌmo alino akani maleꞌnigeꞌa apake noꞌaiye.
\p 
\v 43 Muki afiteꞌa ageꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo ani kavafeꞌmo apakesa afifi huꞌa maigae. Apakaemo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa vayaꞌaeꞌmo hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauꞌniya kavaꞌamo ageꞌa aeto hugae.
\c 110
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa Ala kava netieꞌmo ha paiꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa Ala kava neꞌnieꞌmo, lamaga nahaopaleꞌmo faika maime maime neꞌugeꞌnao kame vayakamo aliꞌna kaiya afeꞌalumelaga apateno, huno ha paiꞌniye.
\v 2 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa kayotetiꞌmo yagaika apatesana himamukamo Saiyoni taonifatiꞌmo alino atesigeno ugiye. Kame vayakamogi folagapiꞌmo maiꞌneka yagaika apato, huno kaha paiꞌniye.
\v 3 Himamukaletiꞌmo hisana afinaꞌmo vayakamogimo apaipafatiꞌmo hapauꞌnisigeꞌa apakufamo kamiteꞌa apaote konali kukenamo aliꞌa vaiteꞌa kakame hugae. Aꞌnemogimo apaipa kupatiꞌmo mafaꞌnemo aliꞌa neꞌataya kava huno netepiꞌmo laoꞌyaꞌmo nelamiye. Ani kava huno Gotiꞌa neya vayakamo alino apatesigeꞌa laoꞌyakana huꞌa afole aiteꞌa kagaetegamo ugae.
\v 4 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa aipa agesamo alino afe oleno agoꞌyamo ataleno ge hunoꞌaeꞌmo, Melikisetekiꞌa mono huno neꞌateya vekamo maiꞌniya kava huka agae akamelegatiꞌmo agae nofi vekamo mono huka neꞌatana vekamo maiꞌneka muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo maige maige huka maigane, huno kaha paiꞌniye.
\p 
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmo lamaga kahaopaleꞌmo maiꞌniye. Agaemo aipamo leno apatesiya afinaꞌmo kini vayaꞌmo alagi apamagigiye.
\v 6 Agaemo muki alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌmo alino fako huno apateteno kamiti apamagisigeꞌa faliteꞌapaeꞌmo apakufaꞌamo mopafiꞌmo asagauꞌa aigae. Agaemo muki haopalega maiꞌnaya kini vayaꞌaifeꞌmo kame huno apateteno huno aeno apakasegaiye.
\v 7 Kategamo neꞌunoꞌaeꞌmo ka agiꞌnaleꞌmo haneꞌniya anipatiꞌmo negaiyaꞌmofeꞌmo he tino lokiya vaino aeno apakasegaiye.
\c 116
\s1 Nagaemo ge huꞌnogeno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa afiteno naha maeꞌniye, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Nagaemo nunumu huge keya aeꞌna ge huge huꞌna maiꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa afiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo neꞌnahaiye.
\v 2 Keya aeꞌna ge huꞌnogeno geꞌnimo afiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo ofaliꞌna afaꞌa maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge huguve.
\v 3 Falisuva kavaꞌmoꞌa nofi aegekana huno natafauno alagi huno maiꞌniye. Kanolufiꞌmo lamiguve, huꞌna nagesamo afiteꞌna nahausoli huteꞌna koli huꞌnove.
\v 4 Ani kava huꞌna maiꞌneꞌna Ala kava nefeꞌmo, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahao ke hovanagi nagufamo alika katika nato, huꞌna keya aeꞌna ge huꞌnove.
\p 
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fiku hapa maeno apamige fatago kavaꞌamo huge huno neꞌmaiye. Gotitimoꞌa hau huno nelateya vekamo maiꞌniye.
\v 6 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa apamuꞌamo ohaneꞌnigeꞌa afiteꞌa oꞌageꞌnaya vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino neꞌapate. Hosu yaꞌmo aliꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo naha maeꞌniye.
\v 7 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alagepa huno naha maeꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo nauneꞌnameyo, huꞌna, maika aika afeleka maika falu huvo.
\v 8 Ala kava neꞌnimogae, huꞌna, falisuva kavategatiꞌmo nagufaꞌnimo ago alika katika nateꞌneka naunumo aeka kalo paeka nateteka naiyafiꞌmo oꞌnahaesiyafeꞌmo yagaika nateꞌnane.
\v 9 Nagaemo Ala kava neꞌmo aulagaleꞌmo ofaliꞌa afaꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌaitegamo umenitata nehuve.
\v 10 Nagesamo afiꞌna fatago nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo ge huꞌnove. Ge huꞌnaeꞌmo, lusi hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌnove, huꞌna ge huꞌnove.
\v 11 Nagaemo, Muki vayaꞌaifeꞌmo aigofe vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae, huꞌna alagepa huꞌna nagesamo oꞌafiꞌneꞌna malage huꞌna ge huꞌnove.
\p 
\v 12 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa nagaetegamo lusi kava huno alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo anonaꞌalefeꞌmo na agufa yaꞌmo amiguve.
\v 13 Nagaemo lagufamo alino katino lateꞌniya kavafeꞌmo nagesamo afiteꞌna kapufi aniꞌmo aliꞌna neteꞌna Ala kava nefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge huguve.
\v 14 Nagaemo, naha maeꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaetegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo huguve, huꞌna huꞌnova gemo akame huꞌna Ala kava neꞌmo vayaꞌamogi apaulagaleꞌmo agaetegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo huguve.
\v 15 Gotiꞌa vayaꞌaeꞌmo, hogote vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae, huno huteno agesamo neꞌafiyaꞌmofeꞌmo mago vayaꞌamo falisagenoꞌaeꞌmo, ina agufa vayane, huno osuno amuse huno apategaiye.
\v 16 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamo maiꞌnove. Itaꞌnimoꞌmo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaliya aꞌmo maiꞌniya kava huꞌna maiꞌnove. Hatu maeka nateꞌnanageꞌna afa vekamo maiꞌnove.
\v 17 Kahao ke heꞌna ofalinimo kamiteꞌna kagaefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge huguve.
\v 18 Naha maeꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo Ala kava nefeꞌmo, kagaetegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo huguve, huꞌna huꞌnova gemo akame huꞌna vayaꞌamogi apaulagaleꞌmo agaetegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo huguve.
\v 19 Yulusalemu taoni folagapiꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo mono noꞌafiꞌmo huguve. Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo.
\c 117
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 O alu nofi vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Muki alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌe alu nofi vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hiyo.
\v 2 Na kava huꞌnigetaene. Agaemo lusi kava huno hau huno lateteno alino ao yaꞌmo hu maleꞌniye. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa lapa maegauve, huno laha paiꞌniya gemo lama geꞌamoꞌmo muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hanege hanege huno afaꞌa hanegaiye.
\p Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo.
\c 118
\s1 Muki afinaꞌmo hau huno neꞌapateyanageno ani kava huno hau huno apategaiye, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmo alagepa vekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo hao ke heyo. Hau huno neꞌapateyanageno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hau huno apatege apatege huno maigiye.
\v 2 Isaleli vayaꞌmogitamo, Hau huno neꞌapateyanageno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hau huno apatege apatege huno maigiye, huta higetao.
\v 3 Eloni nofi vayaꞌamogitapamo, Hau huno neꞌapateyanageno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hau huno apatege apatege huno maigiye, hutapa hiyo.
\v 4 Muki vayaꞌamogitapamo agaefekeꞌmo koli hutetapa mono nehaya vayaꞌmogitapamo, Hau huno neꞌapateyanageno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hau huno apatege apatege huno maigiye, hutapa hiyo.
\p 
\v 5 Lusi hanageke yaꞌmo aliꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge huꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo geꞌnimo afiteno hatu maeno nateꞌnigeꞌna afaꞌa maiꞌnove.
\v 6 Ala kava neꞌmo nagae vekamogeno naha maesiyafeꞌmo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo vayaꞌmogi nagaetegamo hisaya kavafeꞌmo koli osuguve.
\v 7 Ala kava neꞌmo nagae vekamogeno naha maesiyafeꞌmo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo apakeꞌnovana kame vayaꞌnimo asagauꞌa aigae.
\v 8 Vayaꞌmogimo laha maesayafeꞌmo lagesamo afisunana kanale osugifa Ala kava nefekeꞌmo laha maegaiye, huta lagesamo afisunana kanale hugiye.
\v 9 Ala apaki aliteꞌa neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogi laha maesayafeꞌmo lagesamo afisunana kanale osugifa Ala kava nefekeꞌmo laha maegaiye, huta lagesamo afisunana kanale hugiye.
\p 
\v 10 Muki alu nofi vaya alu nofi vayaꞌmo kame vayaꞌnimo maiꞌneꞌa faiꞌa ku aiꞌa nateꞌnageꞌnaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo himamuꞌaletiꞌmo alagi aliꞌna hano huꞌna apatalegauve.
\v 11 Muki haopalega maiꞌneꞌa faiꞌa ku aiꞌa nateꞌnageꞌnaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo himamuꞌaletiꞌmo alagi aliꞌna hano huꞌna apatalegauve.
\v 12 Kevegevegana huꞌa faiꞌa ku aiꞌa nateꞌnayaꞌmonanafa aufe nofipiꞌmo malage huno atamo leno yu neheya kava huꞌna Ala kava neꞌmo himamuꞌaletiꞌmo alagi aliꞌna hano huꞌna apatalegauve.
\v 13 Kameꞌnimogae, huꞌna, alika nagoꞌya faitalanageꞌna heleve hugefe huꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa naha maeꞌniye.
\v 14 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa lokiya vaino nateꞌnigeꞌna yoke nehuve. Agaemo nagufamo ago alino katino nateꞌniye.
\v 15 Afiyo, huꞌna, alagepa vayaꞌmogimo seli noꞌapifatiꞌmo apakufamo ago alino katino apateꞌniya kavafeꞌmo yoke huꞌapaeꞌmo, Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa himamuꞌaletiꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo huꞌniye.
\v 16 Himamuꞌaletiꞌmo aeta apakaseꞌnone, huꞌa nehae.
\v 17 Ofaliꞌna afaꞌa maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa huꞌniya kavafeꞌmo ava gemo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paiguve.
\v 18 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa lusi kava huno namagiꞌniyaꞌmonanafa falisuvafeꞌmo afaꞌa oꞌnataleꞌniye.
\p 
\v 19 Alopa mono noꞌmo kitamo yakika nategeꞌnao haiꞌna Ala kava nefeꞌmo hao ke heno.
\v 20 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa kipaꞌamo haneꞌnigeꞌa alagepa vayaꞌageꞌmo faleꞌa nehaiye.
\v 21 Geꞌnimo afiteka nagufamo alika katika nateꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo kahao ke nehove.
\p 
\v 22 Yafatetiꞌmo no nekiya vayaꞌmogimo mago no nekiya yafafeꞌmo, afa yafane, huꞌa huteꞌa aliꞌa yaga auꞌa ataleꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo Gotiꞌa ani yafafeꞌmo, hogote yafaꞌmo noꞌmo faiꞌna atesuvafeꞌmo konale yafaꞌmo haneꞌniye, huno huteno alino asaga huno ateꞌniye.
\v 23 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa ani kavaꞌmo huꞌnigetaeꞌmo ageteta aeto agufa kanale kava huꞌniye, huta lahau aiꞌnone.
\v 24 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa ani afinaꞌmo hu maleꞌniye. Ani afinaꞌmo lamogaga aigetao.
\v 25 Aukaya hutaeꞌmo, O Ala kava nene, huta, lagufamo alika katika lato. O Ala kava nene, huta, laha maegenoꞌao aliꞌyatimoꞌmo alagepa huno afole aino, huta aukaya nehune.
\v 26 Gotiꞌa Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌalefeꞌmo neꞌeya vekamo fiku ha maeno amino. Lagaemo Ala kava neꞌmo mono noꞌafatiꞌmo Gotiꞌa fiku lapa maeno lapamino, huta nehune.
\v 27 Ala kava neꞌmo Gotiꞌa maiꞌniye. Agaemo ha le yaꞌamo alino lamiꞌniye. Ofalini afumo alitapa hiꞌyalamuteꞌmo maleꞌnetapa nofitetiꞌmo kitapa atafau maleyo.
\v 28 Gotiꞌnimogamo maiꞌnananageꞌna kahao ke hegauve. Gotiꞌnimogamo maiꞌnananageꞌna ala kagikamo kamiguve.
\p 
\v 29 Ala kava neꞌmo alagepa vekamo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agaefekeꞌmo hao ke heyo. Hau huno neꞌapateyanageno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hau huno apatege apatege huno maigiye.
\c 119
\s1 Goti geꞌaeꞌmo ava gemae
\p 
\v 1 Vayaꞌmogimo alagepa kavaꞌmo nehuꞌapaeꞌmo vaiꞌmo oꞌaliꞌa Ala kava neꞌmo keꞌaepa geꞌamo akame nehaya vayaꞌmogi Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\v 2 Avayafatiꞌmo huꞌniya keꞌaepa geꞌamo akame huge agesayafeꞌmo muki apaipafatiꞌmo kahauya huge huꞌa neꞌmaiya vayaꞌmogi Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\v 3 Apakaemo mago hosu kavaꞌmo osuꞌa Ala kava neꞌmo kateꞌmo umenitata nehae.
\v 4 Kagaemo, lapayamukiki hutapa geꞌnimo akame hiyo, huka huꞌnane.
\v 5 Gekamo alagepa huꞌna afiteꞌna akame hisuvafeꞌmo neꞌnahaiye.
\v 6 Muki gekamo ageteꞌna afisuva afinaꞌmo navagage osugiye.
\v 7 Nagaemo fatago kavaꞌmo huka alika fako huka nehana gekamo alagepa huꞌna afiteꞌnaeꞌmo alagepa fatago naipafatiꞌmo ala kagikamo kamiguve.
\v 8 Avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo akame huguvanagi alagi nataleka oꞌuvo.
\p 
\v 9 Haiya kava huno neya vekamoꞌmo nehiya kavaꞌamo afaꞌa aeno kalo paeno atalegaiye. Agaemo gekamo alagepa huno afisiya kavatetikeꞌmo afaꞌa aeno kalo paeno atalegaiye.
\v 10 Muki naipafatiꞌmo kagesuvafeꞌmo kahauya huꞌnove. Hiyo, huka huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo ataleꞌna visuvafeꞌmo oꞌnatalo.
\v 11 Kagaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo osisuvafeꞌmo gekamo naipafiꞌmo aliꞌna fala ki maleꞌnove.
\v 12 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, alagi alagepa huka maiꞌnane. Avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo alika naya malo.
\v 13 Nagaemo navayafatiꞌmo muki gekamo fatago kavaꞌmo huka kavayafatiꞌmo alika fako nehana keꞌaepa gekamo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paiꞌnove.
\v 14 Ma mopafi alopa kagemi yafeꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiya kava huꞌna kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana gekamo akame hisuvafeꞌmo namogaga neꞌauve.
\v 15 Namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maige neꞌvana kaꞌmo ageꞌna alagepa huꞌna agege huꞌna maiguve.
\v 16 Nagaemo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo namogaga aiteꞌna nage okanigiye.
\p 
\v 17 Kagaemo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekakamo magoꞌe huka fiku alika namigeꞌnao ma mopafiꞌmo afaꞌa maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo gekamo akame hino.
\v 18 Naulagamo alika ayakeka nategeꞌnao keꞌaepa gekamo ageteꞌna nahau aiguve.
\v 19 Ma mopafiꞌmo nata neꞌna neꞌvisugekaeꞌmo gekamo afisuvafeꞌmo alika fala okika alika nave liyo.
\v 20 Muki afinaꞌmo alika fako nehana keꞌaepa gekamo afisuva naipamo nekaliyaꞌmofeꞌmo naipafiꞌmo nagafu nekiye.
\v 21 Himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo huka faipa huka apateꞌnana vayaꞌmogimo kakamo ataleꞌa neꞌvagekaeꞌmo ge nehapane.
\v 22 Kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana gekamo akame huꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa natege hosu gemo huge nehagi apavayamo alika akani apategeꞌa afaꞌa maiyo.
\v 23 Neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogimo fai maiꞌneꞌapaeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa nateꞌnayaꞌmonanafa aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌna avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maiꞌnove.
\v 24 Kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana gekaeꞌmo namogaga neꞌauve. Gekamoꞌmo visuva kaꞌmo alino nave neliye.
\p 
\v 25 Nagupi mafaꞌnemo asagauno aiteno mopafiꞌmo maiꞌniye. Lapa maegauve, huka huꞌnana gekamo akame huka alika he tika nato.
\v 26 Nagaemo nehuva kavaꞌnieꞌmo kaha paiꞌnogekaeꞌmo geꞌnileꞌmo aeka atagaina huka naha paiꞌnane. Avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo alika naya malo.
\v 27 Alika naya malegeꞌna namiꞌnana gemo aepaꞌamo afiꞌna alagepa huꞌna afino. Neꞌalina aliꞌyakamo ageteꞌnaeꞌmo nahau aiꞌnova kavaꞌnieꞌmo hapa paiguve.
\v 28 Kanamo aliꞌnogeno nagupi mafaꞌnemoꞌmo ani hegekana huꞌniye. Lokiya vaiꞌna kategauve, huka huꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo lokiya vaika nato.
\v 29 Aigofe kateꞌmo oꞌvisuvafeꞌmo ka akani maleteka keꞌaepa gemo fiku alika namiyo.
\v 30 Lama ge kateꞌmo uguve, huꞌna nagesa afiꞌnove. Alika fako huꞌnana gemo aliꞌna naulagaleꞌmo maleꞌnove.
\v 31 Kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana geleꞌmo aliꞌna kamaeꞌnove. O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, navagage yaꞌmo alika oꞌnamiyo.
\v 32 Magoꞌe huka naipa nagesamo alika namisanageꞌnaeꞌmo nagu nagu huꞌna gekamo hiyo, huka laha paiꞌnana gemo akame huꞌna huguve.
\p 
\v 33 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo alika naya malegeꞌnao oꞌataleꞌna akame hume hume uꞌna hano hisiya afinaꞌeꞌmo akame hino.
\v 34 Alagepa huꞌna nagesamo afisuva yaꞌmo alika namigeꞌnao keꞌaepa gekamo akame hino. He, muki naipafatiꞌmo akame huguve.
\v 35 Hiyo, huka laha paiꞌnana gekaeꞌmo namogaga neꞌauvaꞌmofeꞌmo ani kateꞌmo uꞌneꞌna hisuva naipamo alika kalika nato.
\v 36 Fiku yanageꞌna ma mopafi yafeꞌmo nahaꞌye hugiye. Kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana gekamo akame hisuva naipa nagesamo alika namiyo.
\v 37 Alu yaꞌmo aulu haeꞌna neꞌagesugekaeꞌmo alika aika afe leka nato. Kagae kateꞌmo neꞌvisugekaeꞌmo alika he tika nato.
\v 38 Aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌnafiꞌmo gekamo alika lokiya vaika ato, kagaefekeꞌmo koli nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmae.
\v 39 Alagepa huka alika fako nehanaꞌmofeꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo hisugeꞌapaeꞌmo huꞌa faipa huꞌa natesayafeꞌmo koli nehuvanagi naha mao.
\v 40 Namiꞌnana gekaeꞌmo nahaꞌye nehiye. Fatago kavakaletiꞌmo alika he tika nato.
\p 
\v 41 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahau huka nato. Huguve, huka huꞌnana kavaꞌmo huka nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 42 Gekamokeꞌmo naha maegaiye, huꞌna nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo huno faipa huno neꞌnateya vekamo geꞌaleꞌmo aeꞌna atagaina huꞌna ha paiguve.
\v 43 Alika fako nehana gekaeꞌmo nagesa afiꞌnaeꞌmo, naha maegaiye, huꞌna nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo lama gekamo navayafatiꞌmo alika oꞌatalo.
\v 44 Ani kava huꞌna maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo keꞌaepa gekamo akame hume hume uꞌna maiguve.
\v 45 Namiꞌnana gekamo afisuvafeꞌmo kahauya nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo kalavusifiꞌmo oꞌmaiꞌna afaꞌa maiguve.
\v 46 Nagaemo kavayafatiꞌmo nehana gemo aliꞌna neꞌyagaiya kini vayaꞌaifeꞌmo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paisugenoꞌaeꞌmo navagage osugiye.
\v 47 Nagaemo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo neꞌnahaiya gekaeꞌmo hiyo, huka laha paiꞌnana gekaeꞌmo namogaga aiguve.
\v 48 Nagaemo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo neꞌnahaiya gekaeꞌmo hiyo, huka laha paiꞌnana gekalefeꞌmo nayaꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huteꞌna avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya gekaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maiguve.
\p 
\v 49 Kagaemo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌnaeꞌmo kaha maegauve, huka naha paiꞌnana gekaeꞌmo halate kagesamo afika ho huvo. Ani gekaeꞌmo nagesamo afiꞌnaeꞌmo, alagi afole aigiye, huꞌna huteꞌna navayagunagu huꞌna maisuvafeꞌmo alika he tika nateꞌnane.
\v 50 Gekamoꞌmo alagepa huꞌna maisuva yaꞌmo alino namiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo kana yaꞌmo neꞌalugenoꞌaeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo falu nehiye.
\v 51 Apakiꞌapileꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa neꞌapataya vayaꞌmogimo kigi yokalo gegeꞌmo huꞌa neꞌnatayaꞌmonanafa keꞌaepa gekamo oꞌataleꞌnove.
\v 52 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, akeyaꞌvilagamo gekamo alika fako nehana gekaeꞌmo nagesamo afiꞌna ho huteꞌna naipamo aliꞌna falu huꞌna neꞌatove.
\v 53 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo keꞌaepa gekamo ago amagiꞌa neꞌatalayaꞌmofeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo atete nehiye.
\v 54 Nata neꞌna eꞌna maiꞌnova noꞌnifiꞌmo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo yoke huꞌnove.
\v 55 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, haniꞌilagamo kagikaeꞌmo nagesamo afiꞌna ho nehuꞌnaeꞌmo keꞌaepa gekamo akame nehuve.
\v 56 Namiꞌnana gekamo akame huꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo ani yaꞌmo aliꞌnove.
\p 
\v 57 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kagaemo hetamaꞌnimo maiꞌnane. Nagaemo gekaleꞌmo yagaiꞌneꞌna akame huguve, huꞌna huꞌnove.
\v 58 Nagaemo muki naipafatiꞌmo, fiku naha maeka namiyo, huꞌna kaha paiꞌnove. Nahau huꞌna lapategauve, huka laha paiꞌnana kava huka kahau huka nato.
\v 59 Nagaemo kavaꞌnieꞌmo nagesa afiteꞌnaeꞌmo aiꞌna afe leꞌna kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana gemo akame huꞌnove.
\v 60 Hiyo, huka laha paiꞌnana gemo akame hisuvafeꞌmo afaꞌa oꞌmaiꞌna malage huꞌna he tiꞌna akame huꞌnove.
\v 61 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo nofitetiꞌmo kiꞌa nateꞌnayaꞌmonanafa keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nage okaniꞌniye.
\v 62 Kagaemo fatago kavaꞌmo huka alika fako nehanaꞌmofeꞌmo haniꞌilaga folaguꞌmo he tiꞌna kahao ke hegauve.
\v 63 Nagaemo kagaefeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌeꞌmo magokepiꞌmo lokaeta maiꞌnone. Apamiꞌnana geleꞌmo yagaiꞌa ateꞌneꞌa akame nehaya vayaꞌeꞌmo magokepiꞌmo lokaeta maiꞌnone.
\v 64 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahau huka neꞌapatana kavakamoꞌmo ma mopafiꞌmo havai teꞌniye. Avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo alika naya malo.
\p 
\v 65 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Kaha maegauve, huka huteka ani kava huka aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamo magoꞌe huka naha maeꞌnane.
\v 66 Nagaemo hiyo, huka huꞌnana gekaeꞌmo nagesamo afiꞌna fatago nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo alagepa naipa nagesamo alika namiyo.
\v 67 Kayoꞌmo oꞌnamiꞌnanageꞌnaeꞌmo hogoteꞌna gekamo ago ataleꞌnovaꞌmonanafa hemenimo gekamo akame nehuve.
\v 68 Alagepa kavaꞌmo huteka alagepa vekamo yagu yaga kaipa vekamo maiꞌnananagi avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo alika naya malo.
\v 69 Himuꞌnamu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogi aigofe nava gemo huteꞌa huꞌa faipa huꞌa nateꞌnayaꞌmonanafa muki naipafatiꞌmo namiꞌnana gekamo akame huguve.
\v 70 Apaipamo yafakana huno haneꞌnigeꞌa afiꞌa aeto nosayaꞌmonanafa keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo amuse nehuve.
\v 71 Kayoꞌmo namiꞌnanageꞌnaeꞌmo gekamo afiꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo kayoꞌmoꞌa alagepa huno naha maeꞌniye.
\v 72 Kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamoꞌmo tauseni monimo ago aeno agaseꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo gekaeꞌmo magoꞌe huno neꞌnahaiye.
\p 
\v 73 Kagaemo kayatetiꞌmo nagupi mafaꞌnemo alo huka nateteka nagufamo alo huka nateꞌnane. Hiyo, huka laha paiꞌnana gemo afisuva nagesamo namiyo.
\v 74 Nagaemo gekamoꞌa naha maegaiye, huꞌna huteꞌna navayagunagu huꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo kagaefeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌmogi nageteꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga aigae.
\v 75 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, afiꞌnovana alika fako nehana kavaꞌmo alagepa kavaꞌmo haneꞌnigeka gekamo akame huteka naha maesanafeꞌmo kana yaꞌmo alika namiꞌnane.
\v 76 Kagaemo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌnaeꞌmo naha paiꞌnana gekamo akame huka alagepa huka kahau huka nateteka naipamo alika falu huka nato.
\v 77 Keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo namogaga neꞌauvaꞌmofeꞌmo kahau huka nategeꞌnao afaꞌa maino.
\v 78 Apakiꞌapileꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa neꞌataya vayaꞌmogimo nagaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo apavagage hisiya yaꞌmo alika apamiyo. Nagaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo huꞌnayaꞌmonanafa namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maiguve.
\v 79 Kagaefeꞌmo koli huteꞌa kagaemo kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo afiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo alika aika atagineka apategeꞌapao nagaetegamo eyo.
\v 80 Nagaemo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekaleꞌmo aeꞌna hapaisuva naipa nagesamo alika namigeꞌnao navagage osisiyafeꞌmo akame hino.
\p 
\v 81 Nagufamo alika katika natesanafeꞌmo lusi kava huno nahauꞌnigeno lokiyaꞌnimo ago hano huꞌniyaꞌmonanafa kaha maegauve, huka huꞌnana gekaeꞌmo nagesamo afiteꞌna navayagunagu nehuve.
\v 82 Gekamo afole aisiyaꞌaeꞌmo aulu heꞌna ageꞌna maiꞌnogeno naulagafatiꞌmo nagafu nekiye. Hainu afinaꞌmo naha maeteka naipamo alika falu huka nategane.
\v 83 Nagaemo afu agufaletiꞌmo alo huꞌnaya ani kekana huꞌna maiꞌnove. Halinamo neꞌaigenoꞌaeꞌmo vaiꞌniya ani kekana huꞌna maiꞌnovaꞌmonanafa avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nage okaniꞌna nagesamo neꞌafuve.
\v 84 Na magi afinaꞌmo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌnamo kana yaꞌmo aliꞌna maiguve. Hainu afinaꞌmo apaini huꞌa neꞌnataya vayaꞌmo alika fako huka apateteka kayoꞌmo apamigane.
\v 85 Ala apaki aliteꞌa apakufamo avaleliꞌa nehaiya vayaꞌmogimo kelifiꞌmo asagauꞌna aisuvafeꞌmo kelimo kafi maleꞌnae. Ani kavaꞌmo keꞌaepa gekamo akame nosaya kavaꞌmo haneꞌniye.
\v 86 Kagaemo muki hiyo, huka laha paiꞌnana gekamo alagi lama gemo haneꞌniye. Apakaetegamo hosu kavaꞌmo osuꞌnovaꞌmonanafa apaini huꞌa neꞌnatae. Naha mao.
\v 87 Ma mopafiꞌmo maiꞌnogeꞌapaeꞌmo aliꞌa hano huꞌa natalesayafeꞌmo huꞌnageꞌnaeꞌmo hogoꞌamo faligefeꞌmo nehuꞌnaeꞌmo namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo oꞌataleꞌnove.
\v 88 Nagaemo kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo akame hisuvafeꞌmo muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo kahau kayamopafiꞌmo nekahaiya kavakaletiꞌmo alika he tika nato.
\p 
\v 89 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, gekamo alagi asagauno oꞌaigiyaꞌmonanafa kokuꞌnapiꞌmo lokiya vaino haneme haneme uno haneno hano osugiye.
\v 90 Kagaemo muki afinaꞌmo gekamo akame huka afole aiteꞌa faliteꞌa hume hume neꞌvaya vayaꞌaitegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo nehane. Kagaemo ma mopamo faika ateꞌnanageno haneme haneme eno hemenimo haneꞌniye.
\v 91 Muki yaꞌamo alo huꞌnanageno keꞌaepa gekamo akame huno haneme haneme eno hemeniꞌeꞌmo afaꞌa haneꞌniye. Muki yaꞌamogimo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaliye.
\v 92 Nagaemo keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo namogaga oꞌaiꞌnovesinana kana yaꞌmo aliꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo ago faliꞌnovesine.
\v 93 Namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo nage okanigiye. Gekaletiꞌmo alagepa huꞌna maisuva yaꞌmo alika namiꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmae.
\v 94 Nagaemo namiꞌnana keꞌaepa geeꞌmo kahauya huꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo nagaemo kagaika vekamo maiꞌnovanagi nagufamo alika katika nato.
\v 95 Hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogimo namagisageꞌna falisuvafeꞌmo nagava maiꞌnayaꞌmonanafa kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maiguve.
\v 96 Nagaemo ageꞌnovana muki haino hapaiꞌniya yaꞌmo ago hano huꞌnigeꞌna ageꞌnove. Hano huꞌniyaꞌmonanafa keꞌaepa gekamoꞌmo yofo yaꞌamoꞌmo alopa yaꞌmo haneꞌniye.
\p 
\v 97 Nagaemo keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo lusi kava huno nahau nayamopafiꞌmo nahauꞌniye. Neteꞌe uneꞌeꞌmo gekaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maiꞌnove.
\v 98 Muki afinaꞌmo kagaemo hiyo, huka huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo nagaeꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeno haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo keꞌaepa gekaletiꞌmo alika naya neꞌmalanageꞌnaeꞌmo nagaemo afiteꞌna ageꞌnova kavaꞌmoꞌa kame vayaꞌnimogi afiteꞌa ageꞌnaya kavaꞌapimo ago aeno agaseꞌniye.
\v 99 Kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana gekaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maiꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo nagaemo gemo aepaꞌamo afiꞌnova kavaꞌnimoꞌa tisa vayaꞌnimogi afiꞌnaya kavaꞌapimo ago aeno agaseꞌniye.
\v 100 Namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gemo akame nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo nagaemo gemo aepaꞌamo afiꞌnova kavaꞌnimoꞌa kosuna vayaꞌmogi gemo aepaꞌamo afiꞌnaya kavaꞌapimo ago aeno agaseꞌniye.
\v 101 Gekamo akame huteꞌna muki hosu kateꞌmo oꞌvisuvafeꞌmo naiyamo kalavusi huꞌna ateꞌnove.
\v 102 Kagaikamo alika naya maleꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo alika fako nehana gekamo oꞌataleꞌnove.
\v 103 Nagaemo gekamo neꞌna afi geꞌnogeno haga nahauꞌniye. Gekamo hagaꞌamoꞌmo kevegeve anumoꞌmo nehiya hagaꞌamo ago aeno agaseno haga nehiye.
\v 104 Namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gemoꞌa gemo aepaꞌamo neꞌafuva kavaꞌmo alino namiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo muki aigofe geeꞌmo alagi oꞌnahauꞌniye.
\p 
\v 105 Gekamoꞌmo lamugana huno haneꞌnenoꞌaeꞌmo aeno ha nelegeꞌna umenitata nehuve. Gekamoꞌmo aeno ha leno visuva kaꞌmo alino nave neliye.
\v 106 Nagaemo, Alika fako nehana gekamo fatago gemo akame huguve, huꞌna nagoꞌyamo ataleꞌna ago kaha paiꞌnove.
\v 107 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, lusi kana yaꞌmo aliꞌnovanagi kaha maegauve, huka huꞌnana gekalefeꞌmo alika he tika nato.
\v 108 Kahao ke hovanagi kagaefeꞌmo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo nahauꞌnigeꞌna navayafatiꞌmo hisuva gemo ofalinigana huꞌna kamisuva yaꞌmo aliyo. Kagaemo alika fako nehana gemo alika naya malo.
\v 109 Nagaemo muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa neꞌmauva yaꞌnimo atalesuva kavategamo maiꞌnovaꞌmonanafa keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nage okaniꞌniye.
\v 110 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo natafausiyafeꞌmo aneꞌaimo hanagi maleꞌnayaꞌmonanafa namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo amagiꞌna oꞌataleꞌnove.
\v 111 Mafaꞌneꞌapimogimo afoꞌapimogi kagemi yaꞌapimo neꞌaliya kava huꞌna kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gemo aliꞌnovanageno hetamaꞌnimo hanege hanege huno hanegaiye. Ani gekaeꞌmo naipafiꞌmo namogaga neꞌauve.
\v 112 Avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gemo akame hume hume uꞌna falisuva afinaꞌmo hano hisiyafeꞌmo naipamo aliꞌna he tiꞌna ateꞌnove.
\p 
\v 113 Nagaemo lole apakesamo neꞌafiya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo alagi oꞌnahauꞌniyaꞌmonanafa keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo nahauꞌniye.
\v 114 Nagaemo kagaepiꞌmo fala kiꞌna maiꞌnogeka kagaemo haleguꞌnimo maiꞌnane. Gekamo alagi afole aigiye, huꞌna huteꞌna navayagunagu huꞌna maiꞌnove.
\v 115 Hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, nagaetegatiꞌmo ataletapa viyo. Gotiꞌnimoꞌmo hiyo, huno huꞌniya gemo akame huguve.
\v 116 Alagepa huꞌna afaꞌa maisuvafeꞌmo kaha maegauve, huka huꞌnana gekalefeꞌmo nayateꞌmo aliyo. Afole aisiya kavafeꞌmo navayagunagu nehuvaꞌmofeꞌmo fiku yanageno navagage hugiye.
\v 117 Nayateꞌmo aliyo, lageso osuꞌna afaꞌa maiguve. Afaꞌa maiꞌneꞌna muki afinaꞌmo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo akame huguve.
\v 118 Muki vayaꞌmogi avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo amagiꞌa neꞌatalaya vayaꞌmo kakameꞌyamo neꞌapamine. Apakaemo aigofe kavaꞌmo nehuꞌapaeꞌmo apakaiꞌapieꞌmo humi neꞌapatae.
\v 119 Goli yafaꞌmo atafiꞌmo kaeꞌnagenoꞌaeꞌmo oꞌaniꞌyaꞌamo leno afole aiꞌnigeꞌa aliꞌa neꞌatalaya kava huka hosu vayaꞌmo alika neꞌatalanaꞌmofeꞌmo kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo nahauꞌniye.
\v 120 Nagaemo kagaefeꞌmo koli nehugenoꞌaeꞌmo nagufamoꞌmo atete neꞌnahaiye. Alika fako nehana kavakaeꞌmo koli nehuve.
\p 
\v 121 Nagaemo alagepa huꞌna aliꞌna fako huꞌna apateteꞌna fatago kavaꞌmo huꞌnove. Kana yaꞌmo aliꞌa neꞌnamiya vayaꞌai apayapiꞌmo maisuvafeꞌmo alagi nataleka oꞌuvo.
\v 122 Anonaꞌnilefeꞌmo eka naimuꞌyaleꞌmo maigeꞌnao alagepa huꞌna maino. Fiku yanageꞌa ala apaki aliteꞌa apakufamo avaleliꞌa nehaiya vayaꞌmogi kana yaꞌmo aliꞌa namigayanagi naha mao.
\v 123 Nagufamo alika katika natesanafeꞌmo aulu heꞌna agege fatago kavakalefeꞌmo gekamo agesuvafeꞌmo aulu haeꞌna agege huꞌna ageꞌna maiꞌnogeno naulagafatiꞌmo nagafu nekiye.
\v 124 Kahau huka neꞌapatana kava huka kahau huka nateteka avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo alika naya malo.
\v 125 Nagaemo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamo maiꞌnove. Nagaemo kavayafatiꞌmo keꞌaepa gekamo hugeꞌna gekamo aepaꞌamo afisuva kavaꞌmo alika namiyo.
\v 126 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, apakaemo keꞌaepa gekamo ago aeꞌa ati kaeꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo aliꞌyakamo alisana afinaꞌmo afole aiꞌniye.
\v 127 Gekamo aeꞌa ati kaeꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo hiyo, huka huꞌnana gekalefeꞌmo nahauꞌniya kavaꞌmoꞌa hogote goli yafafeꞌmo nahauꞌniya kavaꞌmo ago aeno agaseꞌniye.
\v 128 Gekamo aeꞌa ati kaeꞌnayaꞌmofeꞌmo muki kavatefeꞌmo namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo, fatago gemo haneꞌniye, huꞌna nagesamo afiteꞌna aigofe kavafeꞌmo alagi oꞌnahauꞌniye.
\p 
\v 129 Kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nahau neꞌauva gemo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo nagupi mafaꞌnemoꞌmo akame nehiye.
\v 130 Gekamoꞌmo vayaꞌai apaipafiꞌmo faleno haitenoꞌaeꞌmo aeno ha nele. Negi vayaꞌmogi gekamo afiteꞌapaeꞌmo ge aepaꞌamo afigae.
\v 131 Hiyo, huka huꞌnana gekaeꞌmo naga teꞌnigeꞌnaeꞌmo navayamo aka hulina ha ha huꞌnove.
\v 132 Kagikaeꞌmo hapau apayamopafiꞌmo hapauꞌniya vayaꞌaitegamo nehana kava huka nagaefeꞌmo kahau huka nato.
\v 133 Kagaemo gekaletiꞌmo alika ho huka nateteka hosu kavaꞌmoꞌa yagaino oꞌnatesiyafeꞌmo nataleka oꞌuvo.
\v 134 Namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo akame hisuvafeꞌmo kana yaꞌmo aliꞌa namiꞌnaya kavapatiꞌmo hatu maeka nato.
\v 135 Kaugosafatiꞌmo ha le yakamoꞌa aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌnaleꞌmo aeno ha leno. Avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo alika naya malo.
\v 136 Vayaꞌmogimo keꞌaepa gekamo akame nosayaꞌmofeꞌmo lusi kava huno naunu nelamiye.
\p 
\v 137 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, fatago vekamo maiꞌneka alagepa fatago kavaꞌmo huka alika fako huka neꞌatane.
\v 138 Kavayafatiꞌmo hiyo, huka huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo fatago gemo alagi lama gemo haneꞌniye.
\v 139 Kame vayaꞌnimogi gekaeꞌmo apake kaniꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo nayamukiki nehuva kavaꞌnimoꞌa atagana huno leno nasaga liꞌniye.
\v 140 Gekamo alagi alagepa gemo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamoꞌnamo gekaeꞌmo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo nahauꞌniye.
\v 141 Ala vekamo oꞌmaiꞌnogeꞌapaeꞌmo nagaefeꞌmo ina agufa neꞌmo maiꞌniye, huꞌa nehayaꞌmonanafa namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo alagi nage okaniꞌniye.
\v 142 Fatago kavakamoꞌmo hanege hanege huno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hanegaiye. Keꞌaepa gekamo alagi lama gemo haneꞌniye.
\v 143 Hanageke yaꞌmo nagaeteꞌmo afole aiꞌnigeno nagafu kiꞌniyaꞌmonanafa hiyo, huka huꞌnana gekaeꞌmo namogaga neꞌauve.
\v 144 Kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo fatago kavaꞌamoꞌmo alagi hanege hanege huno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hanegaiye. Kagaemo gemo aepaꞌamo afisuva kavaꞌmo alika namigeꞌnao afaꞌa maino.
\p 
\v 145 Nagaemo muki naipafatiꞌmo, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, geꞌnimo afiyo, avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo akame huguve, huꞌna kagaefeꞌmo ge nehuve.
\v 146 Nagaemo, Nagufamo alika katika nategeꞌnao kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo akame hino, huꞌna kagaefeꞌmo ge nehuve.
\v 147 Ko otiꞌnigeꞌnaeꞌmo he tiꞌna, naha mao, huꞌna ge nehuve. Gekamo afole aigiye, huꞌna navayagunagu huꞌna maiꞌnove.
\v 148 Nagaemo gekaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maisuvafeꞌmo haniꞌilagamo nau okaleꞌna afaꞌa maiꞌnove.
\v 149 O, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauꞌniya kavakaletiꞌmo geꞌnimo afiyo. Alagepa huka alika fako nehana kavakaletiꞌmo alika he tika nato.
\v 150 Hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌmo nahaopaleꞌmo eꞌnae. Apakaemo keꞌaepa gekamo hanetegeꞌapaeꞌmo afagiꞌaleꞌmo maiꞌnae.
\v 151 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kagaemo nahaopaleꞌmo maiꞌnanagenoꞌaeꞌmo muki gekamo hiyo, huka huꞌnana gekamo alagi lama gemo haneꞌniye.
\v 152 Nagaemo akeyaꞌvilagamo kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo faika ateꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo afaꞌa hanegaiye, huꞌna ago afiꞌnove.
\p 
\v 153 Nagaemo keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nage okaniꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo kana yaꞌmo aliꞌnovanagi kagesamo afiteka hatu maeka nato.
\v 154 Agotileꞌmo he tika maiꞌneka naha maeka hatu maeka nato. Kaha maegauve, huka huꞌnana gekalefeꞌmo alika he tika nato.
\v 155 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo kahauya nosayaꞌmofeꞌmo apakufamo alika katika apatesanafeꞌmo afagiꞌaleꞌmo maiꞌnae.
\v 156 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Lusi kava huka kahau huka apatege apatege huka kahau huka neꞌapatane. Alagepa huka alika fako nehana kavakaletiꞌmo alika he tika nato.
\v 157 Asole vayaꞌmogi apaini huꞌa natege kame huꞌa natege huꞌa maiꞌnayaꞌmonanafa kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo ataleꞌna oꞌuꞌnove.
\v 158 Hosu kavaꞌapimo aeꞌa ati kaeꞌnaya vayaꞌmogi gekamo akame nosayaꞌmofeꞌmo apakeꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo naipamoꞌmo kana huꞌniye.
\v 159 Namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo nahauꞌniya kavaꞌnieꞌmo kagesamo afiyo. Kahau kayamopafiꞌmo kahauꞌniya kavakaletiꞌmo alika he tika nato.
\v 160 Akeyaꞌvilaga aepa faiꞌniya afiꞌnatetiꞌmo haneꞌniya gekamo alagi lama gemo haneꞌniye. Muki gekamo alika fako nehana gekamoꞌmo hanege hanege huno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo hanegaiye.
\p 
\v 161 Ala vayaꞌmo neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogi apaini huꞌa neꞌnataya kavaꞌapimo aepa vekamo oꞌmaiꞌnovaꞌmonanafa gekaekeꞌmo koli nehuve.
\v 162 Vayaꞌmogi kame huꞌa aeꞌa apakaseteꞌa alopa kagemi yaꞌmo aliteꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiya kava huꞌna gekaeꞌmo namogaga neꞌauve.
\v 163 Aigofe geeꞌmo alagi oꞌnahauꞌniyaꞌmonanafa keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo nahau nayamopafiꞌmo nahauꞌniye.
\v 164 Fatago kavaꞌmo huka alika fako nehanaꞌmofeꞌmo muki afinaꞌae afinaꞌaeꞌmo seveniꞌa afinaꞌmo kahao ke nehove.
\v 165 Keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo hapau apayamopafiꞌmo hapauꞌniya vayaꞌmogi alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnageno apaipamoꞌmo falu nehiyanageno mago yaꞌmoꞌa apavalelino asagauno aisiya yaꞌmo ohaneꞌniye.
\v 166 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, nagufamo alika katika natesanafeꞌmo navayagunagu huꞌna maiꞌneꞌna hiyo, huka huꞌnana gemo akame nehuve.
\v 167 Nagupi mafaꞌnemoꞌa kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo akame nehigenoꞌaeꞌmo lusi kava huno nahau nayamopafiꞌmo neꞌnahaiye.
\v 168 Muki nehuva kavaꞌaꞌnimo kaulagaleꞌmo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaꞌe kavayafatiꞌmo huꞌnana keꞌaepa gekaꞌeꞌmo akame nehuve.
\p 
\v 169 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, lokiya vaiꞌna ge nehuva geꞌnimo afiyo. Lapa maegauve, huka huꞌnana gekalefeꞌmo gemo aepaꞌamo afisuva kavaꞌmo alika namiyo.
\v 170 Aukaya nehuva geꞌnimo afiyo. Lapa maegauve, huka huꞌnana gekalefeꞌmo hatu maeka nato.
\v 171 Kagaemo avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnaya keꞌaepa gekamo alika naya neꞌmalanaꞌmofeꞌmo ala kagikamo kamiguve.
\v 172 Muki gekamo hiyo, huka huꞌnana gekamo fatago gemo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo navayafatiꞌmo gekamo aeꞌna hakalo huꞌna hapa paiguve.
\v 173 Namiꞌnana keꞌaepa gekamo lekana pai maleꞌnovaꞌmofeꞌmo kayatetiꞌmo naha mao.
\v 174 O, Ala kava nene, huꞌna, nagufamo alika katika natesanafeꞌmo naga nete. Keꞌaepa gekaeꞌmo namogaga neꞌauve.
\v 175 Afaꞌa maisuva yaꞌmo alika namigeꞌnao ala kagikamo kamino. Alika fako huka nateteka naha mao.
\v 176 Nagaemo hiyo, huka huꞌnana gekaeꞌmo nage okaniꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo kahauya huka nago. Lageso huꞌniya sipisipigana huꞌna kataleꞌna uꞌnovanagi aliꞌyakamo neꞌaluva vekamo kahauya huka nageka navato.
\c 120
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Nagaemo kana yaꞌmo aliꞌnova afinaꞌmo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo alopa gefatiꞌmo ge huꞌna ha paiꞌnogeno afiꞌniye.
\v 2 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Apakaemo aigofe gemo huge humi apatege nehayanagi nagupi mafaꞌnemo alika katika ato.
\p 
\v 3 Aigofe vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, anonatapilefeꞌmo na agufa yaꞌmo aligae. Gotiꞌa lapakaetegamo haiya kavaꞌmo hugiye.
\v 4 Lokiya vekamoꞌa akoꞌya keveletiꞌmo lapaegaiye. Hokanufa atamoꞌmo leno lapasagaligiye.
\p 
\v 5 Avovo nehuve. Nagaemo hosu vayaꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌna maiꞌnove. Meseki nofi vayaꞌe Keta nofi vayaꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌna maiꞌnove.
\v 6 Nagaemo lusi yatala afinaꞌmo kame hisaya vayaꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌna maiꞌnova kavaꞌmoꞌa kanale osiye.
\v 7 Nagaemo, alagepa huta magokepi lokaeta maigune, huꞌna hapa paiꞌnovaꞌmonanafa apakaemo kame hisayafekeꞌmo hapauꞌniye.
\c 121
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Nagaemo avelega aulu heꞌna agesufiye. Haiyategatiꞌmo naha maesiya yaꞌmo afole aigiye.
\v 2 Avelegatiꞌmo naha maesiya yaꞌmo afole oꞌaigifa Ala kava neꞌmo kokuꞌnaꞌe mopaꞌeꞌmo alo huꞌniya vekamokeꞌmo naha maegaiye.
\v 3 Yagaino kateꞌnisigeka aeka halu vale lamika asagauka oꞌaigane. Yagaino nekateya vekamo au okalegaiye.
\v 4 Afiyo, huꞌna, Isaleli vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino neꞌapateya vekamoꞌa au maiꞌmai osuge au okalege huteno afaꞌa maiꞌneno yagaino maigiye.
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa yagaino nekateya vekamo maiꞌniye. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa kahaopaleꞌmo he tino maiꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo auneꞌamoꞌa uluna vaino nekategeka ani ulunapiꞌmo neꞌmaine.
\v 6 Felugamo yegemoꞌmo kaleno kasaga oligiye. Haniꞌilagamo kaimoꞌmo alino hosu huno okategaiye.
\v 7 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alu hosu kavaꞌe alu hosu kavatetiꞌeꞌmo alino hosu huno okatesiyafeꞌmo yagaino katesigeno kagupi mafaꞌnemo alagepa huno maigiye.
\v 8 Nokamo ataleka visanagenoꞌaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa yagaino katege atagi neka esanagenoꞌaeꞌmo yagaino katege huno yagaino kategaiye. Hemenimo yagaino nekateyanageno henagaꞌamo muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo yagaino katesigeka alagepa huka afaꞌa maige maige huka maigane.
\c 122
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Apakaemo, Ala kava neꞌmo noꞌafiꞌmo haigetao, huꞌa naha paiꞌnageꞌnaeꞌmo namogaga aiꞌnove.
\v 2 Uta avaꞌyi huteta haita maiꞌnetaeꞌmo, O Yulusalemuo, huta, lagaemo eta kagae yafa lafi kegiꞌyafiꞌmo he tita maiꞌnone, huta nehune.
\p 
\v 3 Yulusalemu taonimo kiꞌnageno magokepiꞌmo lokaeno alagepa huno haneꞌniye.
\v 4 Muki nofi vayaꞌmo haiꞌa nefalae. Ala kava neꞌmo nofi vayaꞌamogimo Ala kava nefekeꞌmo hao ke hesayafeꞌmo Isaleli vayaꞌaifeꞌmo Goti geꞌamo afisayategamo haite haite huꞌa nehaiye.
\v 5 Ani taonifiꞌmo Nevini nofi vayapati kini vayaꞌmogimo fai maiꞌneꞌa aliꞌa fako huꞌa neꞌapataya siaꞌapimo haneꞌniye.
\p 
\v 6 Yulusalemu vayaꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌa falu huꞌa maisayafeꞌmo nunumu hutapa apateyo. Yulusalemu taonieꞌmo hapauꞌnisiya vayaꞌmogimo alagepa huꞌa maiyo.
\v 7 Yafa lafi kegiꞌyafiꞌmo alagepa huꞌa magokepi lokaeꞌa maiyo. Kini vayaꞌmogi noꞌapifi noꞌapifiꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiyo.
\v 8 Konagaꞌnimogiꞌe nafaluꞌnimogiꞌeꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maisayafeꞌmo huꞌnaeꞌmo, yafa lafi kegiyafiꞌmo alagepa huꞌa magokepi lokaeꞌa maiyo, huꞌna nunumu huꞌna neꞌapatove.
\v 9 Ala kava neꞌmo Gotitimo noꞌaeꞌmo nagesa afiꞌnaeꞌmo agae taonimo alagepa huno hanesiyafeꞌmo nayamukiki huguve.
\c 123
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Kokuꞌnapi maiꞌnana Ala vekamogae, huꞌna, Nagaemo aliꞌna maku huꞌna nekagove.
\v 2 Afiyo, huꞌna, Aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vayaꞌmogimo aliꞌya aepa vekamo ayateꞌmo agege aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya aꞌmafaꞌnemogimo aliꞌya aepa a kanomo ayateꞌmo agege huꞌa maiꞌnaya kava huta Ala kava neꞌmo Gotitimofekeꞌmo ageme ageme neꞌvisunagenoꞌaeꞌmo hau huno lategaiye.
\p 
\v 3 Vayaꞌmogimo muki afinaꞌmo lusi kava huꞌa huꞌa faipa huꞌa nelatae. Kahau huka lato, O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, kahau huka lato.
\v 4 Muki afinaꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo lagaefeꞌmo, ina agufa vayaꞌmo maiꞌnae, huꞌa hapa nepaiye. Ala vayaꞌmo maiꞌnone, huꞌa nehaya vayaꞌmogimo lusi kava huꞌa huꞌa faipa huꞌa nelatae
\c 125
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nefekeꞌmo apakesamo afiꞌa fatago nehaya vayaꞌmogimo Saiyoni avegana huꞌa maiꞌnae. Saiyoni avemoꞌa kanage kanaga osuno lokiya vaino nehaneya kava huꞌa maiꞌnae.
\v 2 Avemoꞌmo Yulusalemu taonimo faino ku aino ateꞌniya kava huno Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa vayaꞌamo faino ku aino neꞌapateyanageno muki afinaꞌaeꞌmo faino ku aino apategaiye.
\v 3 Hosu vayaꞌmogimo muki afinaꞌmo alagepa vayaꞌai mopaleꞌmo yagaiꞌa oꞌapategae. Alagepa vayaꞌmogimo hosu kavaꞌmo osisayafeꞌmo muki afinaꞌmo hosu vayaꞌmogi yagaiꞌa oꞌapategae.
\v 4 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, gekamo akame nehaya vayaꞌaitegamo kanale kavaꞌmo huvo.
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa alagepa kaꞌmo ataleꞌa kayagi kayaga kateꞌmo neꞌvaya vayaꞌmo apavalelino visigeꞌa hosu kavaꞌmo nehaya vayaꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeꞌa ugae. Isaleli vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa lapa maenagetapa yuna lapaipamo kalitapa maiyo.
\c 126
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hatu maeno lateteno Saiyoni kotegamo lavalelino eꞌnigetaeꞌmo alagamuna agegekana huta maiꞌnone.
\v 2 Lusi kava huta kigi huteta lamogaga aita yoke huꞌnone. Alu nofi vayaꞌmogi, Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa lusi kava huno hapa maeꞌniye, huꞌa huꞌnae.
\v 3 He, lusi kava huno laha maeꞌnigeta lamogaga aiꞌnone.
\v 4 Aniꞌmo leno laneꞌniya ani kalokalopafiꞌmo koꞌmo neꞌaigenoꞌaeꞌmo aniꞌmo nelamigeꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga neꞌaiya kava huta vayatimo hatu maeka apategetao lamogaga aino.
\v 5 Avina yaꞌmo nehakalaya vayaꞌmogimo apaunu nelamiyanageꞌa henagaꞌamo neꞌyaꞌmo aliteꞌapaeꞌmo apamogaga aigae.
\v 6 Mago vekamoꞌa avina yaꞌmo hakalesiyafeꞌmo alinino uꞌnigenoꞌaeꞌmo aunu nelamisiyaꞌmoꞌmo neꞌyaꞌamo alitenoꞌaeꞌmo amogaga aime aime egaiye.
\c 127
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hapa oꞌmaesiyaꞌmoꞌmo noꞌmo nekiya vayaꞌmogimo afa aliꞌyakeꞌmo aliteꞌa noꞌmo okigae. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa hapa oꞌmaesiyaꞌmoꞌmo taonifiꞌmo neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogi afaꞌageꞌmo neꞌyagaisagenoꞌaeꞌmo taonifiꞌmo hosu kavaꞌmo afole aigiye.
\v 2 Lapakaemo kotilamiyapiꞌmo lapaupatiꞌmo he titapa aliꞌyaꞌmo alime alime utapa haniꞌilagamo notapilegamo etapa avaꞌyi hutetapaeꞌmo lapaipamoꞌmo falu nosigetapa afa aliꞌyaꞌmo neꞌaligenoꞌaeꞌmo neꞌyaꞌmo afole noꞌaiye. Alagepa yatapimo afole noꞌaiyaꞌmonanafa hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauꞌniya vayaꞌamo fiku hapa maeno neꞌapamigeꞌapaeꞌmo apau nekalae.
\v 3 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa mafaꞌnemo fiku hapa maeno apamiꞌnigeꞌa aliꞌa neꞌapatae. Mafaꞌnemo alagepa miyakana huno neꞌapamiye.
\v 4 Ati vekamoꞌa asole kevemo aliteno maiꞌnisiyana alagepa huno maisiya kava huno neya vekamoꞌa mafaꞌnemo alino apatesiyaꞌmoꞌmo ani kava huno alagepa huno maigiye.
\v 5 Asole keve maleꞌnaya vayaꞌmo maiꞌnaya kava huꞌa asole mafaꞌnemo aliꞌa apateꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo apamogaga aigae. Kame vayaꞌapimogi agoti huꞌa apatesageꞌapaeꞌmo huꞌa aeꞌa apakasegae.
\c 128
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Muki vayaꞌmogi Ala kava nefekeꞌmo koli huge agae kateꞌmo uge huꞌa maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmogimo Goti aulagaleꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiꞌnayanageꞌa afaꞌa apamogaga aigae.
\p 
\v 2 Kagaemo hoyakafatiꞌmo neꞌyaꞌmo alika netekaeꞌmo kamogaga aika alagepa huka maigane.
\v 3 Akamoꞌmo asole alagamo neꞌaeya nofikana huno nokafiꞌmo maigiye. Mafaꞌne anagakamogimo saufa olivi yosagana huꞌa maiꞌneꞌa hiꞌyalamukaleꞌmo faiꞌa ku aiꞌa kategae.
\v 4 Afiyo, huꞌna, Ala kava nefekeꞌmo koli nehaya vayaꞌmogimo ani kava huꞌa alagepa huꞌa maigae.
\p 
\v 5 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa Saiyoni taonifatiꞌmo kaha maeno. Muki afinaꞌmo ma mopafiꞌmo maiꞌnekaeꞌmo Yulusalemu taonifiꞌmo maiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo apakesanageꞌapaeꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiyo.
\v 6 He, kagaemo mafaꞌnekamogimo aliꞌa apatesaya mafaꞌnemo afaꞌa apakesanafeꞌmo Gotiꞌa kaha maeno.
\p Isaleli vayaꞌmo alagepa huꞌa maiyo.
\c 130
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neo, huꞌna, muki yaꞌmoꞌa aino nati kaeꞌnigeꞌna afepilaga maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo kagaefekeꞌmo keya aeꞌna ge nehuve.
\v 2 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, geꞌnimo afiyo. Naha mao, huꞌna keya aeꞌna ge nehuva geꞌnimo kagetafo huka afiyo.
\v 3 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, hosu kavatimo alika fako huka lateteka miyatimo lamiꞌnanesinana Ala kava nene, huꞌna, ina laꞌmo afaꞌa aeno kasalo paeyesine.
\v 4 Magoke vekamoꞌa alagi aeno kasalo opaeyesinaꞌmonanafa kagaefeꞌmo koli huteꞌa mono hisayafeꞌmo hosu kavatimo alika neꞌatalane.
\v 5 Nagaemo Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa naha maesiyafeꞌmo agava maiꞌneꞌna geꞌaekeꞌmo nagesa afiteꞌna agava maiꞌneꞌnaeꞌmo navayagunagu nehuve.
\v 6 Neꞌyagaiya vayaꞌmogi hani huꞌniya yaꞌmo hano hisigeno ha le yaꞌmo afole aisiyafeꞌmo nehapaigeꞌa agava neꞌmaiya kava huꞌna Ala kava nefeꞌmo magoꞌe huꞌna agava neꞌmauve. He, agava neꞌmaiya kava huꞌna aeꞌna apakaseꞌna Ala kava nefeꞌmo magoꞌe huꞌna agava neꞌmauve.
\v 7 Isaleli vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava nefeꞌmo lapakesamo afitetapa lapa maesiyafeꞌmo lapavayagunagu hutapa maiyo. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa vayaꞌaeꞌmo hau huno neꞌapateyanageno olapatalegaiye. Agaemo muki alu hosu kavapatiꞌe alu hosu kavapatiꞌeꞌmo miya faino hatu maeno neꞌapateyaꞌmofeꞌmo ani kavafeꞌmo lapakesa afitetapa lapavayagunagu hutapa maiyo.
\v 8 Agaemo agaiꞌa Isaleli vayaꞌamo muki alu hosu kavapatiꞌe alu hosu kavapatiꞌeꞌmo miya faino hatu maeno apategaiye.
\c 131
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, nagufamo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna noꞌnatove. Aeꞌna apakaseꞌnova vekamo maiꞌnove, huꞌna nosuve. Nagaemo alopa aliꞌyafeꞌmo nagesa oꞌafige afaꞌa oꞌagesuva kavafeꞌmo nagesa oꞌafige nehuve.
\v 2 Nahaꞌye nosigeno naipamoꞌmo falu nehiye. Itaꞌamoꞌeꞌmo magokepi lokaeno maiꞌneno nuꞌmo mo siꞌniya mafaꞌnegana huꞌna maiꞌnove. Naipamoꞌa nuꞌmo mo siꞌniya mafaꞌnegana huno haneꞌniye.
\v 3 Isaleli nofi vayaꞌnimogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa afaꞌa laha maegaiye, hutetapa hemenigekeꞌmo aepa faitetapa muki afinaꞌae afinaꞌaeꞌmo lapakesamo afiyo.
\c 133
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Apakeyo, huꞌna, Goti konaga vayaꞌamogimo magoke apaipa apakesamo aliteꞌa magokepi lokaeꞌa alagepa huꞌa maisaya kavaꞌapimoꞌmo alagepa kavaꞌmo amuse hisaya kavaꞌmo haneꞌniye.
\v 2 Mani agufa alagepa kavaꞌmoꞌa alagepa atumo neꞌaiya uvelimo Gotiꞌa aliꞌyaꞌamo alisayafeꞌmo lekana paino apateꞌniya vayaꞌai apakufaleꞌmo faleꞌa neꞌapataya uveligana huno haneꞌniye. Eloniꞌa hogote vekamo mono huno neꞌapateya vekamo agenopafiꞌmo ani agufa uvelimo lakiꞌa ateꞌnageno emineno avenanapa ayokatetiꞌmo yatala kukenaꞌamo atupalegamo lamino kasaeꞌniye.
\v 3 Alagepa huꞌa magokepi lokaeꞌa neꞌmaiya kavaꞌmoꞌa netepiꞌmo Hemoni aveleꞌe Saiyoni aveleꞌeꞌmo kahauleꞌmo lao yaꞌmo emineno nehaneya lao yakana huno haneꞌniye. Gotiꞌa magoke apaipa apakesamo aliteꞌa magokepi lokaeꞌa alagepa huꞌa neꞌmaiyategamo fiku hapa maeno neꞌapamiyanageꞌa alagepa huꞌa maige maige huꞌa maigae.
\c 134
\s1 Mono notegamo ugefe nehaiya vayaꞌmo kateꞌmo nehaiꞌapaeꞌmo nehaya yokemae
\p 
\v 1 Muki vayaꞌamogitapamo afiyo, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo aliꞌyaꞌamo neꞌaliya vayaꞌmogitapamo haniꞌilagamo Ala kava neꞌmo noꞌafiꞌmo he titapa ala agiꞌamo amiyo.
\v 2 Aote mono noꞌafatiꞌmo lapayaꞌmo alita asaga huliꞌnetapaeꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hutapa ateyo.
\p 
\v 3 Kokuꞌnaꞌe ma mopaꞌeꞌmo alo huꞌniya Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa Saiyoni taonifatiꞌmo lapa maeno.
\c 139
\s1 Gotiꞌa muki afinaꞌmo nelage, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava nene, huꞌna, alagi nageka alagepa huka nageꞌnane.
\v 2 Nagaemo itopaleꞌmo neꞌmaufi he tiꞌna neꞌmaufi huꞌna maiꞌnogekaeꞌmo neꞌnagane. Kagaemo afagitegamo maiꞌnekaeꞌmo nagesa neꞌafuva nagesamo neꞌnagane.
\v 3 Umenitata huge havaege nehugekaeꞌmo nageteka muki nehuva kavaꞌnimo ago neꞌnagane.
\v 4 Ge osuꞌnovaꞌmonanafa Ala kava nene, huꞌna, henagaꞌamo hisuva geꞌnimo ago ageꞌnane.
\v 5 Yagaika ku aika nateteka nagaeteꞌmo kayaꞌmo maleka neꞌnatane.
\v 6 Ago nageꞌnanana kagae kaipa kagesamoꞌmo nagae naipa nagesamo ago aeno agaseꞌniyanageꞌna afaꞌa oꞌagegauve.
\v 7 Kagaetegatiꞌmo faiꞌna kasalo paetaleꞌna haiyategamo uguve. Maiꞌnanategamo uꞌna oꞌmaiꞌna naoteꞌmo maisuvafeꞌmo haiyategamo uguve.
\v 8 Kokuꞌnapiꞌmo haiꞌna maisuvana maiꞌnane. Nagaemo faliꞌnaya vayaꞌmo uꞌa maiꞌnaya kotegamo lamiꞌna maiguvana maiꞌnane.
\v 9 Yegemo hainenoꞌaeꞌmo hayomo neꞌaeya yaꞌmoꞌa afagitega mopa atupaleꞌmo malage huno neꞌviya kava huꞌna malage huꞌna afagitega uꞌna maiguvana maiꞌnane.
\v 10 Afagitega uꞌna maiꞌnisugekaeꞌmo kayatetiꞌmo navalelika egane. Ani kava huka lamaga kayatetiꞌmo natafauka maigane.
\v 11 Nagaemo, hani huka aika nati kao, huꞌna hisuvana hani huꞌniya yapiꞌmo ha le yakamoꞌa aeno ha leꞌnigeka neꞌnagane.
\v 12 Hani huꞌnisiya yapiꞌmo uꞌna fala kisuvana nagegane. Yegemoꞌmo aeno ha neleya kava huno kagae kaulagaleꞌmo hanipiꞌmo aeno ha nele. Hani nehiya kavaꞌmoꞌmo kagae kaulagaleꞌmo ha le yakana huno haneꞌniye.
\v 13 Muki nahau nayamopafiꞌmo haneꞌniya yaꞌaꞌnimo kagaikamo alo huꞌnanageno kagaika yaꞌmo haneꞌniye. Muki nagufafiꞌmo haneꞌniya yaꞌaꞌnimo alo huteka alika itaꞌnimo aipafiꞌmo magokepi maleꞌnane.
\v 14 Kagaemo alagepa huka alo huka nateꞌnanaꞌmofeꞌmo koli huteꞌna kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga nehuve. Nagaetegamo huꞌnana kavaꞌmo ageteꞌnaeꞌmo nahau neꞌauve. Huꞌnana kavafeꞌmo alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌnane, huꞌna huteꞌna aliꞌna namalagiꞌnove.
\v 15 Itaꞌnimo aipafiꞌmo maiꞌnogenoꞌaeꞌmo nayamufaꞌnimo afole aiteno kosime kosime uꞌnigeka nageꞌnane.
\v 16 Itaꞌnimoꞌmo aipafatiꞌmo alino oꞌnateꞌniya afinaꞌmo muki nagufafiꞌmo haneꞌniya yaꞌaꞌnimo ago ageꞌnane. Ma mopafiꞌmo afole aiꞌna oꞌmaiꞌnogekaeꞌmo na magi afinaꞌmo ma mopafiꞌmo maisapi huka mukufiꞌmo ago avoꞌmo kae maleꞌnane.
\v 17 Nagaefeꞌmo kagesamo neꞌafina kavakamoꞌmo aeto agufa kanale yaꞌmo haneꞌnigeno neꞌnahaiye. Nagaefeꞌmo kagesamo neꞌafina kavaꞌmo lusi asole kavaꞌmo haneꞌniye.
\v 18 Lekana paiguvana ani kahaepaleꞌmo aise yafaꞌmo ago aeno agaseꞌniya agufa yaꞌmo haneꞌniye. Naupatiꞌmo he tiꞌnaeꞌmo kagaeꞌekeꞌmo maiꞌnoꞌae.
\v 19 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, hosu vayaꞌmo apamagisanafeꞌmo neꞌnahaiye. Kaveta nehapaya vayaꞌmo nataleꞌa visayafeꞌmo neꞌnahaiye.
\v 20 Apakaemo kagaefeꞌmo hosu gemo huteꞌa huꞌa faipa huꞌa nekatae.
\v 21 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, Apaini huꞌa nekataya vayaꞌaifeꞌmo naini huꞌna neꞌapatove. Apakameꞌyamo nekamiya vayaꞌai apaulagafiꞌmo navenatuꞌna heꞌna neꞌapatove.
\v 22 Nagaemo apakaefeꞌmo alagi oꞌnahauꞌnigeꞌnaeꞌmo, kame vayaꞌnie, huꞌna nehuve.
\v 23 O Gotiyo, huꞌna, naipa nagesafiꞌmo alagepa huka alika fako huka nago. Naipa nagesafiꞌmo aulu haeka ago.
\v 24 Naipafiꞌmo hosu kavaꞌnimo haneꞌnifigi ageteka alagepa huꞌna maige maige huꞌna maisuva kateꞌmo navalelika uvo.
\c 145
\s1 Gotiꞌa alagepa kavaꞌmo nehiye, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Gotiꞌnimogamo kini neꞌnimogae, huꞌna, kagaefekeꞌmo ala vekamo maiꞌnane, huꞌna huguve. Muki afinaꞌmo kahao ke hege hege huꞌna kahao ke hegauve.
\v 2 Muki afinaꞌae afinaꞌaeꞌmo kahao ke hegauve. Muki afinaꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huge huge huꞌna maiguve.
\v 3 Ala kava neꞌmo ala neꞌmo maiꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga huꞌa atesaya vekamo maiꞌniye. Ala agiꞌamo haneꞌniyaꞌmofeꞌmo ageta aeto osugune.
\v 4 Itaꞌapi afoꞌapimogimo huꞌnana kavafeꞌmo, lusi alagepa kavaꞌmo huꞌniye, huꞌa aliꞌa apatesaya mafaꞌneꞌapieꞌmo kava gemo huꞌa hapa paitesageꞌapaeꞌmo apakaemo henagaꞌamo aliꞌa apatesaya mafaꞌneꞌapieꞌmo kava gemo huꞌa hapa paite hapa paite huliꞌa ugae.
\v 5 Apakaemo kagaefeꞌmo huꞌapaeꞌmo, ha le konali yaꞌagi ala agiꞌagi huno haneꞌniya vekamo maiꞌniye, huꞌa hisageꞌnaeꞌmo nagaeꞌeꞌmo aeto agufa kanale kavakaeꞌmo nagesa afifi huꞌna maiguve.
\v 6 Vayaꞌmogi lokiya kavaꞌmo nehana kavakaeꞌmo kava gemo hisageꞌnaeꞌmo nagaeꞌeꞌmo, ala vekamo maiꞌniye, huꞌna huguve.
\v 7 Apakaemo kanale alagepa kavaꞌmo nehana kavafeꞌmo kava gemo huꞌa hapa paige fatago kavakaeꞌmo yokemo huge huꞌa maigae.
\v 8 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa fiku laha maeno lamige hau huno latege malage huno aipamo leno olatege hau ayamopafiꞌmo hauge huno neꞌmaiye.
\v 9 Agaemo muki vayaꞌaitegamo alagepa kavaꞌmo huteno muki alo hu maleꞌniya yategaꞌeꞌmo hau huno neꞌapate.
\v 10 O Ala kava nene, huꞌna, muki alo huꞌnana vayaꞌmogiꞌe yaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo kagikaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hugae. Muki vayakamogimo kahao ke hegae.
\v 11-12 Apakaemo muki vayaꞌmogimo lokiya kavaꞌmo nehana kavakaꞌe ha le konali yakaletiꞌmo neꞌyagaina kavakaleꞌefeꞌmo ava gemo afisayafeꞌmo neꞌyagaina kavafeꞌmo, lokiya himamuꞌaletiꞌmo ani kavaꞌmo nehiye, huꞌa hugae.
\v 13 Muki afinaꞌmo yagaige yagaige huka yagaigane. Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa, ma kavaꞌmo huguve, huno huꞌniya gemo akame huno ani kavaꞌmo nehiye. Muki kavaꞌamo alagepa kavaꞌageꞌmo haneꞌniye.
\v 14 Agaemo hanageke yaꞌmo neꞌaliya vayaꞌmo hapa maege asagauꞌa aiꞌnaya vayaꞌmo alino he tino apatege huno neꞌmaiye.
\v 15 Muki afaꞌa neꞌmaiya yaꞌmogiꞌe vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo apaka neteya afinaꞌmo kagaefeꞌmo apakesamo neꞌafigekaeꞌmo neꞌyaꞌmo neꞌapamine.
\v 16 Hapauꞌnigekaeꞌmo neꞌapamine.
\v 17 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa muki afinaꞌmo ani kava nehunoꞌaeꞌmo fatago kavaꞌmo huge yagu yaga kavaꞌmo huge nehiye.
\v 18 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa agaefeꞌmo apaipafatiꞌmo keya aeꞌa ge nehaya vayaꞌai hapaopaleꞌmo eno neꞌmaiye.
\v 19 Agaefeꞌmo koli huꞌneꞌa mono nehaya vayaꞌaitegamo hapauꞌnisiya kavaꞌmo afaꞌa hugiye. Keya aeꞌa ge nehagenoꞌaeꞌmo apakufamo alino katino neꞌapate.
\v 20 Ala kava neꞌmoꞌa agaefeꞌmo hapau apayamofiꞌmo hapauꞌniya vayaꞌaiteꞌmo yagaino neꞌapategeꞌa afaꞌa neꞌmaiye. Afaꞌa neꞌmaiyaꞌmonanafa muki hosu vayaꞌmo alino apagoꞌya lagauno apatalegaiye.
\v 21 Muki afinaꞌmo Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌna asaga huꞌna ategauve. Muki afinaꞌmo muki afaꞌa neꞌmaiya yaꞌmogiꞌe vayaꞌmogiꞌeꞌmo aote agiꞌaleꞌmo aliꞌa asaga hiyo.
\c 150
\s1 Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌalekeꞌmo alita asaga hiyo, huno huꞌniya gemae
\p 
\v 1 Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo. Mono noꞌafiꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo. Kokuꞌnapi himamuꞌalefeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo.
\v 2 Himamuꞌaletiꞌmo huꞌniya kavatefeꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo. Magoꞌe huno hogote vekamo maiꞌniya kava hutapa magoꞌe hutapa agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo.
\v 3 Pikulimo nehutapa agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo. Alu agufa gita alu agufa gitamo neꞌamagitapa agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo.
\v 4 Yaveꞌyamo neꞌamagitapa lapaiyamo aetapa agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo. Gita neꞌamagitapa kapufa gemo hutapa agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo.
\v 5 Veloꞌmo neꞌamagitapa alopa gefatiꞌmo hutapa agiꞌaleꞌmo alitapa asaga hiyo.
\v 6 Lapavamusamo neꞌaiya vayaꞌmogitapae, huꞌna, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo. He, Ala kava neꞌmo agiꞌaleꞌmo alita asaga hiyo. 
